  <para style="imt">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="imt1">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="im">Injongo kaMatewu ngeyokutshengisa ukuthi uNkulunkulu ugcine isithembiso sakhe sendulo ku-Israyeli ngempilo, ukufa kanye lokuvuka kwabafileyo kukaJesu uKhristu. Umbuso wezulu lowo obukade wakhangelelwa usubuya emhlabeni, uletha indaba yamaJuda enzikini. UMatewu uqala ngokuveza ukuthi uJesu wayeyindodana kaDavida, inkosi ka-Israyeli eyayidume kakhulu njalo eyindodana ka-Abhrahama, uyise lomqali ka-Israyeli. UJesu ngumʼIsrayeli oqotho, njalo unguKhristu owathenjiswa nguNkulunkulu.</para>
  <para style="ip">UKhristu uvezwe engophila kabutsha njengokulondwa kodaba luka-Israyeli, ekwehleleni kwakhe eMfuleni uJodani, ukulingwa kwakhe enkangala, ukubuthanisa abafundi abalitshumi lambili njengezizwe ezilitshumi lambili ezintsha, ukuqansa kwakhe intaba esiyakwethula iThora (incwadi yemithetho yamaJuda), lokunye. Umlobi uveza sobala umbono wokuthi uJesu unguMose omutsha ngokuqoqa imfundiso yakhe ngenkulumo ezinhlanu ezinde zona eziphawulwe ngezehlukaniso ezitshiyeneyo ngomutsho othi <char style="qt">Wathi eseqedile uJesu ukukhuluma ngalokhu.</char> NjengeThora elalilengwalo ezinhlanu, uMatewu wethula izigaba ezinhlanu ezimqoka.</para>
  <para style="ip">Ugwalo luphetha ngokuchaza ukuthi uJesu wasiletha njani isenzo esitsha esikhulu sokuletha insindiso ebantwini bakhe. Njengendabeni yohambo lwabako-Israyeli, kuqala kuthakazelelwe isidlo sePhasika, besekulandela ukukhululwa. UJesu unikela ngempilo yakhe ukuze umhlaba ukhululeke, njalo ebesevuswa kwabafileyo. Ekuqaliseni kogwalo, uJesu uphiwa ibizo elithi <char style="qt">Emanuweli</char> okutsho ukuthi, “uNkulunkulu ulathi.” Kuthi ekucineni, uJesu uthuma abalandeli bakhe emhlabeni ngesithembiso sokuthi <char style="qt">ngeqiniso ngihlezi ngilani izikhathi zonke.</char></para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="MAT 1"/>
  <para style="s1">Usendo LukaJesu Khristu</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 1:1"/>Umbhalo wosendo lukaJesu Khristu indodana kaDavida, indodana ka-Abhrahama:<verse eid="MAT 1:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 1:2"/>U-Abhrahama wayenguyise ka-Isaka,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:2">u-Isaka uyise kaJakhobe,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:2">uJakhobe uyise kaJuda labafowabo,<verse eid="MAT 1:2"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 1:3"/>uJuda uyise kaPherezi loZera, unina owayenguThamari,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:3">uPherezi uyise kaHezironi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:3">uHezironi uyise kaRamu,<verse eid="MAT 1:3"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 1:4"/>uRamu uyise ka-Aminadabi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:4">u-Aminadabi uyise kaNashoni,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:4">uNahishoni uyise kaSalimoni,<verse eid="MAT 1:4"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 1:5"/>uSalimoni uyise kaBhowazi, unina owayenguRahabi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:5">uBhowazi uyise ka-Obhedi, unina owayenguRuthe,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:5">u-Obhedi uyise kaJese,<verse eid="MAT 1:5"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 1:6"/>uJese uyise wenkosi uDavida.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="MAT 1:6"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:6">UDavida wayenguyise kaSolomoni, unina owayeke waba ngumka-Uriya,<verse eid="MAT 1:6"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 1:7"/>uSolomoni uyise kaRehobhowami,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:7">uRehobhowami uyise ka-Abhija,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:7">u-Abhija uyise ka-Asa,<verse eid="MAT 1:7"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 1:8"/>u-Asa uyise kaJehoshafathi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:8">uJehoshafathi uyise kaJehoramu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:8">uJehoramu uyise ka-Uziya,<verse eid="MAT 1:8"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 1:9"/>u-Uziya uyise kaJothamu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:9">uJothamu uyise ka-Ahazi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:9">u-Ahazi uyise kaHezekhiya,<verse eid="MAT 1:9"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 1:10"/>uHezekhiya uyise kaManase,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:10">uManase uyise ka-Amoni,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:10">u-Amoni uyise kaJosiya,<verse eid="MAT 1:10"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 1:11"/>uJosiya owayenguyise kaJekhoniya labafowabo ngesikhathi bethunjwe eBhabhiloni.<verse eid="MAT 1:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 1:12"/>Emva kokuthunjwa eBhabhiloni:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:12">uJekhoniya wayenguyise kaSheyalithiyeli,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:12">uSheyalithiyeli uyise kaZerubhabheli,<verse eid="MAT 1:12"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 1:13"/>uZerubhabheli uyise ka-Abhiyudi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:13">u-Abhiyudi uyise ka-Eliyakhimu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:13">u-Eliyakhimu uyise ka-Azori,<verse eid="MAT 1:13"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 1:14"/>u-Azori uyise kaZadokhi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:14">uZadokhi uyise ka-Akhimu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:14">u-Akhimu uyise ka-Elihudi,<verse eid="MAT 1:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 1:15"/>u-Elihudi uyise ka-Eliyazari,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:15">u-Eliyazari uyise kaMathani,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 1:15">uMathani uyise kaJakhobe,<verse eid="MAT 1:15"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 1:16"/>uJakhobe uyise kaJosefa, umkaMariya, owazala uJesu obizwa ngokuthi nguKhristu.<verse eid="MAT 1:16"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 1:17"/>Ngokunjalo-ke, kwakulezizukulwane ezilitshumi lane sezizonke kusukela ku-Abhrahama kusiya kuDavida, ezilitshumi lane kusukela kuDavida kusiya ekuthunjweni yiBhabhiloni njalo ezilitshumi lane kusukela ekuthunjweni kusiya kuKhristu.<verse eid="MAT 1:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuzalwa KukaJesu Khristu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 1:18"/>UJesu Khristu wazalwa kanje: Unina uMariya wayethembise ukuthi uzakwendela kuJosefa kodwa kwathi bengakahlangani wabonakala esezithwele kwenziwe ngoMoya oNgcwele. <verse eid="MAT 1:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 1:19"/>Ngoba umkakhe uJosefa wayeyindoda elungileyo emthethweni, njalo engafuni ukumyangisa ebantwini, wacabanga ukumala ngasese.<verse eid="MAT 1:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 1:20"/>Uthe esekucabangile lokhu, kwafika kuye ingilosi yeNkosi ephutsheni yathi, “Josefa ndodana kaDavida, ungesabi ukuthatha uMariya ukuba abe ngumkakho ngoba lokhu akhulelwe ngakho kuvela kuMoya oNgcwele. <verse eid="MAT 1:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 1:21"/>Uzabeletha indodana ozayetha ibizo uthi nguJesu ngoba uzasindisa abantu bakhe ezonweni zabo.”<verse eid="MAT 1:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 1:22"/>Konke lokhu kwenzakala ukuze kugcwaliseke okwatshiwo yiNkosi ngomphrofethi ukuthi: <verse eid="MAT 1:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 1:23"/>“Intombi egcweleyo izakhulelwa izale indodana, bayibize ngokuthi ngu-Emanuweli”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">1.23 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 7.14</char></note> (okutsho ukuthi, “uNkulunkulu ulathi”).<verse eid="MAT 1:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 1:24"/>UJosefa esevukile ebuthongweni wenza lokho ingilosi yeNkosi eyayimlaye khona, wamthatha uMariya waba ngumkakhe. <verse eid="MAT 1:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 1:25"/>Kodwa kazange embathe laye waze wabeletha indodana. Wayetha ibizo wathi nguJesu.<verse eid="MAT 1:25"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="MAT 2"/>
  <para style="s1">Izazi Zethekelela UKhristu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 2:1"/>UJesu esezelwe eBhethilehema laseJudiya ngesikhathi sokubusa kwenkosi uHerodi, kwafika eJerusalema iZazi zivela empumalanga, <verse eid="MAT 2:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 2:2"/>zabuza zathi, “Ungaphi lowo ozalelwe ukuba yinkosi yamaJuda na? Sibone inkanyezi yakhe empumalanga ngakho size ukuzamkhonza.”<verse eid="MAT 2:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 2:3"/>Kwathi inkosi uHerodi isikuzwile lokhu yakhathazeka, kanye leJerusalema lonke. <verse eid="MAT 2:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 2:4"/>Kwathi esebizele ndawonye abaphristi abakhulu bonke labafundisi bomthetho, wababuza ukuthi uKhristu wayezazalelwa ngaphi. <verse eid="MAT 2:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 2:5"/>Baphendula bathi, “EBhethilehema laseJudiya, ngoba lokhu yikho okwalotshwa ngumphrofethi ukuthi:<verse eid="MAT 2:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 2:6"/>‘Kodwa wena Bhethilehema, elizweni lakoJuda,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 2:6">kawumncinyane kulabo bonke ababusi bakoJuda;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 2:6">ngoba kuzavela umbusi kuwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 2:6">ozakuba ngumelusi wabantu bami bako-Israyeli.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UMikha 5.2</char></note>”<verse eid="MAT 2:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 2:7"/>UHerodi wasezibiza iZazi ngasese wadingisisa kuzo isikhathi inkanyezi eyaphuma ngaso ngqe. <verse eid="MAT 2:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 2:8"/>Wabathuma eBhethilehema wathi, “Hambani liyemdinga umntwana. Lingamfumana lingazise masinyane ukuze lami ngihambe ngiyemkhonza.”<verse eid="MAT 2:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 2:9"/>Sezizwile okwatshiwo yinkosi, zasuka zahamba, inkanyezi leyo ezaziyibonile empumalanga yahamba phambi kwazo yaze yayakuma lapho umntwana ayekhona. <verse eid="MAT 2:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 2:10"/>Zathi ziyibona inkanyezi zagcwala intokozo. <verse eid="MAT 2:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 2:11"/>Zangena endlini zambona umntwana lonina uMariya, zakhothama zamkhonza. Zasezivula impahla zazo eziligugu zamkhunga ngezipho zegolide lempepha lemure. <verse eid="MAT 2:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 2:12"/>Kwathi ngoba zixwayisiwe ephutsheni ukuthi zingabuyeli kuHerodi, zaqonda elizweni lakibo ngenye indlela.<verse eid="MAT 2:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubalekela EGibhithe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 2:13"/>Kwathi sezihambile, ingilosi yeNkosi yabonakala kuJosefa ngephupho. Yathi, “Vuka uthathe umntwana lonina libalekele eGibhithe. Lihlale khonale ngize ngilitshele ngoba uHerodi uzamdinga umntwana efuna ukumbulala.”<verse eid="MAT 2:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 2:14"/>Ngakho wavuka wathatha umntwana lonina ebusuku waya eGibhithe <verse eid="MAT 2:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 2:15"/>lapho abahlala khona uHerodi waze wafa. Ngakho kwagcwaliseka lokho iNkosi eyayikutshilo ngomphrofethi ukuthi, “Indodana yami ngayikhupha eGibhithe.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.15 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UHosiya 11.1</char></note><verse eid="MAT 2:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 2:16"/>Kwathi ukuba uHerodi ananzelele ukuthi iZazi zazimphicile wazonda kakhulu, wasekhupha umlayo wokuthi kubulawe bonke abantwana abangabafana eBhethilehema lasemangweni wonke oseduze, bonke ababeleminyaka emibili kusehla, kuhambelana lesikhathi leso ayesitshelwe yiZazi. <verse eid="MAT 2:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 2:17"/>Ngakho lokho okwakutshiwo ngumphrofethi uJeremiya kwagcwaliseka ukuthi:<verse eid="MAT 2:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 2:18"/>“Ilizwi lizwakala eRama,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 2:18">ukukhala lesililo esikhulu,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 2:18">uRasheli ekhalela abantwana bakhe njalo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 2:18">wala ukududuzwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 2:18">ngoba kabasekho.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">2.18 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UJeremiya 31.15</char></note><verse eid="MAT 2:18"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubuyela ENazaretha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 2:19"/>UHerodi esefile, ingilosi yeNkosi yabonakala ngephupho kuJosefa eseGibhithe <verse eid="MAT 2:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 2:20"/>yathi, “Sukuma uthathe umntwana lonina liye elizweni lako-Israyeli ngoba labo ababefuna ukubulala umntwana sebefile.”<verse eid="MAT 2:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 2:21"/>Ngakho wasukuma wathatha umntwana lonina waya elizweni lako-Israyeli. <verse eid="MAT 2:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 2:22"/>Kodwa wathi ngokuzwa ukuthi u-Akhelasi wayebusa eJudiya esikhundleni sikayise uHerodi wesaba ukuya khona. Kwathi esexwayisiwe ephutsheni wahamba wayahlala eGalile, <verse eid="MAT 2:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 2:23"/>edolobheni elalithiwa yiNazaretha. Ngalokho kwagcwaliseka okwatshiwo ngabaphrofethi ukuthi: Uzabizwa ngokuthi ngoweNazaretha.<verse eid="MAT 2:23"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="MAT 3"/>
  <para style="s1">UJohane UMbhaphathizi Ulungisa Indlela</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 3:1"/>Ngalesosikhathi kwafika uJohane uMbhaphathizi etshumayela enkangala yaseJudiya <verse eid="MAT 3:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 3:2"/>esithi, “Phendukani ngoba umbuso wezulu ususondele.” <verse eid="MAT 3:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 3:3"/>Nguye lo okwakhulunywa ngaye ngumphrofethi u-Isaya kwathiwa:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 3:3">“Ilizwi lomemezayo enkangala lithi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 3:3">‘Lungiselani iNkosi indlela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 3:3">yenzani izindlela zayo ziqonde.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3.3 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 40.3</char></note>”<verse eid="MAT 3:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 3:4"/>Izigqoko zikaJohane zazenziwe ngoboya bekamela, elebhanti lesikhumba okhalweni lwakhe. Ukudla kwakhe kwakuzintethe loluju lwenyosi zeganga. <verse eid="MAT 3:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 3:5"/>Abantu baphuma baya kuye bevela eJerusalema lakulo lonke elaseJudiya lemangweni wonke waseJodani. <verse eid="MAT 3:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 3:6"/>Bevuma izono zabo, babhaphathizwa nguye emfuleni uJodani.<verse eid="MAT 3:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 3:7"/>Kodwa wathi ebona abaFarisi labaSadusi abanengi besiza lapho ayebhaphathizela khona wathi kubo, “Lina nzalo yezinyoka! Lilimukiswe ngubani ukuthi libalekele ulaka oluzayo na? <verse eid="MAT 3:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 3:8"/>Thelani izithelo ezihambelana lokuphenduka. <verse eid="MAT 3:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 3:9"/>Njalo lingacabangi ukuthi lingazitshela ukuthi, ‘Silo-Abhrahama ongubaba wethu.’ Mina ngilitshela ukuthi kuwonala amatshe uNkulunkulu angamenzela u-Abhrahama abantwana. <verse eid="MAT 3:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 3:10"/>Ihloka selivele selisezimpandeni zezihlahla njalo zonke izihlahla ezingatheli izithelo ezinhle zizaganyulwa, ziphoselwe emlilweni.<verse eid="MAT 3:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 3:11"/>Mina ngilibhaphathiza ngamanzi okutshengisa ukuphenduka. Kodwa ngemva kwami kuza olamandla kulami njalo kakungilingananga ukuthwala amanyathela akhe. Uzalibhaphathiza ngoMoya oNgcwele langomlilo. <verse eid="MAT 3:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 3:12"/>Isitsha sakhe sokwela sisesandleni sakhe njalo uzathanyela isiza sakhe, abuthele amabele akhe wonke esiphaleni, kuthi amakhoba awatshise ngomlilo ongacitshekiyo.”<verse eid="MAT 3:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubhaphathizwa KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 3:13"/>UJesu weza eJodani evela eGalile ukuba abhaphathizwe nguJohane. <verse eid="MAT 3:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 3:14"/>Kodwa uJohane wazama ukwenqaba ngokuthi, “Yimi engidinga ukubhaphathizwa nguwe, kanti pho ungeza njani kimi?”<verse eid="MAT 3:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 3:15"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Yekela kube njalo okwakhathesi ngoba kufanele ukuba sikwenze lokhu ukuze sigcwalise konke ukulunga.”</char> Ngakho uJohane wasevuma.<verse eid="MAT 3:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 3:16"/>Masinyane nje uJesu eqeda kubhaphathizwa waphuma emanzini. Khonokho nje izulu lavuleka, wasebona uMoya kaNkulunkulu usehla njengejuba njalo usehlela phezu kwakhe. <verse eid="MAT 3:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 3:17"/>Ilizwi elavela ezulwini lathi, “Lo yiNdodana yami engiyithandayo; ngiyathokoza kakhulu ngayo.”<verse eid="MAT 3:17"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="MAT 4"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukulingwa KukaJesu ENkangala</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 4:1"/>UJesu wasekhokhelwa nguMoya wamusa enkangala ukuthi ayelingwa nguSathane. <verse eid="MAT 4:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 4:2"/>Emva kokuzila ukudla okwensuku ezingamatshumi amane lobusuku obungamatshumi amane wayeselambile. <verse eid="MAT 4:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 4:3"/>Umlingi weza kuye wathi, “Nxa uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu tshela amatshe la aphenduke abe yisinkwa.”<verse eid="MAT 4:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 4:4"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kulotshiwe ukuthi: ‘Umuntu kayikuphila ngesinkwa kuphela kodwa ngelizwi lonke eliphuma emlonyeni kaNkulunkulu.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 8.3</char></note><char style="wj">”</char><verse eid="MAT 4:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 4:5"/>USathane wasemthatha wamusa emzini ongcwele, wamisa engqongweni yethempeli. <verse eid="MAT 4:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 4:6"/>Wathi kuye, “Nxa uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu, ziphosele phansi. Njengoba kulotshiwe ukuthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 4:6">‘Uzalaya izingilosi zakhe ngawe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 4:6">zikuqage ngezandla zazo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 4:6">ukuze ungatshayeki ngonyawo lwakho elitsheni.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 91.11-12</char></note>”<verse eid="MAT 4:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 4:7"/>UJesu wamphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kulotshiwe ukuthi, ‘Ungayilingi iNkosi uNkulunkulu wakho.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 6.16</char></note><char style="wj">”</char><verse eid="MAT 4:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 4:8"/>Waphinda njalo uSathane wamusa entabeni ephakemeyo kakhulu, wamtshengisa yonke imibuso yomhlaba lokucwebezela kwayo. <verse eid="MAT 4:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 4:9"/>Wathi, “Ngizakunika konke lokhu nxa ungangikhothamela, ungikhonze.”<verse eid="MAT 4:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 4:10"/>UJesu wathi kuye, <char style="wj">“Suka kimi Sathane! Ngoba kulotshiwe ukuthi: ‘Khonza iNkosi uNkulunkulu wakho njalo usebenzele yena yedwa.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 6.13</char></note><char style="wj">”</char><verse eid="MAT 4:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 4:11"/>USathane wasemtshiya, izingilosi zabuya zazomkhonza.<verse eid="MAT 4:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uqalisa Ukutshumayela</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 4:12"/>UJesu wathi esizwa ukuthi uJohane wayesevalelwe entolongweni, wabuyela eGalile. <verse eid="MAT 4:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 4:13"/>Wasuka eNazaretha wayahlala eKhaphenawume eyayisokhunjini lomfula emangweni wakoZebhuluni lakoNafithali, <verse eid="MAT 4:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 4:14"/>ukugcwalisa lokho okwatshiwo ngomphrofethi u-Isaya ukuthi:<verse eid="MAT 4:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 4:15"/>“Lizwe likaZebhuluni lelizwe likaNafithali,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 4:15">iNdlela eya oLwandle, phetsheya kweJodani,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 4:15">iGalile yabeZizweni,<verse eid="MAT 4:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 4:16"/>abantu ababehlezi emnyameni</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 4:16">sebebone ukukhanya okukhulu;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 4:16">kulabo abahlezi elizweni lethunzi lokufa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 4:16">ukukhanya sekufikile.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.16 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 9.1-2</char></note><verse eid="MAT 4:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 4:17"/>Kusukela ngalesosikhathi uJesu waqalisa ukutshumayela esithi, <char style="wj">“Phendukani ngoba umbuso wezulu ususondele.”</char><verse eid="MAT 4:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubizwa Kwabafundi Bakuqala</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 4:18"/>Kwathi uJesu ehamba okhunjini loLwandle lwaseGalile wabona izelamani ezimbili, uSimoni owayethiwa nguPhethro lomfowabo u-Andreya. Babephosela umambule olwandle ngoba bengabagoli benhlanzi. <verse eid="MAT 4:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 4:19"/>UJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Wozani lingilandele,</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4.19 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UJesu ebabiza ukuthi bamlandele, wayebabizela ukuthi bazidele, balingise impilo yakhe.</char></note> <char style="wj">ngizalenza abagoli babantu.”</char> <verse eid="MAT 4:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 4:20"/>Masinyane nje batshiya omambule babo bamlandela.<verse eid="MAT 4:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 4:21"/>Esuka lapho wabona ezinye izelamani ezimbili, uJakhobe indodana kaZebhediya lomfowabo uJohane. Babephakathi kwesikepe loyise uZebhediya, belungisa omambule babo. UJesu wababiza, <verse eid="MAT 4:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 4:22"/>baphanga batshiya isikepe kanye loyise bamlandela.<verse eid="MAT 4:22"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Usilisa Abagulayo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 4:23"/>UJesu wahamba kulolonke iGalile efundisa emasinagogweni abo, etshumayela izindaba ezinhle zombuso, esilisa zonke izifo lemikhuhlane ebantwini. <verse eid="MAT 4:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 4:24"/>Udumo lwakhe lwagcwala kulolonke elase-Asiriya, abantu baletha kuye bonke ababegula belezifo ezehlukeneyo, labo ababesebuhlungwini obukhulu, ababephethwe ngamadimoni, ababelezithuthwane lababeyizilima, bonke wabasilisa. <verse eid="MAT 4:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 4:25"/>Amaxuku amakhulu ayevela eGalile, eDekhapholisi, eJerusalema, eJudiya lasemangweni ongaphetsheya kweJodani amlandela.<verse eid="MAT 4:25"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 4"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" sid="MAT 5"/>
  <para style="s1">Intshumayelo Yasentabeni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 5:1"/>Kwathi ebona amaxuku wakhwela entabeni wahlala phansi. Abafundi bakhe beza kuye.<verse eid="MAT 5:1"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Izibusiso</para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 5:2"/>Waseqalisa ukubafundisa esithi:<verse eid="MAT 5:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 5:3"/>
    <char style="wj">“Babusisiwe abampofu emoyeni</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 5:3">
    <char style="wj">ngoba umbuso wezulu ungowabo.</char><verse eid="MAT 5:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 5:4"/>
    <char style="wj">Babusisiwe labo abakhalayo</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 5:4">
    <char style="wj">ngoba bazakududuzwa.</char><verse eid="MAT 5:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 5:5"/>
    <char style="wj">Babusisiwe abathobekileyo</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 5:5">
    <char style="wj">ngoba bazakuba zindlalifa zomhlaba.</char><verse eid="MAT 5:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 5:6"/>
    <char style="wj">Babusisiwe labo abalambela labomela ukulunga</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 5:6">
    <char style="wj">ngoba bazakusuthiswa.</char><verse eid="MAT 5:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 5:7"/>
    <char style="wj">Babusisiwe abalesihawu</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 5:7">
    <char style="wj">ngoba bazakuhawukelwa.</char><verse eid="MAT 5:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 5:8"/>
    <char style="wj">Babusisiwe abahlanzekileyo enhliziyweni</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 5:8">
    <char style="wj">ngoba bazabona uNkulunkulu.</char><verse eid="MAT 5:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 5:9"/>
    <char style="wj">Babusisiwe abagcina ukuthula</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 5:9">
    <char style="wj">ngoba bazathiwa ngamadodana kaNkulunkulu.</char><verse eid="MAT 5:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 5:10"/>
    <char style="wj">Babusisiwe abahlukunyezwayo ngenxa yokulunga,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 5:10">
    <char style="wj">ngoba umbuso wezulu ungowabo.</char><verse eid="MAT 5:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 5:11"/>
    <char style="wj">Libusisiwe lina nxa abantu belithuka, belihlukumeza njalo beligcona ngobubi bonke ngenxa yami.</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 5:12"/><char style="wj">Thokozani lijabule ngoba mkhulu umvuzo wenu ezulwini, njengoba bahlukunyezwa ngaleyondlela abaphrofethi ababephambi kwenu.”</char><verse eid="MAT 5:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Itswayi Lokukhanya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 5:13"/>
    <char style="wj">“Lina lilitswayi lomhlaba. Kodwa nxa itswayi lingalahlekelwa yibumunyu balo, lingavuselelwa njani na? Kaliselamsebenzi ngaphandle kokuthi lichithelwe phandle linyathelwe ngabantu.</char><verse eid="MAT 5:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 5:14"/>
    <char style="wj">Lina liyikukhanya kwezwe. Idolobho elakhelwe entabeni kalisitheki.</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 5:15"/><char style="wj">Njalo abantu kabalumathisi isibane basibeke ngaphansi kwesitsha. Kodwa basibeka phezu koluthi lwaso ukuze sikhanyisele bonke abasendlini.</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 5:16"/><char style="wj">Ngokunjalo, yenzani ukukhanya kwenu kukhanye phambi kwabantu ukuze babone izenzo zenu ezinhle baze badumise uYihlo osezulwini.”</char><verse eid="MAT 5:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukugcwalisa Umthetho</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 5:17"/>
    <char style="wj">“Lingacabangi ukuthi ngilande ukuzadiliza uMthetho kumbe abaPhrofethi. Kangilandanga ukuzediliza kodwa ukuzogcwalisisa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 5:18"/><char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi kuze kunyamalale izulu lomhlaba kakuyikususwa lutho eMthethweni, loba libadlana kumbe lichatshana elilotshiweyo, kuze kupheleliswe konke.</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 5:19"/><char style="wj">Loba ngubani owephula owodwa nje wale imilayo emincinyane, afundise abanye ukwenzanjalo uzathiwa mncinyane embusweni wezulu kodwa loba ngubani olandela njalo afundise imilayo le njengokuba, uzathiwa mkhulu embusweni wezulu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 5:20"/><char style="wj">Ngakho ngiyalitshela ukuthi ngaphandle kokuthi ukulunga kwenu kwedlule okwabaFarisi labafundisi bomthetho, ngempela kalizukuwungena umbuso wezulu.”</char><verse eid="MAT 5:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubulala Umuntu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 5:21"/>
    <char style="wj">“Lezwa ukuthi kwathiwa kwabasendulo, ‘Ungabulali; lowo obulalayo uzakwahlulelwa.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">5.21 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 20.13</char>
    </note> <verse eid="MAT 5:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 5:22"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ngilitshela ngithi loba ngubani ozondela umfowabo loba udadewabo uzakwahlulelwa emthethwandaba. Njalo lowo othi kumfowabo loba kudadewabo, ‘<char style="tl">Raca</char>,’ okutsho ukuthi ‘Silimandini,’ uzathonisiswa emphakathini. Njalo lowo othi, ‘Wena siwula!’ uzakuba sengozini yomlilo wesihogo.</char><verse eid="MAT 5:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 5:23"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngakho-ke, nxa uletha isipho sakho e-alithareni ubusukhumbula ukuthi umfowenu kumbe udadewenu ulesikhwili lawe,</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 5:24"/><char style="wj">tshiya khonapho isipho sakho phambi kwe-alithari. Qala uyebuyisana laye umfowenu kumbe udadewenu andubana ubuye uzonikela umnikelo wakho.</char><verse eid="MAT 5:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 5:25"/>
    <char style="wj">Phangisa uqedelane lalowo okumangalelayo lisahamba lisiya emthethwandaba funa akunikele kumahluleli ozakunikela kumlindijele ukuthi akuphosele entolongweni.</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 5:26"/><char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso, kawusoze uphume uze uhlawule kanye lohlamvana lokucina lwemali.”</char><verse eid="MAT 5:26"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuphinga</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 5:27"/>
    <char style="wj">“Lezwa ukuthi kwathiwa, ‘Ungaphingi.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">5.27 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 20.14</char>
    </note> <verse eid="MAT 5:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 5:28"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ngilitshela ukuthi lowo okhangela owesifazane amfise usephinge laye enhliziyweni yakhe.</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 5:29"/><char style="wj">Nxa ilihlo lakho lokunene likwenzisa isono, likopole, ulikhuphe ulilahlele khatshana. Kungcono kuwe ukuthi ulahlekelwe ngesisodwa isitho somzimba wakho kulokuthi umzimba wakho wonke uphoselwe esihogweni somlilo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 5:30"/><char style="wj">Njalo nxa isandla sakho sokunene sikwenzisa isono, siqume usiphosele khatshana. Kungcono kuwe ukuthi ulahlekelwe ngesisodwa isitho somzimba wakho kulokuthi umzimba wakho wonke uye esihogweni somlilo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 5:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukwehlukana</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 5:31"/>
    <char style="wj">“Kwathiwa, ‘Lowo owehlukana lomkakhe kamuphe incwadi yokuquma umtshado.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">5.31 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 24.1</char>
    </note> <verse eid="MAT 5:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 5:32"/><char style="wj">Kodwa mina ngilitshela ngithi lowo ohlukana lomkakhe, ngaphandle kokuba ehlobongile, umenza afebe, njalo lowo othatha umfazi ohlukene lomkakhe uyaphinga.”</char><verse eid="MAT 5:32"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Izifungo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 5:33"/>
    <char style="wj">“Njalo selezwa ukuthi kwathiwa kwabendulo, ‘Ungephuli isifungo sakho kodwa gcwalisa izifungo zakho ozenzileyo eNkosini.’</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 5:34"/><char style="wj">Kodwa mina ngithi, lingafungi loba sokutheni, kumbe ngezulu ngoba liyisihlalo sobukhosi sikaNkulunkulu;</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MAT 5:35"/><char style="wj">loba ngomhlaba ngoba uyisinyathelo sakhe loba ngeJerusalema ngoba lidolobho leNkosi enkulu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MAT 5:36"/><char style="wj">Njalo ungafungi ngekhanda lakho ngoba ungeke wenze lalunye unwele lube mhlophe kumbe lube mnyama.</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MAT 5:37"/><char style="wj">Okumele likutsho yikuthi ‘Yebo’ kumbe ‘Hatshi’; okunye okungasilokhu kuvela komubi.”</char><verse eid="MAT 5:37"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ilihlo Ngelihlo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="MAT 5:38"/>
    <char style="wj">“Selezwa ukuthi kwathiwa, ‘Ilihlo ngelihlo njalo izinyo ngezinyo.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">5.38 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 21.24; ULevi 24.20; UDutheronomi 19.21</char>
    </note> <verse eid="MAT 5:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MAT 5:39"/><char style="wj">Kodwa mina ngiyalitshela ngithi, lingamelani lomuntu omubi. Nxa omunye angakutshaya esihlathini sokunene, muphe njalo esinye isihlathi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MAT 5:40"/><char style="wj">Njalo nxa omunye efuna ukukumangalela ukuze akuthathele isigqoko sakho, myekele athathe lejazi lakho njalo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="MAT 5:41"/><char style="wj">Nxa omunye ekubamba ngamandla ukuthi uhambe ikhilomitha elilodwa, hamba laye abe mabili.</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MAT 5:42"/><char style="wj">Muphe lowo ocela kuwe njalo ungamfulatheli lowo ofuna ukweboleka kuwe.”</char><verse eid="MAT 5:42"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuthanda Izitha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="MAT 5:43"/>
    <char style="wj">“Selezwa ukuthi kwathiwa, ‘Thanda umakhelwane wakho, uzonde isitha sakho.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">5.43 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">ULevi 19.18</char>
    </note> <verse eid="MAT 5:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="MAT 5:44"/><char style="wj">Kodwa mina ngilitshela ukuthi, thandani izitha zenu, libakhulekele labo abalihlukuluzayo,</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="MAT 5:45"/><char style="wj">ukuze libe ngamadodana kaYihlo osezulwini. Wenza ilanga lakhe liphume kwababi labalungileyo njalo anise izulu kwabalungileyo lakwabangalunganga.</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="MAT 5:46"/><char style="wj">Nxa lithanda labo abalithandayo kuphela, lizazuza mvuzo bani na? Kabenzi njalo na labathelisi?</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="MAT 5:47"/><char style="wj">Nxa libingelela abafowenu bodwa, kuyini elikwenzayo okwedlula abanye na? Kabenzi lokho labahedeni na?</char> <verse eid="MAT 5:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="MAT 5:48"/><char style="wj">Ngakho wobani ngabapheleleyo njengalokhu uYihlo osezulwini ephelele.”</char><verse eid="MAT 5:48"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 5"/>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" sid="MAT 6"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukupha Abaswelayo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 6:1"/>
    <char style="wj">“Qaphelani ukuthi lingenzi izenzo zokulunga phambi kwabantu ukuze balibone. Nxa lisenza njalo kaliyikuba lomvuzo ovela kuYihlo ezulwini.</char><verse eid="MAT 6:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 6:2"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngakho nxa lisipha abaswelayo, lingamemezeli indawo yonke njengokwenziwa ngabazenzisi emasinagogweni lasezitaladini ukuze badunyiswe ngabantu. Ngilitshela iqiniso, sebewemukele owabo umvuzo ngokugcweleyo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 6:3"/><char style="wj">Kodwa nxa lina lisipha abaswelayo isandla senu sokhohlo kasingakwazi lokho esikwenzayo esokunene,</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 6:4"/><char style="wj">ukuze ukupha kwenu kube sensitha. Ngakho uYihlo obona okwenziwa ensitha uzalipha umvuzo wenu.”</char><verse eid="MAT 6:4"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umkhuleko</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 6:5"/>
    <char style="wj">“Nxa likhuleka lingabi njengabazenzisi ngoba bona bathanda ukukhuleka bemi emasinagogweni lasemakhoneni ezitalada ukuze babonwe ngabantu. Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi sebewutholile owabo umvuzo ngokugcweleyo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 6:6"/><char style="wj">Nxa likhuleka, ngenani ezindlini zenu, livale iminyango beselikhuleka kuYihlo ongabonakaliyo. Ngakho uYihlo obona okwenziwa ensitha uzalipha umvuzo wenu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 6:7"/><char style="wj">Njalo nxa likhuleka lingenzi ubugabazi, linqongoloza njengabahedeni ngoba bacabanga ukuthi bazezwakala ngenxa yamazwi abo amanengi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 6:8"/><char style="wj">Lingabi njengabo ngoba uYihlo uyakwazi elikuswelayo loba lingakakuceli kuye.”</char><verse eid="MAT 6:8"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umkhuleko WeNkosi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 6:9"/>
    <char style="wj">“Kumele likhuleke kanje:</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 6:9">
    <char style="wj">‘Baba wethu osezulwini,</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 6:9">
    <char style="wj">kalidunyiswe ibizo lakho,</char><verse eid="MAT 6:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 6:10"/>
    <char style="wj">umbuso wakho kawuze,</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 6:10">
    <char style="wj">intando yakho kayenziwe emhlabeni</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 6:10">
    <char style="wj">njengalokhu isenziwa ezulwini.</char><verse eid="MAT 6:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 6:11"/>
    <char style="wj">Siphe lamuhla isinkwa sethu sansukuzonke.</char><verse eid="MAT 6:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 6:12"/>
    <char style="wj">Njalo usithethelele izono zethu,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 6:12">
    <char style="wj">njengoba lathi sibathethelela abasonelayo.</char><verse eid="MAT 6:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 6:13"/>
    <char style="wj">Njalo ungasingenisi ekulingweni,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 6:13">
    <char style="wj">kodwa usisindise komubi.’</char><verse eid="MAT 6:13"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 6:14"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngoba nxa libathethelela abayabe belonile, uYihlo osezulwini laye uzalithethelela.</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 6:15"/><char style="wj">Kodwa nxa lingabathetheleli abantu izono zabo, uYihlo kayikulithethelela lani izono zenu.”</char><verse eid="MAT 6:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuzila Ukudla</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 6:16"/>
    <char style="wj">“Lapho lizila ukudla, lingabonakali linyukubele njengalokhu okwenziwa ngabazenzisi ngoba bakhangeleka bedanile ebusweni babo ukuze abantu babone ukuthi bazilile. Ngilitshela iqiniso ngithi sebewutholile owabo umvuzo ngokugcweleyo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 6:17"/><char style="wj">Kodwa lina nxa lizila, gcobani amafutha emakhanda enu, ligeze ubuso benu,</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 6:18"/><char style="wj">ukuze kungabonakali ebantwini ukuthi lizilile, kodwa kuYihlo kuphela ongabonakaliyo njalo yena obona okwenziwa ensitha uzalipha umvuzo wenu.”</char><verse eid="MAT 6:18"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Inotho Ezulwini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 6:19"/>
    <char style="wj">“Lingazibutheleli inotho emhlabeni lapho okubhubhisa khona inondo lokuthomba njalo lapho okugqekeza khona amasela.</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 6:20"/><char style="wj">Kodwa zibutheleleni inotho ezulwini lapho kungabhujiswa khona linondo lokuthomba njalo lapho okungagqekezi khona amasela.</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 6:21"/><char style="wj">Ngoba lapho okulenotho yakho khona kulapho inhliziyo yakho ezakuba khona.</char><verse eid="MAT 6:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 6:22"/>
    <char style="wj">Ilihlo liyisibane somzimba. Nxa amehlo akho elungile umzimba wakho wonke uzagcwala ukukhanya.</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 6:23"/><char style="wj">Kodwa nxa amehlo akho engahlambulukanga umzimba wakho wonke uzagcwala ubumnyama. Nxa ukukhanya okungaphakathi kwakho kungumnyama, pho mkhulu kanganani lowomnyama!</char><verse eid="MAT 6:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 6:24"/>
    <char style="wj">Kakulanceku engakhonza amakhosi amabili. Funa izonde enye kodwa ithande enye, kumbe izinikele kwenye yeyise enye. Lingezake likhonze uNkulunkulu lemali.”</char><verse eid="MAT 6:24"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Linganqineki</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 6:25"/>
    <char style="wj">“Ngakho ngiyalitshela ukuthi lingakhathazeki ngokuphila kwenu, ukuthi lizakudlani loba lizanathani; kumbe ngemizimba yenu, ukuthi lizagqokani. Impilo kayiqakathekanga ukwedlula ukudla na, lomzimba ukwedlula izigqoko na?</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 6:26"/><char style="wj">Khangelani izinyoni zasemoyeni; kazihlanyeli, kazivuni kumbe ukubuthela eziphaleni kodwa uYihlo osezulwini uyazipha ukudla. Lina kaliqakathekanga ukwedlula zona na?</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 6:27"/><char style="wj">Ngubani kini othi ngokukhathazeka angezelele ihola elilodwa empilweni yakhe na?</char><verse eid="MAT 6:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 6:28"/>
    <char style="wj">Kanti lizihluphelani ngezigqoko na? Ake libone ukuthi amaluba eganga akhula njani. Kawasebenzi njalo aweluki.</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 6:29"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ngilitshela ukuthi laye uSolomoni ekucwebezeleni kwakhe kazange acece njengawo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 6:30"/><char style="wj">Nxa kuyiyo indlela uNkulunkulu ahlobisa ngayo utshani beganga, obukhona namuhla kodwa kusasa sebuphoselwa emlilweni, pho lina kazukuligqokisa ngcono yini, lina bokukholwa okuncinyane?</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 6:31"/><char style="wj">Ngakho lingazihluphi lisithi, ‘Sizakudlani?’ kumbe ‘Sizanathani?’ loba ‘Sizavunulani na?’</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 6:32"/><char style="wj">Ngoba abezizweni bagijimela zonke lezizinto kodwa uYihlo osezulwini uyakwazi ukuthi liyazidinga.</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 6:33"/><char style="wj">Kodwa funani kuqala umbuso wakhe lokulunga kwakhe, kuzakuthi-ke zonke lezizinto liziphiwe lazo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 6:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 6:34"/><char style="wj">Ngakho lingazihluphi ngelakusasa ngoba ikusasa lizazinqinekela lona. Usuku lunye ngalunye lulenhlupho zalo oluzaneleyo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 6:34"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 6"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" sid="MAT 7"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukwahlulela Abanye</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 7:1"/>
    <char style="wj">“Lingahluleli funa lani lahlulelwe.</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 7:2"/><char style="wj">Ngoba ngaleyondlela elahlulela ngayo abanye lani lizakwahlulelwa ngayo, langalesosilinganiso elisisebenzisayo lani lizalinganiselwa ngaso.</char><verse eid="MAT 7:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 7:3"/>
    <char style="wj">Kungani ukhangela uvava lokhuni oluselihlweni lomfowenu unganqinekeli ukhuni olukwelakho ilihlo na?</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 7:4"/><char style="wj">Ungatsho kanjani kumfowenu ukuthi, ‘Wothi ngikukhuphe uvava oluselihlweni lakho,’ wena ulokhu ulokhuni kwelakho ilihlo?</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 7:5"/><char style="wj">Wena mzenzisi, qala ukhuphe ukhuni oluselihlweni lakho ukuze ubone kuhle nxa usukhupha uvava oluselihlweni lomfowenu.</char><verse eid="MAT 7:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 7:6"/>
    <char style="wj">Linganiki izinja okungcwele, lingaphoseli imiceciso ezingulubeni, ngoba lingakwenza lokhu zizayinyathela ngezinyawo ziphinde ziphenduke ziyidabudabule.”</char><verse eid="MAT 7:6"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Celani, Dingani, Qoqodani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 7:7"/>
    <char style="wj">“Celani lizaphiwa; dingani lizafumana; qoqodani lizavulelwa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 7:8"/><char style="wj">Ngoba wonke ocelayo uyaphiwa; odingayo uyafumana; lalowo oqoqodayo uzavulelwa umnyango.</char><verse eid="MAT 7:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 7:9"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngubani kini bobaba okuthi nxa indodana yakhe icela isinkwa ayiphe ilitshe na?</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 7:10"/><char style="wj">Loba ithi icela inhlanzi yena ayiphe inyoka?</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 7:11"/><char style="wj">Nxa lina elibabi likwazi ukupha abantwabenu izipho ezilungileyo, pho uYihlo osezulwini uzabapha kangakanani izipho ezinhle labo abacela kuye!</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 7:12"/><char style="wj">Kuzozonke izinto, yenzani kwabanye lokho elifuna bakwenze kini, ngoba lokhu yikho okugoqela uMthetho labaPhrofethi.”</char><verse eid="MAT 7:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amasango Anciphileyo Labanzi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 7:13"/>
    <char style="wj">“Ngenani ngesango elincinyane ngoba isango elikhulu lendlela ebanzi iholela ekubhujisweni njalo abanengi bangena ngalo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 7:14"/><char style="wj">Kodwa isango elincinyane lendlela yalo encinyane iholela ekuphileni, njalo balutshwana abayifumanayo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 7:14"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isihlahla Lezithelo Zaso</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 7:15"/>
    <char style="wj">“Qaphelani abaphrofethi bamanga abeza kini bezigqokise isikhumba semvu kodwa ngaphakathi bezimpisi ezifohlozayo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 7:16"/><char style="wj">Lizabazi ngezithelo zabo. Abantu bayawakha na amavini esihlahleni sameva kumbe amakhiwane edolofiyeni na?</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 7:17"/><char style="wj">Kanjalo-ke, sonke isihlahla esihle sithela izithelo ezinhle kodwa isihlahla esibi sithela ezimbi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 7:18"/><char style="wj">Isihlahla esihle ngeke sithele izithelo ezimbi njalo lesihlahla esibi kasingethele izithelo ezinhle.</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 7:19"/><char style="wj">Zonke izihlahla ezingatheli izithelo ezinhle ziyaganyulwa ziphoselwe emlilweni.</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 7:20"/><char style="wj">Ngakho-ke, lizabazi ngezithelo zabo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 7:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Abafundi Bamanga Labeqiniso</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 7:21"/>
    <char style="wj">“Kakusibo bonke abathi kimi, ‘Nkosi, Nkosi’ abazangena embusweni wezulu, kodwa ngulowo kuphela owenza intando kaBaba osezulwini.</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 7:22"/><char style="wj">Abanengi bazakuthi kimi ngalolosuku, ‘Nkosi, Nkosi, kasiphrofithanga ngebizo lakho, njalo ngebizo lakho sakhupha amadimoni, senza lezimangaliso na?’</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 7:23"/><char style="wj">Lapho-ke, ngizabatshela kakuhle ngithi, ‘Ngivele kangilazi. Sudulukani kimi, lina benzi bobubi!’ ”</char><verse eid="MAT 7:23"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umakhi Ohlakaniphileyo Loyisiwula</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 7:24"/>
    <char style="wj">“Ngakho lowo owezwayo amazwi ami la awenze unjengendoda ehlakaniphileyo eyakhela indlu yayo edwaleni.</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 7:25"/><char style="wj">Latheleka izulu, izifula zagcwala, wavunguza umoya watshaya phezu kwaleyondlu; kodwa kayiwanga ngoba yayigxiliswe isisekelo sayo edwaleni.</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 7:26"/><char style="wj">Kodwa lowo owezwayo amazwi ami la angawenzi unjengendoda eyisiwula eyakhela indlu yayo etshebetshebeni.</char> <verse eid="MAT 7:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 7:27"/><char style="wj">Latheleka izulu, izifula zagcwala, umoya wavunguza watshaya phezu kwendlu leyo yawa yabhidlika.”</char><verse eid="MAT 7:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 7:28"/>UJesu eseqedile ukukhuluma lezizinto, amaxuku abantu amangaliswa yikufundisa kwakhe, <verse eid="MAT 7:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 7:29"/>ngoba wafundisa njengomuntu olamandla, hatshi njengabafundisi babo bomthetho.<verse eid="MAT 7:29"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 7"/>
  <chapter number="8" style="c" sid="MAT 8"/>
  <para style="s1">Indoda Eyayilobulephero</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 8:1"/>Kwathi esehlile entabeni amaxuku abantu amlandela. <verse eid="MAT 8:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 8:2"/>Indoda eyayilobulephero yeza yaguqa phambi kwakhe yathi, “Nkosi nxa uthanda ungangenza ngihlambuluke.”<verse eid="MAT 8:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 8:3"/>UJesu welula isandla sakhe wayithinta wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngiyathanda, hlambuluka!”</char> Masinyane nje yasila ebulepherweni bayo. <verse eid="MAT 8:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 8:4"/>UJesu wasesithi kuyo, <char style="wj">“Zwana, ungatsheli muntu ngalokhu. Kodwa hamba uyeziveza kumphristi, unikele ngesipho esamiswa nguMosi njengobufakazi ebantwini.”</char><verse eid="MAT 8:4"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukholo LweNduna YeKhulu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 8:5"/>UJesu esengenile eKhaphenawume, kwafika kuye induna yekhulu izocela uncedo. <verse eid="MAT 8:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 8:6"/>Yathi, “Nkosi, inceku yami ilele phansi endlini, yome umhlubulo, isebuhlungwini obukhulu.”<verse eid="MAT 8:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 8:7"/>UJesu wathi kuyo, <char style="wj">“Ngizakuza ngizeyisilisa.”</char><verse eid="MAT 8:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 8:8"/>Induna yekhulu yaphendula yathi, “Kakungilingananga ukuthi ungeza ungene ngaphansi kophahla lwami. Kodwa tshono ilizwi nje kuphela, inceku yami izasila. <verse eid="MAT 8:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 8:9"/>Ngoba mina ngokwami ngingumuntu ongaphansi komthetho, ngilamabutho angaphansi kwami. Lo ngimtshela ngithi, ‘Hamba,’ ahambe; ngithi kuloyana, ‘Buya,’ lakanye abuye. Ngithi encekwini yami, ‘Yenza lokhu,’ ikwenze.”<verse eid="MAT 8:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 8:10"/>UJesu wathi ekuzwa lokhu wamangala wathi kulabo ababemlandela, <char style="wj">“Ngilitshela iqiniso, kangikamboni loyedwa ko-Israyeli olokukholwa okukhulu kangaka.</char> <verse eid="MAT 8:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 8:11"/><char style="wj">Ngithi kini abanengi bazavela empumalanga lentshonalanga, bahlale edilini lo-Abhrahama, lo-Isaka loJakhobe embusweni wezulu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 8:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 8:12"/><char style="wj">Kodwa abanini bombuso bazaxotshelwa phandle emnyameni lapho okuzakuba khona ukukhala lokugedla kwamazinyo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 8:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 8:13"/>UJesu wasesithi enduneni yekhulu, <char style="wj">“Hamba! Kuzakwenziwa njengalokhu ukholwa ukuthi kuzakwenziwa.”</char> Inceku yayo yahle yasila ngalesosikhathi.<verse eid="MAT 8:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Usilisa Abanengi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 8:14"/>Kwathi lapho uJesu esengenile endlini kaPhethro, wabona uninazala kaPhethro elele embhedeni ephethwe ngumkhuhlane woqhuqho. <verse eid="MAT 8:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 8:15"/>Wamthinta esandleni umkhuhlane wahle waphuma kuye, wavuka waqala ukumphakela.<verse eid="MAT 8:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 8:16"/>Sekuntambama abanengi ababelamadimoni balethwa kuye wayikhupha imimoya ngelizwi njalo wasilisa bonke abagulayo. <verse eid="MAT 8:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 8:17"/>Lokhu kwakugcwalisa okwakhulunywa ngomphrofethi u-Isaya ukuthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 8:17">“Wathatha ubuthakathaka bethu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 8:17">wathwala izifo zethu.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">8.17 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 53.4</char></note><verse eid="MAT 8:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ubunzima Bokulandela UJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 8:18"/>Wathi uJesu ebona amaxuku abantu abanengi bembuthanele, wathi akuchaphelwe ngaphetsheya ngakuleliyana icele lechibi. <verse eid="MAT 8:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 8:19"/>Kwasekusiza kuye umfundisi womthetho wathi, “Mfundisi, ngizakulandela ungaze uye ngaphi.”<verse eid="MAT 8:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 8:20"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Amakhanka alemilindi lezinyoni zemoyeni zilezidleke, kodwa iNdodana yoMuntu kayilandawo yokufihla ikhanda layo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 8:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 8:21"/>Omunye umfundi wathi kuye, “Nkosi, akuthi ngiqale ngihambe ngiyengcwaba ubaba.”<verse eid="MAT 8:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 8:22"/>Kodwa uJesu wamtshela wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngilandela, uyekele abafileyo bangcwabe abafileyo babo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 8:22"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uthulisa Isiphepho</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 8:23"/>UJesu wasengena esikepeni abafundi bakhe bamlandela. <verse eid="MAT 8:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 8:24"/>Masinyane nje kwaphakama isiphepho esesabekayo echibini, amagagasi atshaya phezu kwesikepe. Kodwa uJesu wayelele. <verse eid="MAT 8:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 8:25"/>Abafundi bahamba bayamvusa besithi, “Nkosi, sihlenge, Sesigalula!”<verse eid="MAT 8:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 8:26"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Lina bokukholwa okuncinyane, kungani lisesaba kangaka?”</char> Wasephakama wawukhuza umoya kanye lamagagasi, kwasekuthula cwaka.<verse eid="MAT 8:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 8:27"/>Amadoda amangala abuza athi, “Ngumuntu bani lo? Oze alalelwe ngumoya kanye lamagagasi!”<verse eid="MAT 8:27"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukusiliswa Kwamadoda Amabili Alamadimoni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 8:28"/>Wathi ekufikeni kwakhe ngakwelinye icele emangweni wamaGadarini wahlangabezwa ngamadoda amabili ayelamadimoni eqhamuka emathuneni. Ayelodlakela, kungasadluli muntu ngaleyondlela. <verse eid="MAT 8:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 8:29"/>Amemeza athi, “Ufunani kithi, Ndodana kaNkulunkulu? Uze lapha ukuzasihlupha singakafiki isikhathi esimisiweyo na?”<verse eid="MAT 8:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 8:30"/>Bucwala kwawo umhlambi omkhulu wengulube wawusidla. <verse eid="MAT 8:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 8:31"/>Amadimoni amncenga uJesu athi, “Nxa usikhupha, sithumele emhlambini wengulube.”<verse eid="MAT 8:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 8:32"/>Wathi kuwo, <char style="wj">“Hambani!”</char> Aphuma ayangena engulubeni, umhlambi wonke waphaphatheka waqonda eliweni wangena echibini, wafela emanzini. <verse eid="MAT 8:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 8:33"/>Labo ababezelusile baphaphatheka baqonda edolobheni bayabika konke lokhu, besitsho lalokho okwenzakala kulawomadoda ayelamadimoni. <verse eid="MAT 8:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 8:34"/>Khonapho idolobho lonke laphuma ukuyahlangana loJesu. Bathi sebembonile bamncenga ukuba asuke emangweni wakibo.<verse eid="MAT 8:34"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 8"/>
  <chapter number="9" style="c" sid="MAT 9"/>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Usilisa Umuntu Owome Umhlubulo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 9:1"/>UJesu wangena esikepeni wachaphela ngasedolobheni lakibo. <verse eid="MAT 9:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 9:2"/>Amanye amadoda aletha kuye indoda eyayome umhlubulo ilele ecansini. UJesu ebona ukholo lwawo wathi kweyome umhlubulo, <char style="wj">“Woba lesibindi, ndodana; izono zakho sezithethelelwe.”</char><verse eid="MAT 9:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 9:3"/>Bekuzwa lokho abanye abafundisi bomthetho bahleba bodwa bathi, “Umuntu lo uyahlambaza!”<verse eid="MAT 9:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 9:4"/>Esazi imicabango yabo uJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Kungani licabanga izinto ezimbi ezinhliziyweni zenu na?</char> <verse eid="MAT 9:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 9:5"/><char style="wj">Yikuphi okulula ukuthi, ‘Izono zakho sezithethelelwe’ kumbe ukuthi, ‘Sukuma uhambe’?</char> <verse eid="MAT 9:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 9:6"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ngifuna lazi ukuthi iNdodana yoMuntu ilamandla okuthethelela izono emhlabeni.”</char> Wasesithi kweyome umhlubulo, <char style="wj">“Sukuma uthathe icansi lakho uhambe uye ekhaya.”</char> <verse eid="MAT 9:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 9:7"/>Indoda yasukuma yaqonda ekhaya. <verse eid="MAT 9:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 9:8"/>Ixuku labantu lathi likubona lokhu lesaba kakhulu; lamdumisa uNkulunkulu owayenike amandla la ebantwini.<verse eid="MAT 9:8"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubizwa KukaMatewu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 9:9"/>Kwathi uJesu eseqhubeka esuka lapho, wabona indoda eyayithiwa nguMatewu ihlezi endaweni yokuthelisa. UJesu wathi kuyo <char style="wj">“Ngilandela,”</char> uMatewu wahle wasukuma wamlandela.<verse eid="MAT 9:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 9:10"/>Kwathi uJesu esidla endlini kaMatewu kweza abathelisi abanengi lezoni bonke bezokudla laye kanye labafundi bakhe. <verse eid="MAT 9:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 9:11"/>Kuthe abaFarisi bekubona lokho babuza abafundi bakhe bathi, “Kungani umfundisi wenu esidla labathelisi lezoni na?”<verse eid="MAT 9:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 9:12"/>UJesu wakuzwa lokho wathi, <char style="wj">“Abaphilileyo kabayidingi inyanga kodwa idingwa ngabagulayo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 9:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 9:13"/><char style="wj">Kodwa hambani liyefunda ukuthi kutshoni lokhu ukuthi, ‘Ngoba ngifuna isihawu hatshi umhlatshelo.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">9.13 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UHosiya 6.6</char></note> <char style="wj">Ngoba kangilandanga ukubiza abalungileyo, kodwa izoni.”</char><verse eid="MAT 9:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ubuzwa Ngokuzila</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 9:14"/>Kwasekufika abafundi bakaJohane bambuza bathi, “Kungani thina labaFarisi sizila kodwa abafundi bakho kabazili?”<verse eid="MAT 9:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 9:15"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Izethekeli zomyeni zingalila kanjani esesekhona phakathi kwazo na? Sizafika isikhathi lapho umyeni ezasuswa kuzo; kulapho-ke ezizazila khona.</char><verse eid="MAT 9:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 9:16"/>
    <char style="wj">Kakho umuntu othungela isichibi selembu elitsha elingakafinyeli esigqokweni esidala, ngoba isichibi sizadonsa esigqokweni ukudabuka kuqhele ngamandla.</char> <verse eid="MAT 9:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 9:17"/><char style="wj">Futhi abantu kabatheli iwayini elitsha emigodleni emidala. Bangenzenjalo imigodla izadabuka, iwayini lichitheke lemigodla ihle iguge iphele. Kodwa, bathela iwayini elitsha emigodleni emitsha besekulondolozeka kuhle kokubili.”</char><verse eid="MAT 9:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Intombazana Efileyo Lomfazi Ogulayo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 9:18"/>Wathi esakhuluma lokhu kwafika umbusi waguqa phambi kwakhe wathi, “Indodakazi yami isanda kufa. Kodwa ngicela uzebeka isandla sakho phezu kwayo, izaphila.” <verse eid="MAT 9:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 9:19"/>UJesu wasuka wahamba laye kanye labafundi bakhe.<verse eid="MAT 9:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 9:20"/>Khonokho owesifazane owayehlutshwa ngumopho okweminyaka elitshumi lambili weza ngemva kwakhe wabamba umphetho wesembatho sakhe. <verse eid="MAT 9:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 9:21"/>Wazitshela wathi, “Nxa ngingathinta nje isembatho sakhe kodwa lokhu, ngizasila.”<verse eid="MAT 9:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 9:22"/>UJesu wanyemukula wambona. Wathi kuye, <char style="wj">“Mana isibindi ndodakazi, ukholo lwakho lukusilisile.”</char> Lakanye owesifazane lowo wasila ngalesosikhathi.<verse eid="MAT 9:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 9:23"/>UJesu wathi esengenile endlini yombusi wesinagogu wabona ababetshaya imihubhe kanye lexuku elalixokozela, <verse eid="MAT 9:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 9:24"/>wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Phumani. Intombazana kayifanga kodwa ilele.”</char> Kodwa bamhleka usulu. <verse eid="MAT 9:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 9:25"/>Ixuku labantu selikhutshelwe phandle, wangena wayibamba ngesandla intombazana yaphakama. <verse eid="MAT 9:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 9:26"/>Indaba yesehlakalo lesi yamemetheka kuwo wonke umango wakuleyondawo.<verse eid="MAT 9:26"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Usilisa Isiphofu Lesimungulu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 9:27"/>Kwathi uJesu esuka lapho amadoda ayiziphofu amabili amlandela ememeza esithi, “Sihawukele, Ndodana kaDavida!”<verse eid="MAT 9:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 9:28"/>Esengenile endlini iziphofu lezo zeza kuye wazibuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Liyakholwa na ukuthi ngingakwenza lokhu?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 9:28">Zamphendula zathi, “Yebo Nkosi.”<verse eid="MAT 9:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 9:29"/>Wasezithinta amehlo wathi kuzo, <char style="wj">“Kuzakwenziwa kini njengokukholwa kwenu”;</char> <verse eid="MAT 9:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 9:30"/>zasiliswa zabona. UJesu waziqonqosela wathi, <char style="wj">“Akungabi lomuntu ozakwazi ngalokhu.”</char> <verse eid="MAT 9:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 9:31"/>Kodwa zasuka lapho zafakaza ngaye indawo yonke yelizwe lelo.<verse eid="MAT 9:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 9:32"/>Ekuphumeni kwalezoziphofu, kwalethwa kuJesu indoda eyayiledimoni iyisimungulu. <verse eid="MAT 9:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 9:33"/>Kwathi idimoni selikhutshiwe indoda leyo eyayiyisimungulu yakhuluma. Ixuku labantu lamangala, abantu bathi, “Akukaze kubonakale okunje ko-Israyeli.”<verse eid="MAT 9:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 9:34"/>Kodwa abaFarisi bathi, “Amadimoni uwakhupha ngenkosi yamadimoni.”<verse eid="MAT 9:34"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Izisebenzi Zimbalwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MAT 9:35"/>UJesu wangena kuwo wonke amadolobho lemizi efundisa emasinagogweni abo, etshumayela izindaba ezinhle ezombuso njalo eselapha zonke izifo lemikhuhlane. <verse eid="MAT 9:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MAT 9:36"/>Wathi ebona amaxuku abantu wawazwela usizi ngoba ayehlukuluzekile njalo ephelelwe, enjengezimvu ezingelamelusi. <verse eid="MAT 9:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MAT 9:37"/>Wasesithi kubafundi bakhe, <char style="wj">“Isivuno sinengi kodwa izisebenzi zimbalwa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 9:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MAT 9:38"/><char style="wj">Ngakho celani iNkosi yokuvuna ukuba ithumele izisebenzi ensimini yokuvuna.”</char><verse eid="MAT 9:38"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 9"/>
  <chapter number="10" style="c" sid="MAT 10"/>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uthumela Abalitshumi Lambili</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 10:1"/>UJesu wabizela ndawonye abafundi bakhe abalitshumi lambili wabapha amandla okukhupha imimoya emibi lokusilisa zonke izifo lemikhuhlane.<verse eid="MAT 10:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 10:2"/>Amabizo abafundi abalitshumi lambili ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="MAT 10:2"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 10:2">Owokuqala wayenguSimoni, othiwa nguPhethro lomfowabo u-Andreya;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 10:2">uJakhobe indodana kaZebhediya loJohane umfowabo;<verse eid="MAT 10:2"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 10:3"/>uFiliphu, uBhatholomewu;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 10:3">uThomasi, uMatewu umthelisi;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="MAT 10:3">uJakhobe indodana ka-Alifewu, uLabhewu osibongo sakhe sasinguThediyasi;<verse eid="MAT 10:3"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 10:4"/>uSimoni umZilothi loJudasi Iskariyothi onguye owamnikelayo.<verse eid="MAT 10:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 10:5"/>Laba abalitshumi lambili uJesu wabathuma, wabalaya wathi, <char style="wj">“Lingayi phakathi kwabeZizwe futhi lingangeni lakuliphi idolobho lamaSamariya.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 10:6"/><char style="wj">Kodwa hambani liyebutha izimvu ezilahlekileyo zako-Israyeli.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 10:7"/><char style="wj">Ekuhambeni kwenu, litshumayele lelilizwi: ‘Umbuso wezulu ususondele.’</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 10:8"/><char style="wj">Silisani abagulayo, livuse abafileyo, lihlambulule abalobulephero, likhuphe amadimoni. Lamukelisiwe kungelambadalo ngakho lani phanini kungelambadalo.</char><verse eid="MAT 10:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 10:9"/>
    <char style="wj">Lingaphathi igolide loba isiliva loba ithusi emixhakeni yamabhanti enu;</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 10:10"/><char style="wj">lingathwali izikhwama ekuhambeni kwenu loba isigqoko sokuntshintsha, loba amanye amanyathela kumbe olunye udondolo ngoba osebenzayo kufanele aphiwe okokuziphilisa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 10:11"/><char style="wj">Loba yiliphi idolobho kumbe umuzi elingena kuwo, dingani umuntu ofaneleyo ukuba lihlale endlini yakhe kokuphela lize lisuke khona.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 10:12"/><char style="wj">Akuthi nxa lingena kulowomuzi, liwunxusele ukuthula.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 10:13"/><char style="wj">Nxa lowomuzi ufanele, ukuthula kwenu akube kuwo, kodwa nxa lingemukelwa aginyeni amazwi enu okuthula.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 10:14"/><char style="wj">Nxa engekho olamukelayo kumbe olalela amazwi enu, sukani kulowomuzi kumbe idolobho lithintithe uthuli ezinyaweni zenu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 10:15"/><char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi, kuzakuba ngcono elizweni leSodoma leGomora ngelanga lokwahlulelwa kulokuzakwehlela lelodolobho.</char><verse eid="MAT 10:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 10:16"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngilithuma linjengezimvu phakathi kwempisi. Ngakho qaphani njengezinyoka kodwa libemsulwa njengamajuba.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 10:17"/><char style="wj">Libalimuke abantu; bazalimangalela ezinkundleni zamacala, balibhaxabule emasinagogweni abo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 10:18"/><char style="wj">Ngenxa yami lizamiswa phambi kwababusi lamakhosi ukuze libe ngofakazi kubo lakwabeZizwe.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 10:19"/><char style="wj">Kodwa nxa belibopha lingazihluphi ngokuthi lizakuthini lokuthi likutsho kanjani. Ngalesosikhathi lizakwambulelwa okumele likutsho,</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 10:20"/><char style="wj">ngoba akuzukuba yini elikhulumayo kodwa kuzakuba nguMoya kaYihlo ozabe ukhuluma ngani.</char><verse eid="MAT 10:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 10:21"/>
    <char style="wj">Umuntu uzanikela umfowabo ukuthi abulawe, loyise anikele umntanakhe; abantwana bazahlamukela abazali babo bababulale.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 10:22"/><char style="wj">Bonke abantu bazalizonda ngenxa yebizo lami kodwa lowo oma aqine kuze kube sekupheleni uzasindiswa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 10:23"/><char style="wj">Nxa lihlukuluzwa endaweni ethile, balekelani kwenye. Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi kaliyikuqeda ukuwahambela wonke amadolobho ako-Israyeli iNdodana yoMuntu ingakafiki.</char><verse eid="MAT 10:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 10:24"/>
    <char style="wj">Umfundi ungaphansi kombalisi wakhe, lenceku ingaphansi kwenkosi yayo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 10:25"/><char style="wj">Kwenele kumfundi ukuba njengombalisi wakhe, lenceku ukuba njengenkosi yayo. Nxa umninimuzi kungathiwa nguBhelizebhubhi pho kuzathiwani ngabendlu yakhe na?</char><verse eid="MAT 10:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 10:26"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngakho lingabesabi. Ngoba kakukho okuthukuziweyo okungayi kubekwa obala, lokufihliweyo okungayikwaziwa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 10:27"/><char style="wj">Lokhu engilitshela khona emnyameni kukhulumeni ekukhanyeni kwemini, okunyenyezwa ezindlebeni zenu kumemezeleni lisophahleni lwezindlu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 10:28"/><char style="wj">Lingabesabi labo ababulala umzimba kodwa bengeke babulale umphefumulo. Kodwa yesabani lowo ongabhubhisa kokubili, umphefumulo lomzimba esihogweni.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 10:29"/><char style="wj">Intaka ezimbili kazithengiswa ngendibilitshi na? Kodwa kayikho leyodwa yazo ewela phansi ingavunyelwanga nguYihlo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 10:30"/><char style="wj">Kwala zona inwele zamakhanda enu zibaliwe.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 10:31"/><char style="wj">Ngakho lingesabi; liligugu elidlula intaka ezinengi.</char><verse eid="MAT 10:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 10:32"/>
    <char style="wj">Loba ngubani ongivuma phambi kwabantu lami ngizamvuma phambi kukaBaba ezulwini.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 10:33"/><char style="wj">Kodwa lowo ongiphikayo phambi kwabantu lami ngizamphika phambi kukaBaba ezulwini.</char><verse eid="MAT 10:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 10:34"/>
    <char style="wj">Lingakhumbuli ukuthi ngilethe ukuthula emhlabeni. Kangilandanga ukuzeletha ukuthula kodwa inkemba.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MAT 10:35"/><char style="wj">Ngoba ngize ukuxabanisa</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 10:35">
    <char style="wj">‘indoda loyise,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 10:35">
    <char style="wj">indodakazi lonina</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 10:35">
    <char style="wj">umalukazana loninazala,</char><verse eid="MAT 10:35"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="MAT 10:36"/>
    <char style="wj">izitha zomuntu zizakuba ngabendlu yakhe.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">10.36 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">UMikha 7.6</char>
    </note><verse eid="MAT 10:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="MAT 10:37"/>
    <char style="wj">Lowo othanda uyise loba unina kulami kangifanelanga; lowo othanda indodana yakhe loba indodakazi yakhe kulami kangifanelanga;</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MAT 10:38"/><char style="wj">njalo lowo ongathathi isiphambano sakhe angilandele kangifanelanga.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MAT 10:39"/><char style="wj">Loba ngubani ozuza impilo yakhe izamlahlekela njalo lalowo olahlekelwa yimpilo yakhe ngenxa yami uzayizuza.</char><verse eid="MAT 10:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="MAT 10:40"/>
    <char style="wj">Lowo olamukelayo wamukela mina, lalowo owamukela mina wamukela lowo ongithumileyo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="MAT 10:41"/><char style="wj">Loba ngubani owamukele umphrofethi ngoba engumphrofethi uzazuza umvuzo womphrofethi njalo lalowo owamukela umuntu olungileyo ngoba engumuntu olungileyo uzakwamukela umvuzo womuntu olungileyo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 10:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MAT 10:42"/><char style="wj">Njalo nxa ekhona onika iloba yinkezo yamanzi aqandayo komunye walaba abancinyane ongumfundi wami, ngilitshela iqiniso, lowomuntu akayikulahlekelwa ngumvuzo wakhe.”</char><verse eid="MAT 10:42"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 10"/>
  <chapter number="11" style="c" sid="MAT 11"/>
  <para style="s1">UJesu LoJohane UMbhaphathizi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 11:1"/>UJesu wathi eseqedile ukulaya abafundi bakhe abalitshumi lambili wasuka kuleyondawo ukuyafundisa lokutshumayela emadolobheni aseGalile.<verse eid="MAT 11:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 11:2"/>UJohane esentolongweni wathi esizwa ukuthi uKhristu wayesenzani, wathuma abafundi bakhe <verse eid="MAT 11:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 11:3"/>ukuba bayembuza bathi, “Unguye yini ozayo kumbe silindele omunye na?”<verse eid="MAT 11:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 11:4"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Buyelani liyebikela uJohane lokhu elikuzwayo lelikubonayo ukuthi</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 11:5"/><char style="wj">Iziphofu zenziwa zibone, abaqhugezelayo bayahamba, abalobulephero bayahlanjululwa, izacuthe ziyezwa, abafileyo bayavuswa, levangeli liyatshunyayelwa kubayanga.</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 11:6"/><char style="wj">Ubusisiwe umuntu ongakhubekiyo ngenxa yami.”</char><verse eid="MAT 11:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 11:7"/>Kwathi abafundi bakaJohane sebesuka, uJesu waqala ukukhuluma labantu ngoJohane esithi: <char style="wj">“Laphuma lisiyabonani enkangala na? Umhlanga owazunguzwa ngumoya na?</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 11:8"/><char style="wj">Nxa kungayisikho, pho lalisiyabonani? Indoda eyayicecile na? Hatshi, labo abagqoka izigqoko ezinhle basezigodlweni zamakhosi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 11:9"/><char style="wj">Pho laphuma lisiyabonani na? Umphrofethi? Yebo, ngiyalitshela, odlula umphrofethi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 11:10"/><char style="wj">Lo nguye okulotshwe ngaye ukuthi:</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 11:10">
    <char style="wj">‘Ngizathuma isithunywa sami phambi kwakho,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 11:10">
    <char style="wj">esizalungisa indlela yakho phambi kwakho.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">11.10 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">UMalaki 3.1</char>
    </note><verse eid="MAT 11:10"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 11:11"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi, phakathi kwabo bonke abazelwe ngabesifazane akukaveli loyedwa omkhulu kuloJohane uMbhaphathizi ikanti lowo ongomncinyane kakhulu embusweni wezulu mkhulu kulaye.</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 11:12"/><char style="wj">Kusukela ensukwini zikaJohane uMbhaphathizi kuze kube khathesi, umbuso wezulu wala uqhubeka ngamandla ngoba abantu abalamandla bawubambile.</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 11:13"/><char style="wj">Ngoba bonke abaPhrofethi kanye loMthetho baphrofitha kwaze kwafika uJohane.</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 11:14"/><char style="wj">Ngakho nxa likwamukela lokhu, ungu-Elija okwathiwa uyeza.</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 11:15"/><char style="wj">Lowo olendlebe zokuzwa, kezwe.</char><verse eid="MAT 11:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 11:16"/>
    <char style="wj">Kambe ngingasifanisa lani isizukulwane lesi na? Banjengabantwana abahlezi emikambo bememeza abanye besithi:</char><verse eid="MAT 11:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 11:17"/>
    <char style="wj">‘Salitshayela umhubhe,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 11:17">
    <char style="wj">kodwa kaligidanga;</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 11:17">
    <char style="wj">salihlabelela ingoma yesililo</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 11:17">
    <char style="wj">kodwa kalililanga.’</char><verse eid="MAT 11:17"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 11:18"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngoba uJohane wafika engadli njalo enganathi basebesithi, ‘Uledimoni,’</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 11:19"/><char style="wj">INdodana yoMuntu yafika yadla, yanatha, bathi, ‘Nansi isidli lesidakwa, umngane wabathelisi lezoni.’ Kodwa, ukuhlakanipha kuziveza ukuthi kuqondile ngemisebenzi yakho.”</char><verse eid="MAT 11:19"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Maye Kuleyomizi Engaphendukanga</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 11:20"/>UJesu waseqalisa ukuwasola amadolobho lawo lapho izimangaliso zakhe ezinengi ezazenziwe khona ngoba kabazange baphenduke: <verse eid="MAT 11:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 11:21"/><char style="wj">“Maye kuwe Khorazini! Maye kuwe Bhethisayida! Aluba izimangaliso lezo ezenziwa kuwe zazenziwe eThire leSidoni, ngabe kudala baphenduka begqoke izigqoko zamasaka, bazibhuqa lemlotheni.</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 11:22"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ngiyalitshela, kuzakuba ngcono eThire leSidoni ngosuku lokwahlulelwa kulalokho okuzalehlela lina.</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 11:23"/><char style="wj">Lawe Khaphenawume, kambe uzaphakanyiselwa emazulwini na? Hatshi, uzatshona phansi uye eHadesi. Ngoba aluba izimangaliso ezenziwa kuwe zazenziwe eSodoma ngabe ikhona lanamuhla.</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 11:24"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ngiyalitshela ukuthi kuzakuba ngcono elizweni leSodoma ngelanga lokwahlulelwa kulakuwe.”</char><verse eid="MAT 11:24"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuphumula Kwabakhatheleyo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 11:25"/>Ngalesosikhathi uJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngiyakubonga Baba, Nkosi yezulu lomhlaba ngoba uzifihlile lezizinto kwabahlakaniphileyo labafundileyo, wazambulela abantwana abancinyane.</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 11:26"/><char style="wj">Yebo Baba, lokhu kwaba yikuthanda kwakho.</char><verse eid="MAT 11:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 11:27"/>
    <char style="wj">Zonke izinto zethulwe kimi nguBaba. Kakho oyaziyo iNdodana ngaphandle kukaBaba, njalo kakho omaziyo uBaba ngaphandle kweNdodana lalabo iNdodana ekhethe ukuba imveze kubo.</char><verse eid="MAT 11:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 11:28"/>
    <char style="wj">Wozani kimi lina lonke elikhatheleyo lelisindwayo, ngizaliphumuza.</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 11:29"/><char style="wj">Zithwaliseni ijogwe lami, lifunde kimi, ngoba ngimnene futhi ngithobekile enhliziyweni njalo lizazuza ukuphumula kwemiphefumulo yenu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 11:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 11:30"/><char style="wj">Ngoba ijogwe lami lilula, lomthwalo wami kawusindi.”</char><verse eid="MAT 11:30"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 11"/>
  <chapter number="12" style="c" sid="MAT 12"/>
  <para style="s1">INkosi YeSabatha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 12:1"/>Ngalesosikhathi uJesu wadabula phakathi kwamasimu amabele kulilanga leSabatha. Abafundi bakhe basebelambile, basebekhwebula izikhwebu zamabele badla. <verse eid="MAT 12:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 12:2"/>AbaFarisi bakubona lokhu, bathi kuye, “Khangela! Abafundi bakho benza okuphambene lomthetho ngeSabatha.”<verse eid="MAT 12:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 12:3"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kalifundanga yini okwenziwa nguDavida lapho yena labakhula bakhe sebelambile?</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 12:4"/><char style="wj">Wangena endlini kaNkulunkulu, yena labakhula bakhe, badla isinkwa esingcwelisiweyo, into eyayingavunyelwa ngomthetho ukuba bayenze, kodwa ivunyelwe abaphristi kuphela.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 12:5"/><char style="wj">Kumbe kalifundanga yini eMthethweni ukuthi ngeSabatha abaphristi ethempelini bayalungcolisa lolusuku kodwa kabalacala.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 12:6"/><char style="wj">Ngiyalitshela ukuthi lowo omkhulu kulethempeli ukhona lapha.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 12:7"/><char style="wj">Kube lalikwazile ukuthi amazwi la atshoni, ‘Ngifuna isihawu hatshi umhlatshelo’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12.7 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UHosiya 6.6</char></note> <char style="wj">belingasoze libalahle abangelacala.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 12:8"/><char style="wj">Phela iNdodana yoMuntu iyiNkosi yeSabatha.”</char><verse eid="MAT 12:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 12:9"/>Esuka lapho wayangena esinagogweni labo, <verse eid="MAT 12:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 12:10"/>khonapho kulendoda eyayitshwabhene isandla. Kwathi ngoba bedinga indlela yokubeka uJesu icala bambuza bathi, “Kuyavunyelwa emthethweni ukusilisa ngeSabatha na?”<verse eid="MAT 12:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 12:11"/>Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Nxa omunye wenu engaba lemvu esuka iwele egodini ngeSabatha, kazukuyibamba ayikhuphe na?</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 12:12"/><char style="wj">Pho umuntu uligugu elinganani kulemvu! Yikho-ke, kusemthethweni ukwenza okuhle ngeSabatha.”</char><verse eid="MAT 12:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 12:13"/>Wasesithi kuleyondoda, <char style="wj">“Yelula isandla sakho.”</char> Ngakho yaselula sahle sabuyela ngokupheleleyo, sesiqinile njengesinye. <verse eid="MAT 12:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 12:14"/>Kodwa abaFarisi basuka lapho bayakwakha icebo lokuthi bangambulala njani uJesu.<verse eid="MAT 12:14"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Inceku KaNkulunkulu Ekhethiweyo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 12:15"/>UJesu esekunanzelele lokho wasuka kuleyondawo. Abanengi bamlandela, wasilisa bonke abagulayo babo, <verse eid="MAT 12:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 12:16"/>ebalaya ukuthi bangakhulumi ukuthi ungubani. <verse eid="MAT 12:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 12:17"/>Lokhu kwakuyikugcwalisa lokho okwakukhulunywe ngumphrofethi u-Isaya ukuthi:<verse eid="MAT 12:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 12:18"/>“Nansi inceku yami engiyikhethileyo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 12:18">yona engiyithandayo, engithokoza ngayo;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 12:18">ngizabeka uMoya wami phezu kwayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 12:18">izamemezela ukulunga phakathi kwezizwe.<verse eid="MAT 12:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 12:19"/>Kayiyikuphika inkani loba imemeze;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 12:19">kakho ozalizwa ilizwi layo emigwaqweni.<verse eid="MAT 12:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 12:20"/>Umhlanga ofecekileyo kayiyikuwephula</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 12:20">lentambo yesibane ethunqayo kayiyikuyicima,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 12:20">ize ilethe ukunqoba kokulunga.<verse eid="MAT 12:20"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 12:21"/>Izizwe zizabeka ithemba lazo ebizweni layo.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">12.21 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 42.1-4</char></note><verse eid="MAT 12:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu LoBhelizebhubhi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 12:22"/>Basebeletha kuye indoda eyayiledimoni, iyisiphofu njalo iyisimungulu. UJesu wayisilisa yakwazi ukukhuluma lokubona. <verse eid="MAT 12:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 12:23"/>Bonke abantu bamangala bathi, “Kambe lo angabe eyiNdodana kaDavida na?”<verse eid="MAT 12:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 12:24"/>Kodwa kwathi abaFarisi bekuzwa lokhu bathi, “Ngamandla kaBhelizebhubhi inkosi yamadimoni amenza enelise ukuxotsha amadimoni.”<verse eid="MAT 12:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 12:25"/>UJesu wayeyazi imicabango yabo wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Loba yiwuphi umbuso odabuke phakathi kwawumi njalo idolobho kumbe indlu edabuke phakathi kayimi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 12:26"/><char style="wj">Nxa uSathane exotsha uSathane, wehlukene phakathi. Pho umbuso wakhe ungema kanjani?</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 12:27"/><char style="wj">Nxa ngikhupha amadimoni ngoBhelizebhubhi, pho abalandeli benu bawakhupha ngobani? Ngakho bazakuba ngabahluleli benu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 12:28"/><char style="wj">Kodwa nxa ngixotsha amadimoni ngoMoya kaNkulunkulu, kutsho ukuthi umbuso kaNkulunkulu usufikile kini.</char><verse eid="MAT 12:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 12:29"/>
    <char style="wj">Umuntu angangena kanjani endlini yesiqhwaga aphange impahla zaso ngaphandle kokuba aqale asibophe isiqhwaga leso? Lapho-ke usengayiphanga indlu yaso</char>.<verse eid="MAT 12:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 12:30"/>
    <char style="wj">Lowo ongemanga lami uphikisana lami, lalowo ongabuthi lami uyachithiza.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 12:31"/><char style="wj">Ngakho ngiyalitshela ngithi imihlobo yonke yezono lezithuko izathethelelwa, kodwa ukuthuka uMoya akuyi kuthethelelwa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 12:32"/><char style="wj">Lowo okhuluma okubi ngeNdodana yoMuntu uzathethelelwa kodwa lowo othuka uMoya oNgcwele akayikuthethelelwa kulesisikhathi kumbe esizayo.</char><verse eid="MAT 12:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 12:33"/>
    <char style="wj">Ungenza isihlahla sibe sihle lezithelo zaso zizakuba zinhle loba ungenza isihlahla sibe sibi lezithelo zaso zizakuba zimbi ngoba isihlahla saziwa ngezithelo zaso.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 12:34"/><char style="wj">Lina nzalo yezinyoka, lingakukhuluma kanjani okuhle lina libabi na? Ngoba lokho okusenhliziyweni yikho umlomo okukhulumayo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MAT 12:35"/><char style="wj">Umuntu olungileyo uveza izinto ezinhle azigcine ngaphakathi kwakhe njalo lomuntu omubi ukhihliza izinto ezimbi azigcine ngaphakathi kwakhe.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MAT 12:36"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ngiyalitshela ukuthi umuntu munye ngamunye uzaziphendulela ngosuku lokwahlulelwa ngawo wonke amazwi ayize awakhulumayo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MAT 12:37"/><char style="wj">Ngoba lizakhululwa ngamazwi enu njalo lizalahlwa ngamazwi enu.”</char><verse eid="MAT 12:37"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isibonakaliso SikaJona</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="MAT 12:38"/>Abanye abaFarisi labafundisi bomthetho basebesithi kuye, “Mfundisi, sifuna ukubona isibonakaliso esivela kuwe.”<verse eid="MAT 12:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="MAT 12:39"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Isizukulwane esixhwalileyo lesiphingayo sicela isibonakaliso! Kodwa kasisoze sisiphiwe ngaphandle kwesibonakaliso somphrofethi uJona.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MAT 12:40"/><char style="wj">NjengoJona owahlala insuku ezintathu lobusuku obuthathu esiswini senhlanzi enkulu, kanjalo iNdodana yoMuntu izahlala insuku ezintathu lobusuku obuthathu phansi komhlabathi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="MAT 12:41"/><char style="wj">Abantu baseNiniva bazasukuma kanye lalesi sizukulwane ngosuku lokwahlulelwa basilahle ngoba bona baphenduka ekutshumayeleni kukaJona, kodwa khathesi lowo omkhulu kuloJona uselapha.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MAT 12:42"/><char style="wj">INdlovukazi yaseNingizimu izavuka mhla wokwahlulelwa kanye lalesi isizukulwane isilahle; ngoba yeza ivela emaphethelweni omhlaba izolalela uSolomoni; pho manje omkhulu kuloSolomoni usekhona.</char><verse eid="MAT 12:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="MAT 12:43"/>
    <char style="wj">Nxa umoya omubi uphuma emuntwini, uyazula enkangala udinga ukuphumula kodwa uyakuswela.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="MAT 12:44"/><char style="wj">Ubususithi, ‘Ngizabuyela endlini engaphuma kuyo.’ Uthi ufika uthole leyondlu ingelamuntu, ithanyelwe yahlanzeka, konke kumi kuhle.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="MAT 12:45"/><char style="wj">Ubusuhamba uyethatha eminye imimoya eyisikhombisa exhwale okudlula wona, ingene ihlale khona. Isiphetho salowomuntu sizakuba sibi kulasekuqaleni. Kuzakuba njalo kulesisizukulwane esixhwalileyo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 12:45"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Unina KaJesu Labafowabo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="MAT 12:46"/>UJesu elokhu esakhuluma lamaxuku abantu, unina labafowabo babemi phandle befuna ukukhuluma laye. <verse eid="MAT 12:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="MAT 12:47"/>Omunye wamtshela wathi, “Unyoko labafowenu bemi phandle, bafuna ukukhuluma lawe.”<verse eid="MAT 12:47"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="MAT 12:48"/>Wamphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngubani umama njalo ngobani abangabafowethu na?”</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="MAT 12:49"/>Wakhomba abafundi bakhe wathi, <char style="wj">“Nampa abangumama labangabafowethu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 12:49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="MAT 12:50"/><char style="wj">Loba ngubani owenza intando kaBaba osezulwini ungumfowethu, ungudadewethu njalo ngumama.”</char><verse eid="MAT 12:50"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 12"/>
  <chapter number="13" style="c" sid="MAT 13"/>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Womhlanyeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 13:1"/>Ngalolosuku uJesu waphuma endlini wayahlala eceleni kwechibi. <verse eid="MAT 13:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 13:2"/>Amaxuku abantu aminyezelana kuye waze wangena esikepeni wahlala kuso, abantu bonke bona babemi okhunjini. <verse eid="MAT 13:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 13:3"/>Wasebatshela izinto ezinengi esebenzisa imizekeliso, wathi, <char style="wj">“Umlimi waphuma wayahlanyela inhlanyelo yakhe.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 13:4"/><char style="wj">Kwathi eyihaza inhlanyelo, eyinye yawela endleleni, izinyoni zafika zayidobha yonke.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 13:5"/><char style="wj">Eyinye yawela okhetheni lapho okwakungela mhlabathi owaneleyo. Yaphanga yamila ngoba umhlabathi wawungatshoni.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 13:6"/><char style="wj">Kodwa kwathi ilanga seliphumile yahanguleka yabuna ngoba yayingelampande.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 13:7"/><char style="wj">Eyinye yawela phakathi kwameva, asuka akhula ayiminya inhlanyelo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 13:8"/><char style="wj">Eyinye inhlanyelo yawela emhlabathini omuhle lapho eyathela khona izithelo eziphindwe okungabalikhulu, kumbe okungamatshumi ayisithupha loba okungamatshumi amathathu ukudlula leyo eyayihlanyelwe.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 13:9"/><char style="wj">Lowo olendlebe kezwe.”</char><verse eid="MAT 13:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 13:10"/>Abafundi beza kuye bambuza bathi, “Kungani ukhuluma ebantwini ngemizekeliso na?”<verse eid="MAT 13:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 13:11"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ulwazi lwemfihlakalo yombuso wezulu luphiwe lina hatshi bona.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 13:12"/><char style="wj">Lowo olakho, uzaphiwa kwengezelelwe abesesiba lokunengi kakhulu. Lowo ongelakho, lalokho alakho uzakwemukwa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 13:13"/><char style="wj">Lokhu yikho okungenza ngikhulume kubo ngemizekeliso:</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 13:13">
    <char style="wj">Ngoba loba bekhangele kababoni;</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 13:13">
    <char style="wj">loba belalele kabezwa njalo kabaqedisisi.</char><verse eid="MAT 13:13"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 13:14"/>
    <char style="wj">Kubo isiphrofethi sika-Isaya siyagcwaliseka, esokuthi:</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 13:14">
    <char style="wj">‘Lizahlala lisizwa kodwa lingaqedisisi;</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 13:14">
    <char style="wj">lizahlala libona kodwa lingabonisisi.</char><verse eid="MAT 13:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 13:15"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngoba inhliziyo zalababantu sezaba lukhuni;</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 13:15">
    <char style="wj">kabasezwa ngezindlebe zabo</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 13:15">
    <char style="wj">njalo sebawavala amehlo abo.</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 13:15">
    <char style="wj">Funa babone ngamehlo abo,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 13:15">
    <char style="wj">bezwe ngezindlebe zabo,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 13:15">
    <char style="wj">baqedisise ngezinhliziyo zabo,</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 13:15">
    <char style="wj">baphenduke bese ngibasilisa.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">13.15 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 6.9-10</char>
    </note><verse eid="MAT 13:15"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 13:16"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa abusisiwe amehlo enu ngoba ayabona lezindlebe zenu ziyezwa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 13:17"/><char style="wj">Ngoba ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi abaphrofethi abanengi lamadoda alungileyo balangazela ukukubona lokhu elikubonayo kodwa kabakubonanga, lokuzwa lokhu elikuzwayo kodwa kabakuzwanga.</char><verse eid="MAT 13:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 13:18"/>
    <char style="wj">Lalelani-ke lizwe ukuthi utshoni umzekeliso womhlanyeli:</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 13:19"/><char style="wj">Nxa umuntu esizwa ilizwi ngombuso kodwa engabambisisi, omubi uyeza ahwithe lokho obekuhlanyelwe enhliziyweni yakhe. Yiyo le inhlanyelo eyahlanyelwa endleleni.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 13:20"/><char style="wj">Inhlanyelo eyawela okhetheni ngumuntu olizwayo ilizwi aphange alamukele ngentokozo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 13:21"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ngenxa yokuthi kalampande, nxa okwesikhatshana kuphela. Nxa kufika uhlupho lokuhlukunyezwa ngenxa yelizwi uphanga akhubeke.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 13:22"/><char style="wj">Inhlanyelo eyawela phakathi kwameva ngumuntu olizwayo ilizwi kodwa lisuke landelwe yizinhlupheko zale impilo lenkohliso yenotho, lingabe lisaba lezithelo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 13:23"/><char style="wj">Kodwa leyonhlanyelo eyawela emhlabathini ovundileyo ngumuntu olizwayo ilizwi alizwisise. Lo nguye othela izithelo ezinengi ngekhulu, ngamatshumi ayisithupha loba ngamatshumi amathathu okudlula lokho okwahlanyelwayo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 13:23"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wokhula</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 13:24"/>UJesu wabatshela omunye umzekeliso wathi, <char style="wj">“Umbuso wezulu unjengomuntu owahlanyela inhlanyelo enhle ensimini yakhe.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 13:25"/><char style="wj">Kodwa kwathi ngesikhathi wonke umuntu elele, isitha sakhe seza sahlanyela ukhula phakathi kwengqoloyi, sahamba.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 13:26"/><char style="wj">Kwathi ingqoloyi isikhahlele yabumba izikhwebu, ukhula lalo lwavela.</char><verse eid="MAT 13:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 13:27"/>
    <char style="wj">Izinceku zomninisivini zeza kuye zathi, ‘Nkosi, kanti kawuhlanyelanga yini inhlanyelo enhle ensimini yakho na? Pho ukhula luvele ngaphi?’</char><verse eid="MAT 13:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 13:28"/>
    <char style="wj">Waphendula wathi, ‘Kwenziwe yisitha lokhu.’</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 13:28">
    <char style="wj">Zambuza izinceku zathi, ‘Uyafuna yini ukuthi siyelusiphuna na?’</char><verse eid="MAT 13:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 13:29"/>
    <char style="wj">Waphendula wathi, ‘Hatshi, ngoba lizakuthi lisiphuna ukhula liqabuke selisiphuna amabele kanye lalo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 13:30"/><char style="wj">Kuyekeleni kukhule ndawonye kuze kube yisikhathi sokuvuna. Lapho-ke, ngizakuthi kubavuni, Qalani ngokuqoqa ukhula lilubophe izinyanda ukuba lutshiswe, beseliqoqa amabele liwalethe esiphaleni sami.’ ”</char><verse eid="MAT 13:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wentanga Yemastadi Lemvubelo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 13:31"/>Wabatshela omunye umzekeliso wathi, <char style="wj">“Umbuso wezulu ufana lentanga yemastadi eyathathwa ngenye indoda yayihlanyela ensimini yayo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 13:32"/><char style="wj">Lanxa incinyane kulentanga yenhlanyelo zonke, kodwa ithi ingakhula ibe yisihlahla esikhulu kulazo zonke, izinyoni zezulu zibuye, zithole ukuphumula ezingatsheni zaso.”</char><verse eid="MAT 13:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 13:33"/>Waphinda wabatshela omunye umzekeliso wathi, <char style="wj">“Umbuso wezulu ufana lemvubelo eyathathwa ngowesifazane wayixubanisa lempuphu enengi, yabila yagcwala inhlama yonke.”</char><verse eid="MAT 13:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 13:34"/>UJesu wakhuluma zonke lezizinto exukwini labantu ngemizekeliso; kazange akhulume lutho kubo engasebenzisanga umzekeliso. <verse eid="MAT 13:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MAT 13:35"/>Ngakho kwagcwaliseka okwakhulunywa ngomphrofethi ukuthi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 13:35">“Ngizavula umlomo wami ngemizekeliso,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 13:35">ngizakutsho izinto ezifihliweyo selokhu kwadatshulwa umhlaba.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">13.35 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 78.2</char></note><verse eid="MAT 13:35"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wokhula Uyachasiswa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="MAT 13:36"/>Wasesuka exukwini waya endlini. Abafundi bakhe beza kuye bathi, “Sichazele umzekeliso wokhula ensimini.”<verse eid="MAT 13:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="MAT 13:37"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Lowo owahlanyela inhlanyelo enhle yiNdodana yoMuntu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MAT 13:38"/><char style="wj">Insimu ngumhlaba njalo inhlanyelo enhle imele abantu bombuso. Ukhula lungabantu bomubi</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MAT 13:39"/><char style="wj">njalo isitha esiluhlanyelayo nguSathane. Isivuno siyikuphela kwesikhathi njalo abavuni yizingilosi.</char><verse eid="MAT 13:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="MAT 13:40"/>
    <char style="wj">Njengalokhu ukhula lusitshunwa lutshiswe emlilweni, kuzakuba njalo ekupheleni kwesikhathi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="MAT 13:41"/><char style="wj">Indodana yoMuntu izathuma izingilosi zayo, zikhuphe konke okuyizikhubekiso embusweni wayo, labo bonke abenza ububi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MAT 13:42"/><char style="wj">Zizabaphosela esihogweni somlilo ovuthayo okuzakuba khona ukukhala lokugedla kwamazinyo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="MAT 13:43"/><char style="wj">Lapho-ke, abalungileyo bazakhazimula njengelanga embusweni kaYise wabo. Lowo olendlebe, kezwe.”</char><verse eid="MAT 13:43"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wenotho Efihliweyo Lowephareli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="MAT 13:44"/>
    <char style="wj">“Umbuso wezulu unjengenotho efihliweyo esivandeni. Kwathi indoda isiyitholile yayifihla njalo, kwathi ngoba iphakathi kokuthokoza, yahamba yayathengisa konke eyayilakho yayathenga lesosivande.</char><verse eid="MAT 13:44"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="MAT 13:45"/>
    <char style="wj">Njalo umbuso wezulu ufana lomthengi edinga amaphareli amahle.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="MAT 13:46"/><char style="wj">Kwathi esefumene elinye elalilentengo ephezulu wahamba wayathengisa konke ayelakho walithenga.”</char><verse eid="MAT 13:46"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Womambule</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="MAT 13:47"/>
    <char style="wj">“Futhi umbuso wezulu ufana lomambule owehliselwa phansi echibini wagola zonke inhlobo zezinhlanzi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="MAT 13:48"/><char style="wj">Wathi usugcwele, abagoli bezinhlanzi bawudonsela okhunjini. Basebehlala phansi, baqoqela ezitsheni zonke inhlanzi ezinhle kodwa ezimbi bazilahla.</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="MAT 13:49"/><char style="wj">Lokhu yikho okuzakwenzakala ekupheleni kwesikhathi. Izingilosi zizakuza zehlukanise ababi kwabalungileyo,</char> <verse eid="MAT 13:49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="MAT 13:50"/><char style="wj">zibaphosele esihogweni somlilo ovuthayo, lapho okuzakuba khona lokukhala kanye lokugedla kwamazinyo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 13:50"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="51" style="v" sid="MAT 13:51"/>UJesu wababuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Selizizwisisile zonke lezizinto na?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 13:51">Bathi, “Yebo.”<verse eid="MAT 13:51"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="52" style="v" sid="MAT 13:52"/>Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Ngakho wonke umfundisi womthetho osephenduke waba ngumfundi wombuso wezulu unjengomnini wendlu okhupha esiphaleni sakhe amagugu amatsha lamadala.”</char><verse eid="MAT 13:52"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umphrofethi Ongeladumo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="53" style="v" sid="MAT 13:53"/>UJesu eseqedile imizekeliso le wasuka lapho wahamba. <verse eid="MAT 13:53"/><verse number="54" style="v" sid="MAT 13:54"/>Wafika edolobheni lakibo waqalisa ukufundisa abantu esinagogweni labo, bamangala. Babuza bathi, “Indoda le yayithatha ngaphi inhlakanipho le lamandla la ayisimangaliso kangaka? <verse eid="MAT 13:54"/><verse number="55" style="v" sid="MAT 13:55"/>Kanti lo kayisiyo indodana yombazi na? Ibizo likanina kasuMariya na, labafowabo kakusiJakhobe, uJosefa, uSimoni loJudasi na? <verse eid="MAT 13:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="MAT 13:56"/>Odadewabo kabakho lapha kanye lathi na? Pho indoda le yazizuza ngaphi izinto zonke lezi?” <verse eid="MAT 13:56"/><verse number="57" style="v" sid="MAT 13:57"/>Bakhubeka ngaye.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 13:57">Kodwa uJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Umphrofethi kaladumo edolobheni lakibo lasendlini yakwabo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 13:57"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="58" style="v" sid="MAT 13:58"/>Kasenzanga izimangaliso ezinengi khona ngenxa yokusilela kwabo ekukholweni.<verse eid="MAT 13:58"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 13"/>
  <chapter number="14" style="c" sid="MAT 14"/>
  <para style="s1">UJohane Umbhaphathizi Uqunywa Ikhanda</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 14:1"/>Ngalesosikhathi uHerodi umbusi wezwa imibiko ngoJesu, <verse eid="MAT 14:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 14:2"/>wasesithi ezincekwini zakhe, “Lo nguJohane uMbhaphathizi; usevukile kwabafileyo! Yikho izimangaliso zisenziwa nguye.”<verse eid="MAT 14:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 14:3"/>UHerodi wayembophile uJohane, wamfaka insimbi, wamphosela entolongweni ngenxa kaHerodiyasi, umkamfowabo uFiliphu, <verse eid="MAT 14:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 14:4"/>ngoba uJohane wayelokhu esithi kuye, “Kungaphandle komthetho ukuthi umthathe.” <verse eid="MAT 14:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 14:5"/>UHerodi wayefuna ukumbulala uJohane kodwa wayesesaba abantu ngoba babesithi ungumphrofethi.<verse eid="MAT 14:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 14:6"/>Ngelanga lesikhumbuzo sokuzalwa kukaHerodi indodakazi kaHerodiyasi yasinela izethekeli, yamjabulisa kakhulu uHerodi <verse eid="MAT 14:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 14:7"/>waze wathembisa ngesifungo ukuyipha loba yini eyayingayicela. <verse eid="MAT 14:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 14:8"/>Isicetshiswe ngunina yathi, “Ngipha ikhanda likaJohane uMbhaphathizi lisemganwini.” <verse eid="MAT 14:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 14:9"/>Inkosi yadana kakhulu kodwa kwathi ngenxa yezifungo zayo langenxa yezethekeli zayo yalaya ukuba isicelo leso senziwe, <verse eid="MAT 14:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 14:10"/>uJohane wahle waqunywa ikhanda entolongweni. <verse eid="MAT 14:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 14:11"/>Ikhanda lakhe lalethwa lisemganwini laphiwa intombazana eyalithwalela kunina. <verse eid="MAT 14:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 14:12"/>Abafundi bakaJohane beza bathatha isidumbu sakhe bayasingcwaba. Basebehamba bayatshela uJesu.<verse eid="MAT 14:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Upha Izinkulungwane Ezinhlanu Ukudla</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 14:13"/>UJesu wathi ekuzwa lokho okwenzakalayo wathi nyelele ngesikepe waya endaweni engelabantu. Amaxuku athi ekuzwa lokhu asuka emadolobheni amlandela ngenyawo. <verse eid="MAT 14:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 14:14"/>UJesu uthe esehla esikepeni wabona ixuku labantu elikhulu walizwela usizi ngakho wasesilisa abagulayo babo.<verse eid="MAT 14:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 14:15"/>Kwathi selithambeme abafundi beza kuye bathi, “Le yindawo ekhatshana kakhulu njalo sekuntambama. Wothi lababantu bahambe ukuze bayozithengela ukudla emizini.”<verse eid="MAT 14:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 14:16"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kakudingeki ukuthi bahambe. Bapheni lina ukudla.”</char><verse eid="MAT 14:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 14:17"/>Baphendula bathi, “Thina esilakho lapha yizinkwa ezinhlanu lenhlanzi ezimbili.”<verse eid="MAT 14:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 14:18"/>Wathi, <char style="wj">“Kuletheni lapha.”</char> <verse eid="MAT 14:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 14:19"/>Waselaya abantu ukuthi bahlale phansi phezu kotshani. Wathatha izinkwa ezinhlanu lenhlanzi ezimbili wakhangela ezulwini wabonga, wasehlephuna izinkwa. Waseziqhubela abafundi, bazinika abantu. <verse eid="MAT 14:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 14:20"/>Bonke badla basutha, abafundi bakhe babutha okuseleyo bagcwalisa izitsha ezilitshumi lambili. <verse eid="MAT 14:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 14:21"/>Inani lalabo abadlayo lalingaba ngamadoda azinkulungwane ezinhlanu kungabalwa abesifazane labantwana.<verse eid="MAT 14:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uhamba Phezu Kwamanzi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 14:22"/>Masinyane nje uJesu wathi abafundi bakhe bangene esikepeni bamandulele ngakwelinye iphetsheya, yena esavalelisana labantu. <verse eid="MAT 14:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 14:23"/>Esebakhulule, waya ewatheni lwentaba ukuyakhuleka eyedwa. Sekuhlwile ngalobobusuku wayekhonale eyedwa, <verse eid="MAT 14:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 14:24"/>kodwa isikepe sasesihambe umango ukusuka okhunjini, siyaluziswa ngamagagasi ngoba sasiphikisana lomoya.<verse eid="MAT 14:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 14:25"/>Kwathi ngomlindo wesine ebusuku uJesu waya kubo ehamba phezu kwechibi. <verse eid="MAT 14:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 14:26"/>Kwathi abafundi bembona ehamba phezu kwechibi besaba kakhulu. Bakhala ngokwesaba bathi, “Lithonga.”<verse eid="MAT 14:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 14:27"/>Kodwa uJesu waphanga wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Manini isibindi! Yimi. Lingesabi.”</char><verse eid="MAT 14:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 14:28"/>UPhethro waphendula wathi, “Nkosi, nxa kunguwe, tshono ukuba ngize kuwe phezu kwamanzi.”<verse eid="MAT 14:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 14:29"/>Wathi, <char style="wj">“Woza.”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 14:29">Khonapho uPhethro wasephuma esikepeni, wahamba phezu kwamanzi weza kuJesu. <verse eid="MAT 14:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 14:30"/>Kodwa wathi ebona umoya wesaba, kwathi eseqala ukutshona wakhala wathi, “Nkosi, akungisize!”<verse eid="MAT 14:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 14:31"/>Khonokho uJesu welula isandla sakhe wambamba. Wathi kuye, <char style="wj">“Wena olokholo oluncinyane, kungani uthandabuzile?”</char><verse eid="MAT 14:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 14:32"/>Bonela ukungena esikepeni umoya wathula. <verse eid="MAT 14:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 14:33"/>Kwathi labo ababesesikepeni bamkhonza bathi, “Ngempela uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="MAT 14:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 14:34"/>Bathi sebechaphile, bafikela eGenesaretha. <verse eid="MAT 14:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MAT 14:35"/>Kwathi amadoda akuleyondawo semnanzelele uJesu athumela ilizwi kuwo wonke umango wakulelo dolobho. Abantu baletha bonke abagulayo babo kuye <verse eid="MAT 14:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MAT 14:36"/>bamncenga ukuthi avumele labo abagulayo ukuthi bathinte nje umphetho wesigqoko sakhe, kwathi bonke labo abamthintayo basiliswa.<verse eid="MAT 14:36"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 14"/>
  <chapter number="15" style="c" sid="MAT 15"/>
  <para style="s1">Okuhlanzekileyo Lokungahlanzekanga</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 15:1"/>Ngalesosikhathi abanye abaFarisi labafundisi bomthetho beza kuJesu bevela eJerusalema bambuza bathi, <verse eid="MAT 15:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 15:2"/>“Kungani abafundi bakho besephula isiko labadala na? Kabagezi izandla zabo bengakadli!”<verse eid="MAT 15:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 15:3"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kungani lina lisephula umlayo kaNkulunkulu ngenxa yamasiko enu na?</char> <verse eid="MAT 15:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 15:4"/><char style="wj">Phela uNkulunkulu wathi, ‘Hlonipha uyihlo lonyoko’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15.4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 20.12; UDutheronomi 5.16</char></note> <char style="wj">njalo ‘Lowo othuka uyise loba unina ufanele ukubulawa.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">15.4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 21.17; ULevi 20.9</char></note> <verse eid="MAT 15:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 15:5"/><char style="wj">Kodwa lina lithi nxa umuntu esithi lokho obekungaba lusizo kuyise kumbe unina kuphawulelwe uNkulunkulu,</char> <verse eid="MAT 15:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 15:6"/><char style="wj">akasamelanga ahloniphe uyise lonina ngakho. Ngaleyondlela lichitha ilizwi likaNkulunkulu ngenxa yesiko lenu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 15:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 15:7"/><char style="wj">Lina bazenzisi! U-Isaya wayeqinisile aze aphrofithe ngani esithi:</char><verse eid="MAT 15:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 15:8"/>
    <char style="wj">‘Lababantu bangidumisa ngezindebe zabo,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 15:8">
    <char style="wj">kodwa inhliziyo zabo zikhatshana lami.</char><verse eid="MAT 15:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 15:9"/>
    <char style="wj">Bangikhonza ngeze;</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 15:9">
    <char style="wj">imfundiso yabo yimithetho yabantu.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">15.9 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 29.13</char>
    </note>
    <char style="wj">”</char><verse eid="MAT 15:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 15:10"/>UJesu wabizela ixuku labantu kuye wathi, <char style="wj">“Lalelani lizwisise.</char> <verse eid="MAT 15:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 15:11"/><char style="wj">Lokho okungena emlonyeni womuntu ‘kakumngcolisi’ kodwa lokho okuphuma emlonyeni wakhe yikho ‘okumngcolisayo.’ ”</char><verse eid="MAT 15:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 15:12"/>Abafundi basebesiza kuye bambuza bathi, “Uyakwazi yini ukuthi abaFarisi kubakhubile ukuzwa lokhu?”<verse eid="MAT 15:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 15:13"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Zonke izihlahla ezingahlanyelwanga nguBaba osezulwini zizasitshunwa lezimpande zazo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 15:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 15:14"/><char style="wj">Bayekeleni; ngabakhokheli abazimpumputhe. Nxa impumputhe ihola impumputhe zombili zizawela egodini.”</char><verse eid="MAT 15:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 15:15"/>UPhethro wathi, “Sichasisele umzekeliso lowo.”<verse eid="MAT 15:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 15:16"/>UJesu wababuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Lilokhu lingelakuqedisisa na?</char> <verse eid="MAT 15:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 15:17"/><char style="wj">Kaliboni yini ukuthi noma yini engena emlonyeni iya esiswini besekuphuma emzimbeni?</char> <verse eid="MAT 15:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 15:18"/><char style="wj">Kodwa lezozinto eziphuma emlonyeni womuntu zivela enhliziyweni yizo ezenza umuntu angcole.</char> <verse eid="MAT 15:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 15:19"/><char style="wj">Ngoba enhliziyweni kuphuma imicabango emibi, ukubulala, ukufeba, ukuhlobonga, ubusela, ukufakaza amanga, ukunyeya lokuhlambaza.</char> <verse eid="MAT 15:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 15:20"/><char style="wj">Lokhu yikho okwenza umuntu angcole, kodwa ukudla ngezandla ezingagezwanga kakumenzi angcole.”</char><verse eid="MAT 15:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukholo Lowesifazane WaseKhenani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 15:21"/>Esuka kuleyondawo uJesu waya emangweni waseThire leSidoni. <verse eid="MAT 15:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 15:22"/>Umfazi ongumKhenani wakuleyondawo weza kuye ezokhala esithi, “Nkosi, Ndodana kaDavida, ake ungihawukele! Indodakazi yami ithwele nzima, ihlutshwa ngamadimoni.”<verse eid="MAT 15:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 15:23"/>UJesu kazange amphendule. Ngakho abafundi bakhe beza kuye bamkhuthaza bathi, “Mxotshe, nangu uselokhu ememeza esilandela.”<verse eid="MAT 15:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 15:24"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngathunywa kuphela ezimvini ezilahlekileyo zako-Israyeli.”</char><verse eid="MAT 15:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 15:25"/>Owesifazane lowo weza waguqa phambi kwakhe wathi, “Nkosi, ake ungisize.”<verse eid="MAT 15:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 15:26"/>Waphendula uJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Kakulunganga ukuthatha isinkwa sabantwana usiphosele izinja.”</char><verse eid="MAT 15:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 15:27"/>Owesifazane wathi, “Yebo Nkosi, angithi izinja ziyayidla imvuthu eziwa etafuleni yabaninizo.”<verse eid="MAT 15:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 15:28"/>UJesu wasephendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Nkosazana, ulokukholwa okukhulu! Isicelo sakho sesamukelwe.”</char> Indodakazi yakhe yahle yasila ngalesosikhathi.<verse eid="MAT 15:28"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Usuthisa Izinkulungwane Ezine</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 15:29"/>UJesu wasuka lapho wehla egudlana loLwandle lwaseGalile. Wasekhwela entabeni wahlala phansi. <verse eid="MAT 15:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 15:30"/>Kweza kuye amaxuku amakhulu abantu eletha abaqhulayo, iziphofu, izigoga, izimungulu labanye abanengi, bababeka phambi kwakhe; wabasilisa. <verse eid="MAT 15:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 15:31"/>Abantu bamangala ukubona izimungulu sezikhuluma, izigoga sezitshwaphulukile, abaqhugezelayo sebezihambela leziphofu sezibona. Bamdumisa uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli.<verse eid="MAT 15:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 15:32"/>UJesu wabiza abafundi bakhe wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngibazwela usizi lababantu; sebehlale lami insuku ezintathu bengadlanga lutho. Angifuni kubakhulula belambile funa bayathe endleleni.”</char><verse eid="MAT 15:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 15:33"/>Abafundi bakhe bamphendula bathi, “Singakuthatha ngaphi ukudla okwaneleyo endaweni ekhatshana kanje ukuba sisuthise ixuku elingaka na?”<verse eid="MAT 15:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 15:34"/>UJesu wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Lilezinkwa ezingaki?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 15:34">Bathi, “Eziyisikhombisa lenhlanzi ezincane ezimbalwa.”<verse eid="MAT 15:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MAT 15:35"/>Wasetshela ixuku labantu ukuba lihlale phansi. <verse eid="MAT 15:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MAT 15:36"/>Wasethatha lezozinkwa eziyisikhombisa lenhlanzi, kwathi esebongile, wazihlephula waziqhubela abafundi, labo bazinika abantu. <verse eid="MAT 15:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MAT 15:37"/>Bonke badla basutha. Ngemva kwalokho abafundi babutha imvuthu kwagcwala izitsha eziyisikhombisa. <verse eid="MAT 15:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MAT 15:38"/>Inani lalabo abadlayo lalizinkulungwane ezine kungabalwa abafazi labantwana. <verse eid="MAT 15:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MAT 15:39"/>UJesu eselikhulule ixuku labantu, wangena esikepeni waya emangweni waseMagadani.<verse eid="MAT 15:39"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 15"/>
  <chapter number="16" style="c" sid="MAT 16"/>
  <para style="s1">Abafuna Isibonakaliso</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 16:1"/>AbaFarisi labaSadusi beza kuJesu bamlinga ngokumcela ukuthi abatshengise isibonakaliso esivela ezulwini.<verse eid="MAT 16:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 16:2"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Nxa kufika ukuhlwa lithi, ‘Umkhathi uzakuba muhle ngoba isibhakabhaka sibomvu,’</char> <verse eid="MAT 16:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 16:3"/><char style="wj">ekuseni lithi, ‘Lamuhla kuzaqubuka isiphepho ngoba isibhakabhaka sibomvu njalo kugubuzele.’ Liyakwazi ukuchaza umumo womkhathi kodwa kalenelisi ukuchaza izibonakaliso zesikhathi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 16:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 16:4"/><char style="wj">Isizukulwane esixhwalileyo lesiphingayo sifuna isibonakaliso kodwa kasisoze sisiphiwe ngaphandle kwesibonakaliso sikaJona.”</char> UJesu wasebatshiya wahamba.<verse eid="MAT 16:4"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Imvubelo YabaFarisi LabaSadusi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 16:5"/>Bathi sebekhuphukele ngaphetsheya kwechibi, abafundi babekhohliwe ukuza lesinkwa. <verse eid="MAT 16:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 16:6"/>UJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Limukani. Liqaphele imvubelo yabaFarisi labaSadusi.”</char><verse eid="MAT 16:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 16:7"/>Bakhulumisana ngalokhu bathi, “Kungenxa yokuba kasizanga lesinkwa.”<verse eid="MAT 16:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 16:8"/>UJesu wakwazi abakukhulumayo wasebuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Lina elilokholo oluncinyane, kungani likhulumisana ngokungabi lasinkwa na?</char> <verse eid="MAT 16:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 16:9"/><char style="wj">Lilokhu lingaqedisisi yini? Kalikhumbuli na izinkwa ezinhlanu ezasuthisa abantu abazinkulungwane ezinhlanu, lokuthi laqoqa izitsha ezingaki?</char> <verse eid="MAT 16:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 16:10"/><char style="wj">Kumbe izinkwa eziyisikhombisa ezasuthisa abantu abazinkulungwane ezine lokuthi laqoqa izitsha ezigcweleyo ezingaki?</char> <verse eid="MAT 16:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 16:11"/><char style="wj">Kungani lingezwisisi ukuthi bengingakhulumi lani ngesinkwa? Kodwa qaphelani imvubelo yabaFarisi labaSadusi.”</char> <verse eid="MAT 16:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 16:12"/>Basebezwisisa ukuthi wayengabatsheli ukuqaphela imvubelo esetshenziswa esinkweni kodwa ukunanzelela imfundiso yabaFarisi labaSadusi.<verse eid="MAT 16:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ubufakazi BukaPhethro NgoKhristu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 16:13"/>Kwathi uJesu esefike emangweni waseKhesariya Filiphi wabuza abafundi bakhe wathi, <char style="wj">“Abantu bathi iNdodana yoMuntu ingubani na?”</char><verse eid="MAT 16:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 16:14"/>Baphendula bathi, “Abanye bathi nguJohane uMbhaphathizi; abanye bathi ngu-Elija; abanye njalo bathi nguJeremiya loba omunye nje wabaphrofethi.”<verse eid="MAT 16:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 16:15"/>Wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Lina-ke, lithi ngingubani?”</char><verse eid="MAT 16:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 16:16"/>USimoni Phethro waphendula wathi, “UnguKhristu iNdodana kaNkulunkulu ophilayo.”<verse eid="MAT 16:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 16:17"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ubusisiwe wena Simoni, ndodana kaJona ngoba lokhu kawukwambulelwanga ngumuntu wegazi lenyama kodwa nguBaba osezulwini.</char> <verse eid="MAT 16:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 16:18"/><char style="wj">Ngakho ngiyakutshela ukuthi unguPhethro</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">16.18 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Ibala lesiGrikhi elithi </char><char style="fq" closed="false">Phethro </char><char style="ft" closed="false">litsho </char><char style="fq" closed="false">idwala.</char></note> <char style="wj">njalo phezu kwalelidwala ngizakwakha ibandla lami, futhi amasango eHadesi akayikulehlula.</char> <verse eid="MAT 16:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 16:19"/><char style="wj">Ngizakupha izihluthulelo zombuso wezulu; loba yini oyibophayo emhlabeni izabotshwa lasezulwini njalo loba yini oyithukululayo emhlabeni izathukululwa lasezulwini.”</char> <verse eid="MAT 16:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 16:20"/>Waseqonqosela abafundi bakhe ukuba bangatsheli muntu ukuthi wayenguKhristu.<verse eid="MAT 16:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ukhuluma Ngokufa Kwakhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 16:21"/>Kusukela ngalesosikhathi uJesu waqalisa ukuchazela abafundi bakhe ukuthi kumele aye eJerusalema ayehlupheka ngezinto ezinengi ezandleni zabadala bebandla, abaphristi abakhulu labafundisi bomthetho njalo lokuthi kumele abulawe, kuthi ngelanga lesithathu avuswe kwabafileyo.<verse eid="MAT 16:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 16:22"/>UPhethro wamdonsela eceleni waqalisa ukumkhuza wathi, “Ngeke kwenzeke Nkosi! Lokhu kakusoze kwafa kwenzeka kuwe!”<verse eid="MAT 16:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 16:23"/>UJesu waphendula wathi kuPhethro, <char style="wj">“Suka emva kwami Sathane! Uyisikhubekiso kimi; engqondweni yakho kawulazo izinto zikaNkulunkulu kodwa ucabanga ezabantu.”</char><verse eid="MAT 16:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 16:24"/>UJesu wasesithi kubafundi bakhe, <char style="wj">“Nxa ekhona ofuna ukungilandela, kazidele athathe isiphambano sakhe angilandele.</char> <verse eid="MAT 16:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 16:25"/><char style="wj">Ngoba lowo ofuna ukusindisa impilo yakhe izamlahlekela kodwa lowo olahlekelwa yimpilo yakhe ngenxa yami uzayizuza.</char> <verse eid="MAT 16:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 16:26"/><char style="wj">Kuzamsiza ngani umuntu ukuzuza wonke umhlaba kodwa alahlekelwe ngumphefumulo wakhe na? Kambe umuntu angaphani esikhundleni sempilo yakhe na?</char> <verse eid="MAT 16:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 16:27"/><char style="wj">Phela iNdodana yoMuntu izakuza ngobukhosi bukaYise kanye lezingilosi zakhe, ibisisipha umvuzo emuntwini munye ngamunye ngalokho akwenzileyo.</char><verse eid="MAT 16:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 16:28"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso, abanye abemiyo khonapha kabayikukuzwa ukufa bengakayiboni iNdodana yoMuntu isiza embusweni wayo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 16:28"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 16"/>
  <chapter number="17" style="c" sid="MAT 17"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukukhazimuliswa KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 17:1"/>Ngemva kwensuku eziyisithupha, uJesu wathatha uPhethro, loJakhobe loJohane umfowabo kaJakhobe wakhwela labo entabeni ephakemeyo lapho ababa bodwa khona. <verse eid="MAT 17:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 17:2"/>Bekhona lapho waguquka isimo emehlweni abo. Ubuso bakhe bakhazimula njengelanga lezigqoko zakhe zaba mhlophe njengokukhanya. <verse eid="MAT 17:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 17:3"/>Khonokho kwasekubonakala uMosi lo-Elija bekhuluma loJesu.<verse eid="MAT 17:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 17:4"/>UPhethro wathi kuJesu, “Nkosi, kuhle kithi ukuba lapha. Nxa uthanda ngizakwakha izihonqo ezintathu, esakho, esinye esikaMosi lesinye esika-Elija.”<verse eid="MAT 17:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 17:5"/>Wathi elokhe esakhuluma, iyezi elikhazimulayo labagubuzela, ilizwi elavela eyezini lathi, “Le yiNdodana yami engiyithandayo; ngiyathokoza kakhulu ngayo. Ilaleleni!”<verse eid="MAT 17:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 17:6"/>Abafundi bathi bekuzwa lokhu bathi mbo phansi ngobuso, besaba. <verse eid="MAT 17:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 17:7"/>Kodwa uJesu weza wabathinta. Wathi, <char style="wj">“Sukumani. Lingesabi.”</char> <verse eid="MAT 17:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 17:8"/>Bathi bevusa amehlo kabasabonanga muntu ngaphandle kukaJesu.<verse eid="MAT 17:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 17:9"/>Bathi sebesehla entabeni, uJesu wabalaya wathi, <char style="wj">“Lingatsheli muntu ngalokhu elikubonileyo iNdodana yoMuntu ize ivuswe kwabafileyo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 17:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 17:10"/>Abafundi bambuza bathi, “Kungani pho abafundisi bomthetho besithi u-Elija kumele aqale afike?”<verse eid="MAT 17:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 17:11"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngeqiniso, u-Elija uyeza azolungisa kutsha izinto zonke.</char> <verse eid="MAT 17:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 17:12"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ngiyalitshela ngithi u-Elija uvele sewafika njalo kabamazanga kodwa bazenzela kuye konke ababekufuna. INdodana yoMuntu bazayihlukuluza ngaleyondlela.”</char> <verse eid="MAT 17:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 17:13"/>Lapho-ke abafundi basebezwisisa ukuthi wayekhuluma labo ngoJohane uMbhaphathizi.<verse eid="MAT 17:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukusiliswa Komfana Owayeledimoni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 17:14"/>Bathi sebefike exukwini labantu, indoda ethile yamqonda uJesu yaguqa phambi kwakhe. <verse eid="MAT 17:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 17:15"/>Yathi, “Nkosi, ake uhawukele indodana yami. Ilezithuthwane njalo iyahlupheka kakhulu. Kanengi iwela emlilweni kumbe emanzini. <verse eid="MAT 17:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 17:16"/>Ngiyilethile kubafundi bakho kodwa behlulekile ukuyisilisa.”<verse eid="MAT 17:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 17:17"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Oh, lina sizukulwane esingakholwayo lesonakeleyo. Ngizahlala lani kuze kube nini na? Ngizalibekezelela kuze kube nini na? Mletheni lapha kimi umfana lowo.”</char> <verse eid="MAT 17:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 17:18"/>UJesu walikhuza idimoni laphuma emfaneni wahle wasila ngalesosikhathi.<verse eid="MAT 17:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 17:19"/>Abafundi basebesiza kuJesu ngasese bambuza bathi, “Kungani sehlulekile ukulikhupha idimoni na?”<verse eid="MAT 17:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 17:20"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngoba ukholo lwenu luncinyane. Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi nxa lingaba lokukholwa loba kukuncinyane njengentanga yemastadi, lingathi entabeni le, ‘Suduluka lapha uye laphayana’ izasuduluka. Kakukho kini okungasoze kwenzeke. [</char> <verse eid="MAT 17:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 17:21"/><char style="wj">Kodwa uhlobo olunje aluphumi ngaphandle kwangomkhuleko lokuzila ukudla.]”</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">17.21 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Imibhalo ekholekayo yekuqaleni lobunye ubufakazi bendulo kabulayo livesi UMakho 9.29.</char></note><verse eid="MAT 17:21"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuphrofitha Kwesibili KukaJesu Mayelana Lokufa Kwakhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 17:22"/>Bathi sebebuthene eGalile wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“INdodana yoMuntu izanikelwa ezandleni zabantu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 17:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 17:23"/><char style="wj">Bazayibulala, kuthi ngosuku lwesithathu izavuswa kwabafileyo.”</char> Abafundi badabuka kakhulu.<verse eid="MAT 17:23"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umthelo WeThempeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 17:24"/>UJesu labafundi bakhe sebefikile eKhaphenawume, abaqoqi bomthelo wamadrakhima amabili beza kuPhethro babuza bathi, “Umfundisi wenu kawuhlawuli yini umthelo wethempeli?”<verse eid="MAT 17:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 17:25"/>Wathi, “Yebo, uyawuthela.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 17:25">Kwathi uPhethro engena endlini, uJesu nguye owakhuluma kuqala, wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Ucabangani kambe Simoni? Amakhosi omhlaba ayithatha kubani inkongozelo lemithelo, emadodaneni abo na loba kwabanye abantu?”</char><verse eid="MAT 17:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 17:26"/>UPhethro waphendula wathi, “Kwabanye abantu.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 17:26">UJesu wasesithi kuye, <char style="wj">“Ngakho-ke amadodana akhululekile.</char> <verse eid="MAT 17:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 17:27"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ukuze singabakhubi, yana echibini uphosele iwuka yakho khona. Ubothatha inhlanzi yokuqala ozayibamba, uvule umlomo wayo uzafumana khona uhlamvu lwemali engamadrakhima amane. Uyithathe ubaphe ibe ngumthelo wami lowenu.”</char><verse eid="MAT 17:27"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 17"/>
  <chapter number="18" style="c" sid="MAT 18"/>
  <para style="s1">Omkhulu Kulabo Bonke Embusweni Wezulu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 18:1"/>Ngalesosikhathi abafundi beza kuJesu babuza bathi, “Ngubani omkhulu kulabo bonke embusweni wezulu na?”<verse eid="MAT 18:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 18:2"/>Wabiza umntwana omncinyane wamisa phakathi kwabo. <verse eid="MAT 18:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 18:3"/>Wasesithi, <char style="wj">“Ngiqinisile ngithi kini, ngaphandle kokuba liguquke libe njengabantwana abancinyane, kalisoze lafa langena embusweni wezulu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 18:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 18:4"/><char style="wj">Ngakho lowo ozithobayo njengomntwana lo nguye omkhulu kulabo bonke embusweni wezulu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 18:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 18:5"/><char style="wj">Njalo lowo owamukela umntwana omncane njengalo ebizweni lami wamukela mina.”</char><verse eid="MAT 18:5"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukukhubekisa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 18:6"/>
    <char style="wj">“Nxa umuntu ekhubekisa oyedwa walaba abancinyane abakholwa kimi ukuthi enze isono, kungabangcono kuye ukuthi kulengiswe entanyeni yakhe inkalakatha yembokodo yokuchola agaluliswe enzikini yolwandle.</char> <verse eid="MAT 18:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 18:7"/><char style="wj">Maye kuwo umhlaba ngenxa yezinto ezenza abantu benze isono! Izinto ezinjalo zivele ziyafika kodwa maye kulowomuntu ezifika ngaye!</char> <verse eid="MAT 18:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 18:8"/><char style="wj">Nxa isandla sakho loba unyawo lwakho kukwenzisa isono, kuqume ukulahle. Kungcono kuwe ukuba ungene ekuphileni uyingini kumbe ugogekile kulokuba lezandla zombili kumbe inyawo zombili uphoselwe emlilweni ongapheliyo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 18:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 18:9"/><char style="wj">Nxa ilihlo lakho likwenzisa isono, likopole ulilahle. Kungcono kuwe ukungena ekuphileni ulelihlo elilodwa kulokuba lamehlo amabili kodwa uphoselwe esihogweni somlilo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 18:9"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wemvu Elahlekileyo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 18:10"/>
    <char style="wj">“Nanzelelani ukuthi lingeyisi lamunye walaba abancinyane. Ngoba ngilitshela ukuthi izingilosi zabo zezulu zihlezi zibona ubuso bukaBaba ezulwini.</char> [<verse eid="MAT 18:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 18:11"/><char style="wj">INdodana yoMuntu yalanda ukusindisa okwakulahlekile.</char>]<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">18.11 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Livesi ayikho kwamanye amaBhayibhili esiLungu.</char></note><verse eid="MAT 18:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 18:12"/>
    <char style="wj">Kambe likhumbulani? Nxa indoda ilezimvu ezilikhulu, enye iqambuke kwezinye, kayiyikuzitshiya yini lezo ezingamatshumi ayisificamunwemunye lasificamunwemunye ezintabeni iyedinga leyo eqambukileyo?</char> <verse eid="MAT 18:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 18:13"/><char style="wj">Ithi ingayithola, ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi, iyathokoza ngaleyo ukwedlula lezo ezingamatshumi ayisificamunwemunye lasificamunwemunye ezingazange zilahleke.</char> <verse eid="MAT 18:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 18:14"/><char style="wj">Ngokufanayo, uYihlo osezulwini kafisi ukuthi lamunye walaba abancinyane abhubhe.”</char><verse eid="MAT 18:14"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umfowenu Owenza Isono Kuwe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 18:15"/>
    <char style="wj">“Nxa umfowenu ekona, yana kuye umtshengise isiphambeko sakhe lilodwa lobabili. Nxa ekulalela usumzuzile umfowenu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 18:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 18:16"/><char style="wj">Kodwa nxa engakulaleli, biza omunye loba ababili ukuze ‘indaba yonke ivele obala ilabofakazi ababili loba abathathu.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">18.16 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 19.15</char></note> <verse eid="MAT 18:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 18:17"/><char style="wj">Nxa esala ukubalalela, tshela ibandla, nxa esala ukulilalela lalo ibandla mthatheni njengomhedeni kumbe njengomthelisi.</char><verse eid="MAT 18:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 18:18"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi, loba yini eliyibophayo emhlabeni izabotshwa lasezulwini njalo lokho elikuthukululayo emhlabeni kuzathukululwa lasezulwini.</char><verse eid="MAT 18:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 18:19"/>
    <char style="wj">Njalo ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi nxa ababili kini emhlabeni bevumelana loba ngalutho bani abalucelayo bazalwenzelwa nguBaba osezulwini.</char> <verse eid="MAT 18:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 18:20"/><char style="wj">Ngoba lapho okuhlangana khona ababili loba abathathu ngebizo lami, ngizabe ngikhona lami.”</char><verse eid="MAT 18:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wenceku Engelasihawu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 18:21"/>UPhethro weza kuJesu wabuza wathi, “Nkosi, umfowethu loba udadewethu ngizamthethelela kangaki nxa elokhu engona na? Kuze kube kasikhombisa na?”<verse eid="MAT 18:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 18:22"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngithi hatshi kasikhombisa kodwa okwezikhathi ezingamatshumi ayisikhombisa lesikhombisa.</char><verse eid="MAT 18:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 18:23"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngakho umbuso wezulu unjengenkosi eyayifuna ukuqeda izikwelede zayo lezinceku zayo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 18:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 18:24"/><char style="wj">Yathi isiqalisa ukuthonisa kwalethwa kuyo indoda eyayilesikwelede samathalenta azinkulungwane ezilitshumi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 18:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 18:25"/><char style="wj">Kwathi ngoba ingelamandla okuhlawula inkosi yalaya ukuthi yona, umkayo, abantwana lakho konke eyayilakho kuthengiswe ukuze kuqedwe umlandu.</char><verse eid="MAT 18:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 18:26"/>
    <char style="wj">Inceku yaguqa phambi kwenkosi yayincenga yathi, ‘Ake ungibekezelele, ngizahlawula konke.’</char> <verse eid="MAT 18:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 18:27"/><char style="wj">Inkosi yenceku leyo yayizwela usizi, yayithethelela, yawesula umlandu yayiyekela yahamba.</char><verse eid="MAT 18:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 18:28"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa leyo yonela ukuphuma, yafumana eyinye inceku eyayilesikwelede sayo samadenari alikhulu. Yayibamba ngomphimbo, yayiklinya, yathi ngolaka, ‘Hlawula isikwelede sami!’</char><verse eid="MAT 18:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 18:29"/>
    <char style="wj">Leyonceku layo yawa ngamadolo yayincenga yathi, ‘Ake ungibekezelele, ngizakuhlawula.’</char><verse eid="MAT 18:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 18:30"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa yona yala. Endaweni yalokho, yahamba yenza ukuba leyondoda iphoselwe entolongweni ize iqale ihlawule isikwelede.</char> <verse eid="MAT 18:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 18:31"/><char style="wj">Kwathi ezinye izinceku sezibonile okwakwenzakele, zathukuthela kakhulu zayaceba enkosini ngalokho okwenzakeleyo.</char><verse eid="MAT 18:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 18:32"/>
    <char style="wj">Inkosi yayibiza leyonceku, yathi, ‘Wena nceku embi. Ngikuthethelele, ngasesula sonke isikwelede sakho ngoba ungincengile.</char> <verse eid="MAT 18:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 18:33"/><char style="wj">Kungani pho ungazwelanga omunye wakho isihawu njengalokhu ngenzile kuwe?’</char> <verse eid="MAT 18:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 18:34"/><char style="wj">Inkosi yayo yathukuthela kakhulu, yayinikela kubaphathi bejele ukuthi bayihlukuluze ize isihlawule sonke isikwelede.</char><verse eid="MAT 18:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MAT 18:35"/>
    <char style="wj">Yiyo le indlela uBaba osezulwini azaphatha ngayo lowo lalowo wenu nxa lingathetheleli abazalwane kuphuma enhliziyweni.”</char><verse eid="MAT 18:35"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 18"/>
  <chapter number="19" style="c" sid="MAT 19"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuchitha Umtshado</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 19:1"/>UJesu eseqedile ukutsho lezizinto, wasuka eGalile waya emangweni waseJudiya ngaphetsheya kweJodani. <verse eid="MAT 19:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 19:2"/>Walandelwa ngamaxuku amakhulu abantu, wabasilisa khona lapho.<verse eid="MAT 19:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 19:3"/>Abanye abaFarisi beza kuye ukuzamlinga. Bambuza bathi, “Kusemthethweni yini ukuthi indoda ilahle umkayo loba kungasiphi isizatho?”<verse eid="MAT 19:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 19:4"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Kalikubalanga yini ukuthi ekuqaleni uMdali ‘wabenza baba ngowesilisa lowesifazane,’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">19.4 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UGenesisi 1.27</char></note> <verse eid="MAT 19:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 19:5"/><char style="wj">wathi, ‘Ngalesi isizatho indoda izatshiya uyise lonina ihlanganiswe lomkayo, kuthi laba ababili bazakuba nyamanye?’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">19.5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UGenesisi 2.24</char></note> <verse eid="MAT 19:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 19:6"/><char style="wj">Ngakho kabasebabili, kodwa sebenyamanye. Ngakho, lokho uNkulunkulu asekuhlanganisile akungehlukaniswa muntu.”</char><verse eid="MAT 19:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 19:7"/>Babuza bathi, “Kungani pho uMosi walaya ukuthi indoda imuphe umkayo incwadi yokuquma umtshado ibisimxotsha?”<verse eid="MAT 19:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 19:8"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“UMosi walivumela ukuthi lilahle omkenu ngobulukhuni bezinhliziyo zenu. Kodwa kwakungenjalo ekuqaleni.</char> <verse eid="MAT 19:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 19:9"/><char style="wj">Ngilitshela ukuthi lowo ohlukana lomkakhe, ngaphandle kokuba ehlobongile, athathe omunye umfazi, uyaphinga.”</char><verse eid="MAT 19:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 19:10"/>Abafundi bathi kuye, “Nxa kumi kanjalo phakathi kwendoda lomkayo kungcono ukungathathi.”<verse eid="MAT 19:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 19:11"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Akusibo bonke abangalemukela lelilizwi, kodwa labo kuphela abaliphiweyo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 19:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 19:12"/><char style="wj">Ngoba abanye bangabathenwa ngenxa yokuthi bazalwa benjalo, abanye benziwa ngabantu njalo abanye bakudela ukutshada ngenxa yombuso wezulu. Lowo ongakwamukela lokho kakwemukele.”</char><verse eid="MAT 19:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Abantwana Abancane LoJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 19:13"/>Kwasekulethwa abantwana abancinyane kuJesu ukuba ababeke izandla lokubakhulekela. Kodwa abafundi babakhuza labo ababalethayo.<verse eid="MAT 19:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 19:14"/>UJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Yekelani abantwana beze kimi, lingabavimbeli ngoba umbuso wezulu ungowabanjengalaba.”</char> <verse eid="MAT 19:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 19:15"/>Esebabekile izandla wasuka lapho wahamba.<verse eid="MAT 19:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Insizwa Enothileyo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 19:16"/>Kweza enye insizwa kuJesu yabuza yathi, “Mfundisi, ngingenzani okulungileyo ukuze ngizuze ukuphila okungapheliyo na?”<verse eid="MAT 19:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 19:17"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ungibuzelani ngokulungileyo na? Munye kuphela olungileyo. Nxa ufuna ukungena ekuphileni, landela imilayo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 19:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 19:18"/>Insizwa yabuza yathi, “Yiphi na?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 19:18">UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“ ‘Ungabulali, ungaphingi, ungatshontshi, ungafakazeli amanga,</char> <verse eid="MAT 19:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 19:19"/><char style="wj">hlonipha uyihlo lonyoko,’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">19.19 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 20.12-16; UDutheronomi 5.16-20</char></note> <char style="wj">njalo ‘thanda umakhelwane wakho njengoba uzithanda wena.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">19.19 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ULevi 19.18</char></note><char style="wj">”</char><verse eid="MAT 19:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 19:20"/>Insizwa yathi, “Yonke le ngiyigcinile. Pho ngisaswelani na?”<verse eid="MAT 19:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 19:21"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Nxa ufuna ukuthi uphelele, thengisa yonke inotho yakho uphe abampofu, lapho-ke inotho yakho izakuba sezulwini. Ubusubuya ungilandele.”</char><verse eid="MAT 19:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 19:22"/>Kwathi insizwa ikuzwa lokho, yasuka idanile ngoba yayilenotho enengi kakhulu.<verse eid="MAT 19:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 19:23"/>UJesu wasesithi kubafundi bakhe, <char style="wj">“Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi kunzima emuntwini onothileyo ukuthi angene embusweni wezulu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 19:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 19:24"/><char style="wj">Njalo ngiyalitshela ukuthi kungaba lula ukuthi ikamela lingene embotsheni yenalithi kulokuthi umuntu onothileyo angene embusweni kaNkulunkulu.”</char><verse eid="MAT 19:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 19:25"/>Kwathi abafundi sebekuzwile lokhu bamangala kakhulu babuza bathi, “Pho ngubani ongasindiswa na?”<verse eid="MAT 19:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 19:26"/>UJesu wabakhangela wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngokwabantu, lokhu kakwenzeki kodwa ngoNkulunkulu zonke izinto ziyenzeka.”</char><verse eid="MAT 19:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 19:27"/>UPhethro wamphendula wathi, “Sesitshiye konke ukuze sikulandele! Pho sizazuzani na?”<verse eid="MAT 19:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 19:28"/>UJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi, emhlabeni omutsha, lapho iNdodana yoMuntu isihlezi esihlalweni sobukhosi, lina elingilandelayo lani lizahlala ezihlalweni zobukhosi ezilitshumi lambili, lahlulele izizwana ezilitshumi lambili zako-Israyeli.</char> <verse eid="MAT 19:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 19:29"/><char style="wj">Njalo bonke labo abatshiye izindlu zabo, loba abafowabo, loba odadewabo kumbe uyise loba unina kumbe abantwana loba amasimu ngenxa yami bazakwamukeliswa okwandiswe ngekhulu njalo bazakudla ilifa lokuphila okungapheliyo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 19:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 19:30"/><char style="wj">Kodwa abanengi abangabokuqala bazakuba ngabokucina njalo abanengi abangabokucina bazakuba ngabokuqala.”</char><verse eid="MAT 19:30"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 19"/>
  <chapter number="20" style="c" sid="MAT 20"/>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wezisebenzi Esivinini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 20:1"/>
    <char style="wj">“Ngoba umbuso wezulu unjengomlimi owaphuma ekuseni kakhulu wayaqhatsha amadoda okusebenza esivinini sakhe.</char> <verse eid="MAT 20:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 20:2"/><char style="wj">Wathembisa ukubaholisa idenari okwalolosuku wasebathumela esivinini sakhe.</char><verse eid="MAT 20:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 20:3"/>
    <char style="wj">Waphuma njalo ngehola lesificamunwemunye ekuseni wabona abanye bezimele nje emsikeni bengenzi lutho.</char> <verse eid="MAT 20:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 20:4"/><char style="wj">Wabatshela wathi, ‘Lani hambani liyesebenza esivinini sami, ngizaliholisa okufaneleyo.’</char> <verse eid="MAT 20:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 20:5"/><char style="wj">Ngakho bahamba.</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 20:5">
    <char style="wj">Wabuye waphuma emini sekubanga ihola lesithathu emini wenza okufanayo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 20:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 20:6"/><char style="wj">Sekusondele ihola lesihlanu waphuma wafumana abanye bezimele nje khonapho. Wababuza wathi, ‘Kungani belilokhu limi lapha ilanga lonke lingenzi lutho na?’</char><verse eid="MAT 20:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 20:7"/>
    <char style="wj">Bamphendula bathi, ‘Ngoba kakho osiqhatshileyo.’</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 20:7">
    <char style="wj">Wathi kubo, ‘Lani hambani liyesebenza esivinini sami.’</char><verse eid="MAT 20:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 20:8"/>
    <char style="wj">Kwathi sekuntambama, umninisivini wathi enduneni yezinceku, ‘Biza izinceku uziphe iholo lazo, uqalise ngabokucina usehla usiya kwabokuqala.’</char><verse eid="MAT 20:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 20:9"/>
    <char style="wj">Izinceku ezaqhatshwa sekubanga ihola lesihlanu ntambama zeza ngamunye zaphiwa idenari.</char> <verse eid="MAT 20:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 20:10"/><char style="wj">Kwathi sekufike labo abaqhatshwa kuqala balindela ukuphiwa okwedlulayo. Kodwa ngamunye wabo waphiwa idenari.</char> <verse eid="MAT 20:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 20:11"/><char style="wj">Bonela ukuyamukela baqalisa ukumsola umnininsimu besithi,</char> <verse eid="MAT 20:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 20:12"/><char style="wj">‘Lababantu abaqhatshwe ekucineni basebenze ihola elilodwa kuphela kodwa usubalinganise lathi thina esithwale kanzima ngomsebenzi sitshiswa lilanga usuku lonke.’</char><verse eid="MAT 20:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 20:13"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa waphendula omunye wabo wathi, ‘Mnakwethu, angikudlelezeli ngalutho. Kawuvumanga yini ukusebenzela idenari?</char> <verse eid="MAT 20:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 20:14"/><char style="wj">Thatha umholo wakho uhambe. Mina ngithanda ukupha indoda leyo eqhatshwe muva okulingana lalokho engikunike khona.</char> <verse eid="MAT 20:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 20:15"/><char style="wj">Kangilalungelo na lokwenza loba yini engiyithandayo ngemali yami? Kumbe ulomhawu ngokuphana kwami na?’</char><verse eid="MAT 20:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 20:16"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngakho owokucina uzakuba ngowokuqala, lowokuqala abe ngowokucina.”</char><verse eid="MAT 20:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ukhuluma Ngokufa Kwakhe Njalo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 20:17"/>Kwathi uJesu esesiya eJerusalema wathatha abafundi abalitshumi lambili wema labo eceleni wathi kubo, <verse eid="MAT 20:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 20:18"/><char style="wj">“Sesisiya eJerusalema lapho iNdodana yoMuntu ezanikelwa khona kubaphristi abakhulu labafundisi bomthetho. Bazayigwebela ukufa,</char> <verse eid="MAT 20:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 20:19"/><char style="wj">bayinikele kwabeZizwe ukuba iyangiswe, itshaywe njalo ibethelwe. Ngosuku lwesithathu izavuswa kwabafileyo!”</char><verse eid="MAT 20:19"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isicelo Somzali Wesifazane</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 20:20"/>Kwasekufika unina wamadodana kaZebhediya kuJesu elamadodana akhe waguqa phansi wacela ukuthi enzelwe umusa.<verse eid="MAT 20:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 20:21"/>UJesu wabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Kuyini okufunayo?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 20:21">Yena wathi, “Tshono ukuthi omunye wala amadodana ami amabili uzahlala kwesokunene sakho kuthi omunye laye ahlale kwesokhohlo sakho embusweni wakho.”<verse eid="MAT 20:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 20:22"/>UJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Kalikwazi elikucelayo. Lingayinatha na inkezo engizayinatha?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 20:22">Bathi, “Yebo singayinatha.”<verse eid="MAT 20:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 20:23"/>UJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Yebo lizanatha kuyo inkezo yami kodwa ukuhlala kwesokunene kumbe kwesokhohlo kwami kakusikho kwami ukukuvumela. Izindawo lezi ngezalabo abazilungiselwe nguBaba.”</char><verse eid="MAT 20:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 20:24"/>Kwathi abalitshumi bekuzwa lokhu bazithukuthelela lezozelamani. <verse eid="MAT 20:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 20:25"/>UJesu wasebabizela ndawonye wathi, <char style="wj">“Liyakwazi ukuthi ababusi beZizwe bazibusa kalukhuni, kuthi lezikhulu zazo zikhonye phezu kwazo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 20:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 20:26"/><char style="wj">Kakunjalo kini. Kodwa loba ngubani ofuna ukuba mkhulu phakathi kwenu kabe yinceku yenu,</char> <verse eid="MAT 20:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 20:27"/><char style="wj">lalowo ofuna ukuba ngowokuqala kabe yinceku yenu,</char> <verse eid="MAT 20:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 20:28"/><char style="wj">njengalokhu iNdodana yoMuntu ingezanga ukuzokhonzwa kodwa ukuzokhonza lokunikela impilo yayo njengenhlawulo yabanengi.”</char><verse eid="MAT 20:28"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Iziphofu Ezimbili Zenziwa Zibone</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 20:29"/>Kwathi uJesu labafundi bakhe sebesuka eJerikho ixuku elikhulu labantu lamlandela. <verse eid="MAT 20:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 20:30"/>Amadoda amabili ayiziphofu ayehlezi eceleni komgwaqo athi esizwa ukuthi uJesu wayesedlula khonapho amemeza athi, “Nkosi, Ndodana kaDavida, sihawukele!”<verse eid="MAT 20:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 20:31"/>Ixuku labantu lawakhuza lathi kawathule kodwa amemeza ngamandla athi, “Nkosi, Ndodana kaDavida, sihawukele!”<verse eid="MAT 20:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 20:32"/>UJesu wema wawabiza, wawabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Lifuna ukuba ngilenzeleni?”</char><verse eid="MAT 20:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 20:33"/>Aphendula athi, “Nkosi, sifuna ukuthi sibone.”<verse eid="MAT 20:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 20:34"/>UJesu wawazwela isihawu wawathinta emehlweni. Masinyane nje ahle abona asemlandela.<verse eid="MAT 20:34"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 20"/>
  <chapter number="21" style="c" sid="MAT 21"/>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uza EJerusalema NjengeNkosi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 21:1"/>Bathi sebesondela eJerusalema, bafika eBhethifage eNtabeni yama-Oliva, uJesu wathuma abafundi ababili, <verse eid="MAT 21:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 21:2"/>wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Yanini emzini ophambi kwenu, khonapho lizabona inkonyane kababhemi lobabhemi ebotshelwe khonapho. Libakhulule libuye labo kimi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 21:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 21:3"/><char style="wj">Nxa kungaba lozalibuza, limtshele ukuthi iNkosi yiyo ebafunayo, uzahle abayekele bahambe masinyane.”</char><verse eid="MAT 21:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 21:4"/>Lokhu kwenzeka ukuze kugcwaliseke okwakhulunywa ngomphrofethi ukuthi:<verse eid="MAT 21:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 21:5"/>“Tshela iNdodakazi yaseZiyoni ukuthi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 21:5">‘Khangela, inkosi yakho iyeza kuwe,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 21:5">imnene igade ubabhemi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 21:5">iphezu kwenkonyane, inkonyane kababhemi.’<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">21.5 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UZakhariya 9.9</char></note>”<verse eid="MAT 21:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 21:6"/>Abafundi bahamba benza njengokulaywa kwabo nguJesu. <verse eid="MAT 21:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 21:7"/>Baletha inkonyane kababhemi lobabhemi, bendlala amajazi abo phezu kwabobabhemi ukuze uJesu ahlale phezu kwawo. <verse eid="MAT 21:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 21:8"/>Ixuku elikhulu lendlala amajazi alo endleleni, kukanti abanye bephula ingatsha ezihlahleni bazendlala endleleni. <verse eid="MAT 21:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 21:9"/>Amaxuku ayehamba phambi kwakhe lalawo ayelandela amemeza athi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 21:9">“Hosana kuyo iNdodana kaDavida!”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">21.9 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 118.26</char></note></para>
  <para style="b" vid="MAT 21:9"/>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 21:9">“Ubusisiwe lowo obuya ngebizo likaThixo!”</para>
  <para style="b" vid="MAT 21:9"/>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 21:9">“Hosana ezulwini eliphezulu!”<verse eid="MAT 21:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 21:10"/>Kwathi uJesu esengenile eJerusalema, umuzi wonke wanyakazela, abantu babuzana bathi, “Kanti ngubani lo?”<verse eid="MAT 21:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 21:11"/>Amaxuku aphendula athi, “Lo nguJesu, umphrofethi waseNazaretha eGalile.”<verse eid="MAT 21:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu EThempelini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 21:12"/>UJesu wangena egumeni lethempeli wabaxotsha bonke ababethenga lababethengisa khona. Wagenqula amatafula alabo ababentshintshela abanye izimali lezihlalo zabathengisa amajuba. <verse eid="MAT 21:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 21:13"/>Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Kulotshiwe ukuthi, ‘Indlu yami izabizwa ngokuthi yindlu yokukhuleka,’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">21.13 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 56.7</char></note> <char style="wj">kodwa lina seliyenza ‘ubhalu lwabaphangi.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">21.13 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UJeremiya 7.11</char></note><char style="wj">”</char><verse eid="MAT 21:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 21:14"/>Iziphofu labaqhugezelayo beza kuye ethempelini wabasilisa. <verse eid="MAT 21:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 21:15"/>Kodwa kwathi abaphristi abakhulu labafundisi bomthetho bebona izimanga ayezenza labantwana bememeza egumeni lethempeli besithi, “Hosana kuyo iNdodana kaDavida,” banengeka.<verse eid="MAT 21:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 21:16"/>Bambuza bathi, “Uyabezwa nje abantwana laba ukuthi bathini?”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">21.16 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 8.2</char></note></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 21:16">Waphendula uJesu wathi, <char style="wj">“Yebo, kalikaze lifunde ukuthi,</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 21:16">
    <char style="wj">‘Ezindebeni zabantwana lensane</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 21:16">
    <char style="wj">wena Nkosi uyimisile indumiso’?”</char><verse eid="MAT 21:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 21:17"/>Wasebatshiya waphuma edolobheni waya eBhethani lapho alala khona.<verse eid="MAT 21:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isihlahla Somkhiwa Siyabuna</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 21:18"/>Ekuseni kakhulu esebuyela edolobheni wezwa eselambile. <verse eid="MAT 21:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 21:19"/>Wabona isihlahla somkhiwa eceleni kwendlela, waqambukela kuso kodwa wathola kungelalutho kuso ngaphandle kwamahlamvu nje. Wasesithi kuso, <char style="wj">“Ungaphindi uthele izithelo lanini!”</char> Khonapho nje isihlahla sahle sabuna.<verse eid="MAT 21:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 21:20"/>Abafundi bathi bekubona lokhu bamangala kakhulu. Babuza bathi, “Kwenzeke kanjani ukuthi isihlahla somkhiwa sibune masinyane kangaka?”<verse eid="MAT 21:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 21:21"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngilitshela iqiniso ngithi nxa lilokukholwa njalo lingathandabuzi, kalisoze lenze okwenziwe kulesi isihlahla somkhiwa kuphela kodwa njalo lingathi kule intaba, ‘Suka, uziphosele olwandle,’ lakanye kuzenzeka.</char> <verse eid="MAT 21:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 21:22"/><char style="wj">Nxa likholwa, lizaphiwa loba yini eliyicelayo ngomkhuleko.”</char><verse eid="MAT 21:22"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Kubuzwa Ngemvelo Yamandla KaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 21:23"/>UJesu wangena ethempelini, kwathi elokhu efundisa abaphristi abakhulu labadala babantu beza kuye. Bambuza bathi, “Izinto lezi uzenza ngawaphi amandla na? Ngubani okunike amandla la?”<verse eid="MAT 21:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 21:24"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Lami ngizalibuza umbuzo owodwa. Lingangiphendula, ngizalitshela ukuthi ngizenza ngawaphi amandla lezizinto.</char> <verse eid="MAT 21:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 21:25"/><char style="wj">Ubhaphathizo lukaJohane lwavela ngaphi na? Lwavela ezulwini loba ebantwini na?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 21:25">Bangunguna bodwa ngalokho bathi, “Nxa singathi, ‘Lwavela ezulwini,’ uzakuthi, ‘Pho kungani lingazange limkholwe na?’ <verse eid="MAT 21:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 21:26"/>Kodwa singathi, ‘Lwavela ebantwini,’ sesaba abantu ngoba bonke uJohane bamthatha njengomphrofethi.”<verse eid="MAT 21:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 21:27"/>Ngakho bamphendula uJesu bathi, “Kasikwazi.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 21:27">Ngakho wasesithi, <char style="wj">“Lami kangiyikulitshela ukuthi izinto lezi ngizenza ngamandla bani.”</char><verse eid="MAT 21:27"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wamadodana Amabili</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 21:28"/>
    <char style="wj">“Likhumbulani kambe? Kwakulendoda eyayilamadodana amabili. Yaya kweyokuqala yathi, ‘Ndodana, lamuhla hamba uyesebenza esivinini.’</char><verse eid="MAT 21:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 21:29"/>
    <char style="wj">Yaphendula yathi, ‘Kangisoze ngiye mina,’ kodwa yaphinde yazisola yahamba.</char><verse eid="MAT 21:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 21:30"/>
    <char style="wj">Uyise wasesiya kwenye indodana watsho okufanayo. Yaphendula yathi, ‘Ngizahamba, baba,’ kodwa kayihambanga.</char><verse eid="MAT 21:30"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 21:31"/>
    <char style="wj">Yiphi phakathi kwawo womabili eyenza lokho okwakufunwa nguyise na?”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 21:31">Baphendula bathi, “Ngeyakuqala.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 21:31">UJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Ngilitshela iqiniso ngithi abathelisi lezifebe bazangena embusweni kaNkulunkulu kuqala kulani.</char> <verse eid="MAT 21:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 21:32"/><char style="wj">Ngoba uJohane weza kini ukuzalitshengisa indlela yokulunga kodwa kalimkholwanga ikanti abathelisi lezifebe bamkholwa. Kwathi lokuba selikubonile konke lokhu kalimkholwanga.”</char><verse eid="MAT 21:32"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wabalimi Esivinini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 21:33"/>
    <char style="wj">“Zwanini omunye umzekeliso: Kwakukhona umnini wesiqinti owahlanyela isivini. Wasihonqolozela ngomduli, wagebha isikhamelo sewayini phakathi, wasesakha isilindo. Waseqhatshisa isivini leso kubalimi wasuka wathatha uhambo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 21:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 21:34"/><char style="wj">Kuthe sekufika isikhathi sokuvuna wathuma izinceku zakhe kulabobalimi ukuyathatha izithelo.</char><verse eid="MAT 21:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MAT 21:35"/>
    <char style="wj">Abalimi bazibamba izinceku zakhe; eyinye bayitshaya, eyinye bayibulala kwathi eyesithathu bayikhanda ngamatshe.</char> <verse eid="MAT 21:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MAT 21:36"/><char style="wj">Wasethuma ezinye izinceku kubo, ezinengi kulezakuqala, njalo abalimi baziphatha ngendlela efanayo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 21:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MAT 21:37"/><char style="wj">Ekucineni wasethumela indodana yakhe kubo. Wathi, ‘Bazayihlonipha indodana yami.’</char><verse eid="MAT 21:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="MAT 21:38"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa kwathi abalimi beyibona indodana batshelana bathi, ‘Lo yindlalifa. Wozani simbulale sithathe ilifa lakhe.’</char> <verse eid="MAT 21:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MAT 21:39"/><char style="wj">Ngakho bamdumela bamphosela ngaphandle kwesivini bambulala.</char><verse eid="MAT 21:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="MAT 21:40"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngakho-ke nxa umninisivini esesiza uzabathini abalimi labo na?”</char><verse eid="MAT 21:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="MAT 21:41"/>Baphendula bathi, “Uzababonisa into yamehlo, abeseqhatshisa isivini sakhe kwabanye abalimi abazamnika ingxenye yakhe yezithelo ngesikhathi sokuvuna.”<verse eid="MAT 21:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="MAT 21:42"/>UJesu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Kalibalanga yini emibhalweni ukuthi:</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 21:42">
    <char style="wj">‘Ilitshe elalahlwa ngabakhi</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 21:42">
    <char style="wj">seliyilona ilitshe lensika;</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 21:42">
    <char style="wj">iNkosi ikwenzile lokhu,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 21:42">
    <char style="wj">njalo kuyamangalisa emehlweni ethu?’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">21.42 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 118.22-23</char>
    </note><verse eid="MAT 21:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="MAT 21:43"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngakho ngiyalitshela ukuthi umbuso kaNkulunkulu lizawuthathelwa uphiwe abantu abazathela izithelo zawo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 21:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="MAT 21:44"/><char style="wj">Lowo ozawela phezu kwalelilitshe uzavadlaka kodwa lowo elizawela phezu kwakhe uzafihlizwa.”</char><verse eid="MAT 21:44"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="MAT 21:45"/>Kwathi abaphristi abakhulu labaFarisi besizwa imizekeliso kaJesu, bakwazi ukuthi wayekhuluma ngabo. <verse eid="MAT 21:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="MAT 21:46"/>Badinga indlela yokumbopha kodwa besaba ixuku labantu ngoba abantu bambona njengomphrofethi.<verse eid="MAT 21:46"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 21"/>
  <chapter number="22" style="c" sid="MAT 22"/>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wedili Lomthimba</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 22:1"/>UJesu wakhuluma kubo njalo ngemizekeliso wathi: <verse eid="MAT 22:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 22:2"/><char style="wj">“Umbuso wezulu unjengenkosi eyalungisela indodana yayo idili lomthimba.</char> <verse eid="MAT 22:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 22:3"/><char style="wj">Yathuma izinceku zayo kulabo ababenxusiwe edilini ukuba beze kodwa bala ukuza.</char><verse eid="MAT 22:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 22:4"/>
    <char style="wj">Yaphinda yathuma ezinye izinceku yathi, ‘Batsheleni labo abanxusiweyo ukuthi sengililungisile idili. Ngihlabe inkabi lenkomo ezinonisiweyo, konke sekulungile. Wozani edilini lomthimba.’</char><verse eid="MAT 22:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 22:5"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa kabakunanzanga lokho, bazihambela, omunye waya ensimini yakhe, omunye emsebenzini wakhe.</char> <verse eid="MAT 22:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 22:6"/><char style="wj">Abanye bazibamba izinceku zayo, bazihlukuluza bazibulala.</char> <verse eid="MAT 22:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 22:7"/><char style="wj">Inkosi yathukuthela. Yathumela impi yayo yababhuqa labobabulali yatshisa idolobho labo.</char><verse eid="MAT 22:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 22:8"/>
    <char style="wj">Yasisithi ezincekwini zayo, ‘Idili lomthimba selilungile kodwa labo engibanxusileyo bebengasafanele ukuza.</char> <verse eid="MAT 22:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 22:9"/><char style="wj">Hambani liye emahlanganweni ezindlela linxuse loba ngubani elimbonayo.’</char> <verse eid="MAT 22:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 22:10"/><char style="wj">Ngakho izinceku zangena ezitaladini zabutha bonke abantu ezababonayo, abalungileyo lababi, indlu yomthimba yagcwala izethekeli.</char><verse eid="MAT 22:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 22:11"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa kwathi inkosi ingena ukuzabona izethekeli, yananzelela khonapho indoda eyeyingavunulanga izigqoko zomthimba.</char> <verse eid="MAT 22:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 22:12"/><char style="wj">Yabuza yathi, ‘Mngane, ungene njani lapha ungelazigqoko zomthimba?’ Indoda yatsha amathe.</char><verse eid="MAT 22:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 22:13"/>
    <char style="wj">Inkosi yasitshela izinceku zayo yathi, ‘Mbopheni izandla lezinyawo limphosele ngaphandle ebumnyameni, lapho okuzakuba khona ukukhala lokugedla kwamazinyo.’</char><verse eid="MAT 22:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 22:14"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngoba banengi ababiziweyo kodwa balutshwana abakhethiweyo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 22:14"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuthela KuKhesari</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 22:15"/>Lapho-ke abaFarisi basuka baphuma bayaceba ukuthi bambambe ngamazwi akhe. <verse eid="MAT 22:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 22:16"/>Bathuma abafundi babo kuye behamba lamaHerodiya. Bathi, “Mfundisi, siyazi ukuthi uyindoda eqotho lokuthi ufundisa indlela kaNkulunkulu ngokweqiniso. Kawusuye uthathekile ngoba kawulani lokuthi bangobani. <verse eid="MAT 22:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 22:17"/>Sitshele-ke, uthini ngalokhu? Kusemthethweni na ukuthela kuKhesari kumbe hatshi?”<verse eid="MAT 22:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 22:18"/>UJesu ngokwazi inhloso yabo embi wathi, <char style="wj">“Lina bazenzisi, lenzani lizama ukungithiya na?</char> <verse eid="MAT 22:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 22:19"/><char style="wj">Ake lingitshengise uhlamvu lwemali okuthelwa ngayo.”</char> Bamlethela idenari, <verse eid="MAT 22:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 22:20"/>wasebabuza wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngumfanekiso kabani lo? Njalo luphawu lukabani lolu?”</char><verse eid="MAT 22:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 22:21"/>Baphendula bathi, “NgokukaKhesari.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 22:21">Wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Phanini uKhesari okungokukaKhesari loNkulunkulu okungokukaNkulunkulu.”</char><verse eid="MAT 22:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 22:22"/>Bathi besizwa lokhu bamangala. Ngakho basuka kuye bahamba.<verse eid="MAT 22:22"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukuthathana Ekuvukeni Kwabafileyo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 22:23"/>Ngalelolanga abaSadusi, abathi kakukho ukuvuka kwabafileyo, beza kuye belombuzo. <verse eid="MAT 22:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 22:24"/>Bathi, “Mfundisi, uMosi wasitshela wathi, nxa indoda ingafa ingazalanga mntwana, umfowabo kamthathe umfelokazi amzalele abantwana. <verse eid="MAT 22:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 22:25"/>Kwakulabafowabo abayisikhombisa phakathi kwethu. Wathatha owakuqala wasesifa, kwathi ngoba engazuzanga mntwana watshiyela umkakhe umfowabo. <verse eid="MAT 22:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 22:26"/>Kwaphinda lokho kowesibili lowesithathu njalo kwaze kwaba ngowesikhombisa. <verse eid="MAT 22:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 22:27"/>Ekucineni wafa lowomfazi. <verse eid="MAT 22:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 22:28"/>Pho-ke, ekuvukeni kwabafileyo uzakuba ngumkabani phakathi kwabayisikhombisa njengoba bonke babemthethe?”<verse eid="MAT 22:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 22:29"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Liyalahleka ngoba kaliyazi imibhalo lamandla kaNkulunkulu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 22:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 22:30"/><char style="wj">Ekuvukeni kwabafileyo abantu kabayikuthatha loba bendiswe; bazakuba njengezingilosi ezulwini.</char> <verse eid="MAT 22:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 22:31"/><char style="wj">Kodwa mayelana lokuvuka kwabafileyo, kalibalanga yini lokho uNkulunkulu akutsho kini ukuthi,</char> <verse eid="MAT 22:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 22:32"/><char style="wj">‘NginguNkulunkulu ka-Abhrahama, uNkulunkulu ka-Isaka loNkulunkulu kaJakhobe’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">22.32 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">U-Eksodasi 3.6</char></note><char style="wj">? KasuNkulunkulu wabafileyo kodwa owabaphilayo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 22:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 22:33"/>Kwathi amaxuku abantu esizwa lokhu amangaliswa yikufundisa kwakhe.<verse eid="MAT 22:33"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umlayo Omkhulu Kulayo Yonke</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 22:34"/>AbaFarisi sebezwile ukuthi uJesu wayesebathulisile abaSadusi, bahlangana ndawonye. <verse eid="MAT 22:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MAT 22:35"/>Omunye wabo owayeyisazi somthetho wamlinga ngombuzo wathi, <verse eid="MAT 22:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MAT 22:36"/>“Mfundisi, yiwuphi umlayo omkhulu kulayo yonke eMthethweni?”<verse eid="MAT 22:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="MAT 22:37"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“ ‘Thanda iNkosi uNkulunkulu wakho ngenhliziyo yakho yonke langomphefumulo wakho wonke langengqondo yakho yonke.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">22.37 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UDutheronomi 6.5</char></note> <verse eid="MAT 22:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MAT 22:38"/><char style="wj">Yiwo owokuqala njalo odlula yonke imilayo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 22:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MAT 22:39"/><char style="wj">Owesibili unjengawo: ‘Thanda umakhelwane wakho njengoba uzithanda wena.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">22.39 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">ULevi 19.18</char></note> <verse eid="MAT 22:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MAT 22:40"/><char style="wj">Wonke uMthetho labaPhrofethi kweyeme kuyonale imilayo emibili.”</char><verse eid="MAT 22:40"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UKhristu UyiNdodana Kabani?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="MAT 22:41"/>Kwathi abaFarisi behlangene ndawonye uJesu wababuza wathi, <verse eid="MAT 22:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MAT 22:42"/>“Licabangani ngoKhristu? Uyindodana kabani?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 22:42">Baphendula bathi, “Yindodana kaDavida.”<verse eid="MAT 22:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="MAT 22:43"/>Wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Kungani pho uDavida wathi ekhuluma ngoMoya umbiza athi ‘Nkosi’? Ngoba uthi,</char><verse eid="MAT 22:43"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="MAT 22:44"/>
    <char style="wj">‘INkosi yathi eNkosini yami:</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 22:44">
    <char style="wj">“Hlala ngakwesokunene sami</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 22:44">
    <char style="wj">ngize ngibeke izitha zakho</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 22:44">
    <char style="wj">ngaphansi kwenyawo zakho.” ’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">22.44 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 110.1</char>
    </note><verse eid="MAT 22:44"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="MAT 22:45"/>
    <char style="wj">Pho, nxa uDavida esithi kuye, ‘Nkosi,’ angaba yindodana yakhe njani?”</char> <verse eid="MAT 22:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="MAT 22:46"/>Kakho loyedwa owaba lelizwi lokumphendula. Kwathi-ke kusukela ngalolosuku kakho owaqunga isibindi sokumbuza eminye imibuzo.<verse eid="MAT 22:46"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 22"/>
  <chapter number="23" style="c" sid="MAT 23"/>
  <para style="s1">Izixwayiso Eziyisikhombisa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 23:1"/>UJesu wasesithi emaxukwini abantu lakubafundi bakhe: <verse eid="MAT 23:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 23:2"/><char style="wj">“Abafundisi bomthetho labaFarisi bahlezi esihlalweni sikaMosi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 23:3"/><char style="wj">Ngakho kumele libalalele lenze konke abalitshela khona. Kodwa lingakwenzi abakwenzayo, ngoba kabakulandeli lokho abakutshumayelayo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 23:4"/><char style="wj">Baqoqa imithwalo enzima bayetshate emahlombe abantu kodwa bona bengafuni lokulokotha bayithwale.</char><verse eid="MAT 23:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 23:5"/>
    <char style="wj">Konke abakwenzayo bakwenzela ukuba babonwe ngabantu, benza imicwatsho yabo yemibhalo ibe banzi lezintshaka zezigqoko zabo zibe zinde;</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 23:6"/><char style="wj">bathanda izindawo eziphezulu emadilini lezihlalo eziqakathekileyo emasinagogweni,</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 23:7"/><char style="wj">bathanda ukubingelelwa emisikeni lokuthi abantu bababize ngokuthi ‘Rabi.’</char><verse eid="MAT 23:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 23:8"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa lina nxa lingabizwa kuthiwe ‘Rabi,’ ngoba munye kuphela oyiNkosi yenu njalo lina lonke liyizinini.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 23:9"/><char style="wj">Futhi lingabizi muntu emhlabeni ngokuthi ‘baba,’ ngoba liloYihlo oyedwa, yena osezulwini.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 23:10"/><char style="wj">Njalo lingabizwa ngokuthi bafundisi, ngoba liloMfundisi oyedwa, uKhristu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 23:11"/><char style="wj">Omkhulu kulani lonke phakathi kwenu uzakuba yinceku yenu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 23:12"/><char style="wj">Ngoba lowo oziphakamisayo uzathotshiswa, lalowo ozithobayo uzaphakanyiswa.”</char><verse eid="MAT 23:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Inhlupheko Eziyikhombisa Kubafundisi Bomthetho LakubaFarisi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 23:13"/>
    <char style="wj">“Maye kini, bafundisi bomthetho lakubaFarisi, lina bazenzisi! Livalela abantu umbuso wezulu. Lina ngokwenu kalingeni liphinde livimbele labo abazama ukungena.</char> [<verse eid="MAT 23:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 23:14"/><char style="wj">Maye kini bafundisi bomthetho lakini baFarisi, lina bazenzisi! Liphanga izindlu zabafelokazi, beselizenzisa lisenza imikhuleko emide, ngalokho lizakwamukeliswa ukulahlwa okukhulu.</char>]<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">23.14 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Livesi ayikho kwamanye amaBhayibhili esiLungu.</char></note><verse eid="MAT 23:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 23:15"/>
    <char style="wj">Maye kini bafundisi bomthetho lakini baFarisi, lina bazenzisi! Lidabula ilizwe lihambe laphezu kolwandle lidinga ukuphendula oyedwa zwi, lithi selimzuzile limphendule abe yindodana yesihogweni okuphindwe kabili kulani.</char><verse eid="MAT 23:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 23:16"/>
    <char style="wj">Maye kini, baholi abayiziphofu! Lithi, ‘Nxa umuntu efunga ngethempeli kakutsho lutho; kodwa nxa umuntu efunga ngegolide lethempeli usezibophile ngesifungo sakhe.’</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 23:17"/><char style="wj">Lina ziphofundini! Yikuphi okukhulu kulokunye: igolide kumbe ithempeli elenza igolide libengcwele?</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 23:18"/><char style="wj">Lithi njalo, ‘Nxa umuntu efunga nge-alithare, akusilutho; kodwa nxa umuntu efunga ngesipho esikulo usezibophile ngesifungo sakhe.’</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 23:19"/><char style="wj">Lina ziphofu zabantu! Yikuphi okudlula okunye: isipho langabe i-alithari elenza isipho sibe ngcwele?</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 23:20"/><char style="wj">Ngakho lowo ofunga nge-alithare ufunga ngalo langakho konke okukulo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 23:21"/><char style="wj">Njalo lowo ofunga ngethempeli ufunga ngalo njalo langaye lowo ohlala kulo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 23:22"/><char style="wj">Njalo lalowo ofunga ngezulu ufunga ngesihlalo sobukhosi sikaNkulunkulu langaye ohlezi phezu kwaso.</char><verse eid="MAT 23:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 23:23"/>
    <char style="wj">Maye kini, bafundisi bomthetho lakini baFarisi, bazenzisi! Linika okwetshumi okweziyoliso zenu, iminti ledili lekhamini. Kodwa liyekethise izinto ezimqoka emthethweni, eziyikulunga, isihawu kanye lokwethembeka. Bekufanele lithi likwenza lokhu lingawuyekethisanga umthetho.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 23:24"/><char style="wj">Lina baholi abayiziphofu! Liyacenga ukukhupha ubuyane kodwa liginye ikamela.</char><verse eid="MAT 23:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 23:25"/>
    <char style="wj">Maye kini, bafundisi bomthetho lakini baFarisi, lina bazenzisi! Ligezisa inkezo lomganu ngaphandle kodwa ngaphakathi kugcwele ubuhwaba lokuzisuthisa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 23:26"/><char style="wj">MFarisi oyisiphofu! Qala uhlambulule ingaphakathi yenkezo lomganu, ukuze ingaphandle layo ihlambuluke.</char><verse eid="MAT 23:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 23:27"/>
    <char style="wj">Maye kini, bafundisi bomthetho lakini baFarisi, lina bazenzisi! Linjengamathuna aconjiweyo, akhanya ebukeka ngaphandle, kodwa ngaphakathi agcwele amathambo abantu abafileyo lakho konke okungcolileyo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 23:28"/><char style="wj">Kanjalo, ngaphandle libonakala ebantwini linjengabalungileyo, kodwa ngaphakathi ligcwele ukuzenzisa lobubi.</char><verse eid="MAT 23:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 23:29"/>
    <char style="wj">Maye kini, bafundisi bomthetho lakini baFarisi, lina bazenzisi! Lakhela abaphrofethi amathuna njalo licecise amathuna abalungileyo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 23:30"/><char style="wj">Beselisithi, ‘Ngabe saphila ngezinsuku zabokhokho bethu sasingeyikuhlanganyela labo ekuchitheni igazi labaphrofethi.’</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 23:31"/><char style="wj">Ngalokho yini elipha ubufakazi bokuthi liyisizukulwane salabo ababulala abaphrofethi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 23:32"/><char style="wj">Nanko-ke, wohlani liqedise lesosono sabokhokho benu!</char><verse eid="MAT 23:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 23:33"/>
    <char style="wj">Lina zinyoka! Lina nzalo yezinhlangwana! Lizaphepha kanjani ukuba lilahlelwe esihogweni na?</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 23:34"/><char style="wj">Ngakho ngilithumela abaphrofethi lamadoda ahlakaniphileyo labafundisi. Abanye babo lizababulala libabethele; abanye lizababhaxabula emasinagogweni enu, lilandelelane labo kuleli laleliyana idolobho.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MAT 23:35"/><char style="wj">Ngakho-ke, lonke igazi elilungileyo elachithwayo emhlabeni kusukela egazini lika-Abheli owayelungile kusiya egazini likaZakhariya indodana kaBherekhiya elambulala phakathi laphakathi kwethempeli le-alithari lizakwehliselwa phezu kwenu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MAT 23:36"/><char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso, konke lokhu kuzakuba phezu kwalesi isizukulwane.</char><verse eid="MAT 23:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="MAT 23:37"/>
    <char style="wj">Jerusalema, Jerusalema, wena obulala abaphrofethi, ubakhande ngamatshe labo abathunywe kuwe, sekukanengi ngiloyisa ukuqoqa ndawonye abantwabakho, njengesikhukhukazi siqoqa amatsiyane aso ngaphansi kwamaphiko aso, kodwa wena wawungathandi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MAT 23:38"/><char style="wj">Khangela, indlu yakho isitshiywe ilunxiwa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 23:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MAT 23:39"/><char style="wj">Ngoba ngiyalitshela, kalisayikungibona futhi lize lithi, ‘Ubusisiwe lowo obuya ngebizo likaThixo.’</char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">23.39 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 118.26</char></note><char style="wj">”</char><verse eid="MAT 23:39"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 23"/>
  <chapter number="24" style="c" sid="MAT 24"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukubhidlizwa KweThempeli Lezibonakaliso Zokucina Kwesikhathi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 24:1"/>UJesu wathi esuka ethempelini esehamba abafundi bakhe beza kuye bathi kake ananzelele izakhiwo zalo. <verse eid="MAT 24:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 24:2"/>Wathi, <char style="wj">“Liyazibona na zonke lezizinto? Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi akulalitshe lapha elizasala liphezu kwelinye; wonke azabhidlizwa.”</char><verse eid="MAT 24:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 24:3"/>Kwathi uJesu ehlezi eNtabeni yama-Oliva abafundi bakhe beza kuye ngasese bathi, “Sitshele, kuzakwenzakala nini lokhu na, njalo kuzakuba lesibonakaliso bani sokuza kwakho lokuphela kwesikhathi na?”<verse eid="MAT 24:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 24:4"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Qaphelani ukuze lingakhohliswa muntu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 24:5"/><char style="wj">Ngoba abanengi bazakuza ngebizo lami besithi, ‘NginguKhristu,’ bakhohlise abanengi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 24:6"/><char style="wj">Lizakuzwa ngezimpi lamahungahunga azo, kodwa lingaze lethuka. Izinto ezinjalo zizakwenzeka, kodwa ukucina kulokhu kuseza.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 24:7"/><char style="wj">Isizwe sizavukela isizwe, lombuso uvukele umbuso. Kuzakuba lendlala lokuzamazama komhlaba ezindaweni ezitshiyeneyo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 24:8"/><char style="wj">Konke lokhu kuyikuqalisa kobuhlungu bokuhelelwa.</char><verse eid="MAT 24:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 24:9"/>
    <char style="wj">Lapho lizanikelwa ukuba lihlutshwe njalo libulawe, futhi lizazondwa yizizwe zonke ngenxa yami.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 24:10"/><char style="wj">Ngalesosikhathi abanengi bazadela ukukholwa banikelane njalo bazondane,</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 24:11"/><char style="wj">kuvele abaphrofethi bamanga abanengi abazakhohlisa abantu abanengi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 24:12"/><char style="wj">Ngenxa yokwanda kobubi, uthando lwabanengi luzaphola,</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 24:13"/><char style="wj">kodwa lowo oma aqine kuze kube sekupheleni uzasindiswa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 24:14"/><char style="wj">Njalo lelivangeli lombuso lizatshunyayelwa kuwo wonke umhlaba njengobufakazi kuzozonke izizwe, besekufika ukuphela.</char><verse eid="MAT 24:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 24:15"/>
    <char style="wj">Nxa libona kumi endaweni engcwele ‘amanyala aletha incithakalo,’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">24.15 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">UDanyeli 9.27; 11.31; 12.11</char>
    </note> <char style="wj">okwakhulunywa ngomphrofethi uDanyeli, ofundayo kezwisise.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 24:16"/><char style="wj">Lapho-ke akuthi labo abaseJudiya babalekele ezintabeni.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 24:17"/><char style="wj">Akungabikhona osophahleni lwendlu ozakwehla phansi ukuyathatha ulutho endlini.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 24:18"/><char style="wj">Lowo osemasimini kangabuyeli ngekhaya ukuyathatha ijazi lakhe.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 24:19"/><char style="wj">Yeka ubulukhuni obuzakuba khona ngalezonsuku kwabesifazane abakhulelweyo labangabadlezane!</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 24:20"/><char style="wj">Khulekelani ukuba ukuphaphatheka kwenu kungabi sebusika loba ngeSabatha.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 24:21"/><char style="wj">Ngoba ngalesosikhathi kuzakuba lokuhlupheka okukhulu, okungazange kube khona kulokhu kwadabuka umhlaba kuze kube manje, njalo kakusoze kube khona futhi.</char><verse eid="MAT 24:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 24:22"/>
    <char style="wj">Aluba lezinsuku bezingaphungulwanga, kakho obezaphepha, kodwa ngenxa yabakhethiweyo lezinsuku zizaphungulwa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 24:23"/><char style="wj">Nxa ngalesosikhathi omunye esithi kini, ‘Khangela, nangu uKhristu!’ loba ‘Ulaphaya!’ lingakukholwa lokho.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 24:24"/><char style="wj">Ngoba oKhristu bamanga labaphrofethi bamanga bazavela benze izibonakaliso lezimangaliso ezinkulu ukukhohlisa kanye labakhethiweyo, nxa lokho kungenzeka.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 24:25"/><char style="wj">Zwanini, sengihle ngalitshela mandulo kwesikhathi.</char><verse eid="MAT 24:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 24:26"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngakho-ke, nxa umuntu elitshela esithi, ‘Nanguyana, laphayana egangeni,’ lingayi khona loba athi, ‘Nangu lapha ezindlini ezingaphakathi,’ lingaze lakukholwa lokho.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 24:27"/><char style="wj">Ngoba njengombane osuka empumalanga uhle ubonakale lasentshonalanga, kuzakuba njalo ukufika kweNdodana yoMuntu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 24:28"/><char style="wj">Lapho okulesidumbu khona kulapho amanqe abuthana khona.</char><verse eid="MAT 24:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 24:29"/>
    <char style="wj">Masinyane ngemva kokuhlupheka kwalezonsuku,</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 24:29">
    <char style="wj">‘ilanga lizafiphala</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 24:29">
    <char style="wj">lenyanga kayiyikukhanya;</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 24:29">
    <char style="wj">izinkanyezi zizakuwa esibhakabhakeni,</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 24:29">
    <char style="wj">izisekelo zasezulwini zizazanyazanyiswa.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">24.29 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">U-Isaya 13.10; 34.4</char>
    </note><verse eid="MAT 24:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 24:30"/>
    <char style="wj">Kulesosikhathi isibonakaliso seNdodana yoMuntu sizavela emkhathini, kuthi zonke izizwe zomhlaba zilile. Zizabona iNdodana yoMuntu isiza ngamayezi esibhakabhakeni, ilamandla lobukhosi obukhulu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 24:31"/><char style="wj">Njalo izathumela izingilosi zayo zitshaya icilongo ngomsindo omkhulu, beseziqoqa abakhethiweyo bayo emagumbini womane omhlaba, kusukela ngapha kwamazulu kusiya ngale kwawo.</char><verse eid="MAT 24:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 24:32"/>
    <char style="wj">Manje-ke, fundani lesisifundo esihlahleni somkhiwa: Amahlumela aso angaqalisa ukuba buthakathaka lamahlamvu aso ahlume, lihle lazi ukuthi ihlobo selisondele.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 24:33"/><char style="wj">Kanjalo-ke, nxa lingabona zonke lezizinto, lazi ukuthi sekusondele, khonapho emnyango.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 24:34"/><char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso, lesisizukulwane kasiyikudlula zize zenzakale zonke lezizinto.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MAT 24:35"/><char style="wj">Izulu lomhlaba kuzedlula, kodwa amazwi ami kawayikwedlula lanini.”</char><verse eid="MAT 24:35"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Usuku Lehola Kakwaziwa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="MAT 24:36"/>
    <char style="wj">“Kodwa kakho olwaziyo lolosuku lehola, loba izingilosi zasezulwini, kumbe iNdodana, kodwa uBaba kuphela.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MAT 24:37"/><char style="wj">Njengoba kwakunjalo ensukwini zikaNowa, kuzakuba njalo ekufikeni kweNdodana yoMuntu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MAT 24:38"/><char style="wj">Ngoba ensukwini ezandulela uzamcolo, abantu babesidla, benatha, bethatha njalo besenda, kwaze kwafika usuku uNowa angena ngalo emkhunjini;</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MAT 24:39"/><char style="wj">futhi babengazi lutho ngalokho okwakuzakwenzeka uzamcolo waze wafika wabatshabalalisa. Kuzakuba njalo ekufikeni kweNdodana yoMuntu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MAT 24:40"/><char style="wj">Kuzakuthi amadoda emabili esensimini, eyodwa izathathwa, eyinye isale.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="MAT 24:41"/><char style="wj">Kuzakuthi abesifazane bebabili bechola ngembokodo, oyedwa uzathathwa omunye asale.</char><verse eid="MAT 24:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="MAT 24:42"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngakho, lindani ngoba kalikwazi ukuthi iNkosi yenu izafika ngaluphi usuku.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="MAT 24:43"/><char style="wj">Kodwa zwisisani lokhu: Kube umninindlu wayekwazile ukuthi isela lizafika ngasiphi isikhathi sobusuku ngabe walinda kaze avumela ukuthi indlu yakhe igqekezwe.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="MAT 24:44"/><char style="wj">Ngakho lani hlalani lilindile, ngoba iNdodana yoMuntu izafika ngesikhathi leso elizabe lingayikhumbuleli sona.</char><verse eid="MAT 24:44"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="MAT 24:45"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngubani kambe oyinceku ethembekileyo lehlakaniphileyo umninimuzi ayibeke esikhundleni sokukhangela izisebenzi zalapha ekhaya ukuthi azinike ukudla kwazo ngesikhathi esifaneleyo?</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="MAT 24:46"/><char style="wj">Kuzakuba kuhle kuleyo nceku inkosi ezayifica isenza njalo ekuphendukeni kwayo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="MAT 24:47"/><char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso, izakumbeka ukuthi aphathe yonke impahla yayo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="MAT 24:48"/><char style="wj">Kodwa cabanga mhlawumbe inceku leyo ikhohlakele njalo ingazitshela ithi, ‘Inkosi yami isesekhatshana ukubuya,’</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="MAT 24:49"/><char style="wj">ibisiqalisa ukutshaya ezinye izinceku njalo lokudla inatha lezidakwa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:49"/><verse number="50" style="v" sid="MAT 24:50"/><char style="wj">Inkosi yaleyonceku izabuya ngosuku engacatshangelwa khona langesikhathi inceku engasaziyo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 24:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="MAT 24:51"/><char style="wj">Izayiqumaquma, iyiphe indawo kanye labazenzisi, lapho okuzakuba khona ukukhala lokugedla kwamazinyo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 24:51"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 24"/>
  <chapter number="25" style="c" sid="MAT 25"/>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wezintombi Ezilitshumi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 25:1"/>
    <char style="wj">“Kulesosikhathi umbuso wezulu uzakuba njengezintombi ezigcweleyo ezilitshumi ezathatha izibane zazo zaphuma ukuyahlangabeza umyeni.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 25:2"/><char style="wj">Ezinhlanu zazo zaziyiziwula, ezinhlanu zihlakaniphile.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 25:3"/><char style="wj">Eziyiziwula zathatha izibane zazo, kodwa kazithathanga amafutha.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 25:4"/><char style="wj">Kodwa ezihlakaniphileyo zathwala imbodlela zamafutha kanye lezibane zazo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 25:5"/><char style="wj">Umyeni waphuza ukufika zonke zaze zawozela zajunywa yibuthongo.</char><verse eid="MAT 25:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 25:6"/>
    <char style="wj">Phakathi kobusuku kwamenyezelwa kwathiwa, ‘Nangu umyeni! Phumani limhlangabeze!’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 25:7"/>
    <char style="wj">Zasezivuka zonke izintombi zalumathisa izibane zazo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 25:8"/><char style="wj">Lezo ezaziyiziwula zathi kwezihlakaniphileyo, ‘Ake lisiphe lathi amanye amafutha enu; izibane zethu sezicitsha.’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 25:9"/>
    <char style="wj">Zaphendula ezihlakaniphileyo zathi, ‘Hatshi, kakulamafutha angasanela thina lani. Hambani liye kulabo abathengisa amafutha liyezithengela awenu.’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 25:10"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa kwathi besayathenga amafutha umyeni wafika. Izintombi ezazizilungiselele zangena laye edilini lomthimba. Umnyango wasuvalwa.</char><verse eid="MAT 25:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 25:11"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngemva kwesikhathi ezinye lazo zatsho sezifikile. Zathi, ‘Nkosi! Nkosi! Ake usivulele umnyango!’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 25:12"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa waphendula wathi, ‘Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi, kangilazi.’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 25:13"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngakho lindani ngoba kalilwazi usuku loba ihola.”</char><verse eid="MAT 25:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umzekeliso Wamathalenta</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 25:14"/>
    <char style="wj">“Njalo unjengendoda eyathatha uhambo, yabiza izinceku zayo yazigcinisa impahla yayo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 25:15"/><char style="wj">Oyedwa yamupha amathalenta amahlanu emali, omunye amabili omunye njalo ithalenta elilodwa, ngulowo kusiya ngamandla akhe. Yasisuka ingena uhambo lwayo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 25:16"/><char style="wj">Leyondoda eyayiphiwe amathalenta amahlanu yahle yasuka yayayisebenzisa leyomali yazuza amanye amahlanu.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 25:17"/><char style="wj">Yenza njalo laleyo eyayiphiwe amabili, yazuza amanye amabili.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 25:18"/><char style="wj">Kodwa indoda eyayiphiwe ithalenta elilodwa yasuka yemba igodi emhlabathini yayifihla imali yenkosi yayo.</char><verse eid="MAT 25:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 25:19"/>
    <char style="wj">Ngemva kwesikhathi eside umnini walezozinceku wabuya wafisa ukwazi ukuthi babehambise njani ngaleyomali.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 25:20"/><char style="wj">Leyondoda eyayiphiwe amathalenta amahlanu yaletha amanye amahlanu. Yathi, ‘Nkosi, wangethemba ngamathalenta amahlanu. Khangela, sengizuze amanye amahlanu.’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 25:21"/>
    <char style="wj">Umnini wayo waphendula wathi, ‘Wenze kuhle, nceku elungileyo lethembekileyo! Uthembekile ezintweni ezilutshwane; ngizakugcinisa izinto ezinengi. Woza uzojabula kanye lenkosi yakho!’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 25:22"/>
    <char style="wj">Indoda eyayilamathalenta amabili layo yeza. Yathi, ‘Nkosi, wangethemba ngamathalenta amabili; khangela, sengizuze amanye amabili.’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 25:23"/>
    <char style="wj">Umniniyo waphendula wathi, ‘Wenze kuhle, nceku elungileyo lethembekileyo! Uthembekile ngezinto ezilutshwane; ngizakugcinisa izinto ezinengi. Woza uzojabula kanye lenkosi yakho!’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 25:24"/>
    <char style="wj">Kwasekusiza leyondoda eyayiphiwe ithalenta elilodwa. Yathi, ‘Nkosi, bengikwazi ukuthi uyindoda elukhuni, evuna lapho engahlanyelanga khona njalo ibuthe lapho engazange ihaze khona inhlanyelo.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 25:25"/><char style="wj">Yikho ngesaba ngasuka ngayafihla ithalenta lakho emhlabathini. Khangela, nanku okungokwakho.’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 25:26"/>
    <char style="wj">Inkosi yaphendula yathi, ‘Wena nceku embi lelivila! Utsho ukuthi wazile ukuthi ngivuna lapho engingahlanyelanga khona njalo ngibuthe lapho engingahazanga khona inhlanyelo?</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 25:27"/><char style="wj">Kube imali yami uyifake ebhanga, ukuze kuthi ekubuyeni kwami ngiyizuze isizele.</char><verse eid="MAT 25:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 25:28"/>
    <char style="wj">Mthatheleni ithalenta lelo liliphe lowo olamathalenta alitshumi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 25:29"/><char style="wj">Ngoba lowo olakho uzaphiwa okunye njalo abesesiba lokunengi. Lowo ongelakho, lalokho alakho uzakwemukwa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 25:30"/><char style="wj">Manje-ke, iphoseni ngaphandle inceku engelamsebenzi, ebumnyameni lapho okuzakuba khona ukukhala lokugedla kwamazinyo.’ ”</char><verse eid="MAT 25:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Izimvu Lembuzi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 25:31"/>
    <char style="wj">“Nxa iNdodana yoMuntu isisiza ngenkazimulo yayo, ikanye lezingilosi zonke, izahlala esihlalweni sayo sobukhosi ilenkazimulo yasezulwini.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 25:32"/><char style="wj">Zonke izizwe zizabuthaniswa phambi kwayo, ibe isisahlukanisa abantu omunye komunye njengomelusi esehlukanisa izimvu embuzini.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 25:33"/><char style="wj">Izabeka izimvu ngasekwesokunene kwayo lembuzi ngakwesokhohlo.</char><verse eid="MAT 25:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 25:34"/>
    <char style="wj">Lapho-ke iNkosi izakuthi kulabo abangakwesokunene sayo, ‘Wozani, lina elibusiswe nguBaba; thathani ilifa lenu, umbuso owalungiselwa lina kusukela ekudalweni komhlaba.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MAT 25:35"/><char style="wj">Ngoba ngangilambile, langinika ulutho oludliwayo, ngangomile langipha okunathwayo, ngangiyisihambi langinxusela endlini,</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MAT 25:36"/><char style="wj">ngangiswele izembatho langigqokisa, ngangigula langonga, ngangisentolongweni lazongibona.’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:36"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="MAT 25:37"/>
    <char style="wj">Abalungileyo bazamphendula bathi, ‘Nkosi, sakubona nini ulambile sakupha ukudla na, kumbe womile sakunathisa?</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MAT 25:38"/><char style="wj">Sakubona nini uyisihambi sakunxusela endlini na, kumbe uswele izembatho sakugqokisa?</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MAT 25:39"/><char style="wj">Sakubona nini ugula kumbe usentolongweni seza sazakubona na?’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="MAT 25:40"/>
    <char style="wj">INkosi izaphendula ithi, ‘Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi loba yini elayenzela loba ngomncinyane kanganani walaba abazalwane bami, lakwenzela mina.’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="MAT 25:41"/>
    <char style="wj">INkosi izakuthi kulabo abakwesokhohlo sayo, ‘Xekani kimi lina eliqalekisiweyo liye emlilweni ongapheliyo owalungiselwa uSathane lezingilosi zakhe.</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MAT 25:42"/><char style="wj">Ngoba ngangilambile, kalingiphanga lutho lokudla, ngangomile kalingiphanga lutho lokunatha,</char> <verse eid="MAT 25:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="MAT 25:43"/><char style="wj">ngangiyisihambi kalinginxuselanga endlini, ngangiswele izembatho kalingigqokisanga, ngangigula njalo ngisentolongweni kalizange lingethekelele.’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:43"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="MAT 25:44"/>
    <char style="wj">Labo bazaphendula bathi, ‘Nkosi, sakubona nini ulambile kumbe womile kumbe uyisihambi kumbe ungelazigqoko kumbe ugula noma usentolongweni asaze sakunceda na?’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:44"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="MAT 25:45"/>
    <char style="wj">Izaphendula ithi, ‘Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi, loba kuyini elingakwenzelanga oyedwa nje omncinyane kulabo bonke walaba, kalikwenzelanga mina.’</char><verse eid="MAT 25:45"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="MAT 25:46"/>
    <char style="wj">Bazasuka baye ekujezisweni kwaphakade, kodwa abalungileyo baye ekuphileni okungapheliyo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 25:46"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 25"/>
  <chapter number="26" style="c" sid="MAT 26"/>
  <para style="s1">Icebo Elibi NgoJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 26:1"/>UJesu eseqedile ukukhuluma zonke lezi izinto, wathi kubafundi bakhe, <verse eid="MAT 26:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 26:2"/><char style="wj">“Njengoba lisazi, sekusele insuku ezimbili ukuba iPhasika lifike, njalo iNdodana yoMuntu izanikelwa ukuba ibethelwe.”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 26:3"/>Abaphristi abakhulu labadala babantu basebeqoqana egumeni lomphristi omkhulu owayethiwa nguKhayifasi, <verse eid="MAT 26:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 26:4"/>baceba ukubopha uJesu ngasese bambulale. <verse eid="MAT 26:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 26:5"/>Bathi, “Kakungabi ngesikhathi somkhosi funa kube lesiphithiphithi ebantwini.”<verse eid="MAT 26:5"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Uyagcotshwa EBhethani</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 26:6"/>Kwathi uJesu eseBhethani endlini yendoda eyayithiwa nguSimoni owayelobulephero, <verse eid="MAT 26:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 26:7"/>kweza kuye owesifazane ephethe imbodlela yamakha adula kakhulu wawathela ekhanda likaJesu owayeyeme etafuleni.<verse eid="MAT 26:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 26:8"/>Abafundi bathi bekubona lokho bacasuka. Basebebuza bathi, “Adlaliselwani kanje na? <verse eid="MAT 26:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 26:9"/>Amakha la abengathengiswa ngemali ephezulu leyomali iphiwe abampofu.”<verse eid="MAT 26:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 26:10"/>UJesu esekunanzelele lokhu wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Limkhathazelani owesifazane lo na? Wenze into enhle kimi.</char> <verse eid="MAT 26:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 26:11"/><char style="wj">Abampofu lizahlala lilabo kokuphela, kodwa kalisoze libe lami kokuphela.</char> <verse eid="MAT 26:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 26:12"/><char style="wj">Uthe ethululela amakha la emzimbeni wami ubesenzela ukungilungiselela ukungcwatshwa.</char> <verse eid="MAT 26:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 26:13"/><char style="wj">Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi langaphi lapho okuzatshunyayelwa ivangeli leli emhlabeni wonke, lokhu akwenzileyo kuzakhulunywa, kube yisikhumbuzo ngaye.”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJudasi Uvuma Ukunikela UJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 26:14"/>Kwathi omunye wabalitshumi lambili, lowo owayethiwa nguJudasi Iskariyothi, waya kubaphristi abakhulu <verse eid="MAT 26:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 26:15"/>wabuza wathi, “Lizangiphani nxa ngimnikela kini?” Base bembalela inhlamvu zesiliva ezingamatshumi amathathu. <verse eid="MAT 26:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 26:16"/>Kusukela khonapho uJudasi wadinga ithuba lokuba amnikele.<verse eid="MAT 26:16"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Isidlo SeNkosi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 26:17"/>Ngosuku lokuqala loMkhosi weSinkwa esingelaMvubelo abafundi beza kuJesu bambuza bathi, “Ufuna senzele ngaphi amalungiselelo okuthi udle iPhasika na?”<verse eid="MAT 26:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 26:18"/>Waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngenani edolobheni komunye umuntu limtshele lithi, ‘UMfundisi uthi: Isikhathi sami esimisiweyo sesiseduze. Ngizakudla iPhasika labafundi bami endlini yakho.’ ”</char> <verse eid="MAT 26:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 26:19"/>Ngakho abafundi benza njengokulayelwa kwabo nguJesu balungisa iPhasika.<verse eid="MAT 26:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 26:20"/>Kwathi kusihlwa, uJesu wayehlezi eyeme etafuleni elabalitshumi lambili. <verse eid="MAT 26:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 26:21"/>Kwathi besidla wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngilitshela iqiniso ukuthi omunye wenu uzanginikela.”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 26:22"/>Badana kakhulu basebesithi kuye ngamunye, “Pho kawutsho mina Nkosi?”<verse eid="MAT 26:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 26:23"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Lowo odle kanye lami emganwini uzanginikela.</char> <verse eid="MAT 26:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 26:24"/><char style="wj">INdodana yoMuntu kwenzakala kuyo njengoba kulotshiwe ngayo. Kodwa maye kulowomuntu ozanikela iNdodana yoMuntu! Bekungaba ngcono kuye ngabe wayengazalwanga.”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 26:25"/>Wasesithi uJudasi, lowo owayezamnikela, “Pho kawutsho mina, Rabi?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 26:25">UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Yebo, nguwe okutshoyo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 26:26"/>Bathi besadla uJesu wathatha isinkwa wabonga, wasihlephula wasipha abafundi bakhe esithi, <char style="wj">“Thathani lidle; lokhu kungumzimba wami.”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 26:27"/>Wasethatha inkezo, esebongile, wabanika esithi, <char style="wj">“Nathani kuyo, lonke.</char> <verse eid="MAT 26:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 26:28"/><char style="wj">Leli ligazi lami lesivumelwano, elichithelwe abanengi ekuthethelelweni kwezono.</char> <verse eid="MAT 26:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 26:29"/><char style="wj">Ngiyalitshela, angisayikuphinda nginathe okwesithelo sevini, kusukela manje kuze kube yilolosuku lapho engizakunatha khona kabutsha lani embusweni kaBaba.”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:29"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 26:30"/>Bathi sebehlabele ihubo baphuma baya eNtabeni yama-Oliva.<verse eid="MAT 26:30"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ubonisa Ngokuphika KukaPhethro</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 26:31"/>UJesu wasebatshela wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngabona lobubusuku lizakwenyela ngami, ngoba kulotshiwe ukuthi:</char></para>
  <para style="q1" vid="MAT 26:31">
    <char style="wj">‘Ngizatshaya umelusi</char></para>
  <para style="q2" vid="MAT 26:31">
    <char style="wj">izimvu zomhlambi zizahlakazeka.’</char>
    <note caller="+" style="f">
      <char style="fr" closed="false">26.31 </char>
      <char style="ft" closed="false">UZakhariya 13.7</char>
    </note><verse eid="MAT 26:31"/></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 26:32"/>
    <char style="wj">Kodwa ngemva kokuba sengivukile kwabafileyo, ngizalandulela ukuya eGalile.”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 26:33"/>UPhethro waphendula wathi, “Loba bonke bangaze benyele ngenxa yakho, mina kimi ngezake kwenzeke.”<verse eid="MAT 26:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 26:34"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Ngikutshela iqiniso ukuthi ngabona lobubusuku, iqhude lingakakhali uzangiphika kathathu.”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:34"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="MAT 26:35"/>Kodwa uPhethro wala wagomela wathi, “Loba kungenzeka ukuba ngife lawe, ngeke lanini ngikuphike.” Abanye abafundi labo batsho njalo.<verse eid="MAT 26:35"/></para>
  <para style="s1">EGetsemane</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="MAT 26:36"/>UJesu wasehamba labafundi bakhe endaweni eyayithiwa yiGetsemane, wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Hlalani lapha, mina ngisaya laphayana ukuyakhuleka.”</char> <verse eid="MAT 26:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MAT 26:37"/><char style="wj">Wathatha uPhethro lamadodana kaZebhediya womabili wahamba labo, waseqala ukuhlulukelwa lokukhathazeka.</char> <verse eid="MAT 26:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="MAT 26:38"/>Wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Umphefumulo wami ugajelwa lusizi kuze kuthi ngife. Hlalani lapha lilinde lami.”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="MAT 26:39"/>Wahamba ibanganyana, wazilahla phansi wathi mbo ngobuso wakhuleka wathi, <char style="wj">“Baba, nxa kungenzeka, sengathi inkezo le ingasuswa kimi. Kodwa akungabi yintando yami, kodwa kube yintando yakho.”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:39"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="MAT 26:40"/>Wasephenduka kubafundi bakhe wabafica belele. Wabuza uPhethro wathi, <char style="wj">“Lina madoda kambe kulehlule ukulinda kanye lami okwehola elilodwa nje?</char> <verse eid="MAT 26:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="MAT 26:41"/><char style="wj">Lindani likhuleke ukuze lingaweli ekulingweni. Umoya uyathanda kodwa umzimba ubuthakathaka.”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:41"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="MAT 26:42"/>Wahamba njalo okwesibili wakhuleka wathi, <char style="wj">“Baba wami, nxa kungenzeki ukuthi linkezo isuswe ngaphandle kokuthi ngiyinathe, intando yakho mayenziwe.”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="MAT 26:43"/>Wathi esebuya wabafica njalo sebelele, ngoba amehlo abo ayenzima. <verse eid="MAT 26:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="MAT 26:44"/>Ngakho wasebatshiya waphinda wahamba njalo wayakhuleka okwesithathu ephinda into yinye.<verse eid="MAT 26:44"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="MAT 26:45"/>Wasebuyela kubafundi wathi kubo, <char style="wj">“Lilele, liyaphumula na? Khangelani, isikhathi sesisondele, iNdodana yoMuntu isizanikelwa ezandleni zezoni.</char> <verse eid="MAT 26:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="MAT 26:46"/><char style="wj">Phakamani! Kasihambeni! Nangu usesiza onginikelayo.”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:46"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubotshwa KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="MAT 26:47"/>Wathi esakhuluma, uJudasi, omunye wabalitshumi lambili wafika. Wayehamba lexuku elikhulu lihlomile ngezinkemba lezinduku lithunywe ngabaphristi abakhulu labadala babantu. <verse eid="MAT 26:47"/><verse number="48" style="v" sid="MAT 26:48"/>Omnikelayo wayelungisile labo isiboniso wathi: “Lowo engizamanga nguye; mbopheni.” <verse eid="MAT 26:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="MAT 26:49"/>UJudasi wahle waqonda kuJesu wathi, “Sabona, Rabi!” wamanga.<verse eid="MAT 26:49"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="MAT 26:50"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Mfowethu, yenza lokho okulandileyo.”</char></para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 26:50">Asesondela amadoda, amdumela uJesu ambopha. <verse eid="MAT 26:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="MAT 26:51"/>Khonapho omunye wabaphelekezeli bakaJesu wakhokha inkemba yakhe wagadla encekwini yomphristi omkhulu, wayiquma indlebe.<verse eid="MAT 26:51"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="52" style="v" sid="MAT 26:52"/>UJesu wathi kuye, <char style="wj">“Buyisela inkemba yakho endaweni yayo, ngoba bonke abakhokha inkemba bazakufa ngenkemba.</char> <verse eid="MAT 26:52"/><verse number="53" style="v" sid="MAT 26:53"/><char style="wj">Ucabanga ukuthi ngingaze ngacela kuBaba, masinyane nje angiphe amaviyo alitshumi lambili ezingilosi?</char> <verse eid="MAT 26:53"/><verse number="54" style="v" sid="MAT 26:54"/><char style="wj">Kodwa phela ibingagcwaliseka kanjani imibhalo ethi kumele kwenzeke ngale indlela na?”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:54"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="55" style="v" sid="MAT 26:55"/>Khonapho uJesu wathi exukwini labantu, <char style="wj">“Kanti ngikhokhela umvukela yini lize lihlome ngezinkemba lezinduku ukuzangibamba na? Insuku zonke ngangihlala emagumeni ethempeli ngifundisa, kodwa kalingibophanga.</char> <verse eid="MAT 26:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="MAT 26:56"/><char style="wj">Kodwa lokhu kwenzeke ukuze kugcwaliseke imibhalo yabaphrofethi.”</char> Khonapho abafundi bonke bamtshiya babaleka.<verse eid="MAT 26:56"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Phambi KweSanihedrini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="57" style="v" sid="MAT 26:57"/>Labo abambophayo uJesu bamusa kuKhayifasi, umphristi omkhulu, lapho okwasekubuthene khona abafundisi bomthetho labadala. <verse eid="MAT 26:57"/><verse number="58" style="v" sid="MAT 26:58"/>Kodwa uPhethro wayemlandela ehambela khatshana waze wayangena egumeni lomphristi omkhulu. Wangena wahlala phansi lamanxusa efuna ukubona okwakuzakwenzakala.<verse eid="MAT 26:58"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="59" style="v" sid="MAT 26:59"/>Abaphristi abakhulu leSanihedrini yonke babedinga ubufakazi bamanga ngoJesu ukuze bambulale. <verse eid="MAT 26:59"/><verse number="60" style="v" sid="MAT 26:60"/>Kodwa babuswela, lanxa abanengi ofakazi bamanga bavela.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 26:60">Ekucineni ababili beza phambili <verse eid="MAT 26:60"/><verse number="61" style="v" sid="MAT 26:61"/>bathi, “Umfokazi lo wathi, ‘Ngilamandla okulidiliza ithempeli likaNkulunkulu ngiphinde ngilakhe kutsha ngezinsuku ezintathu.’ ”<verse eid="MAT 26:61"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="62" style="v" sid="MAT 26:62"/>Umphristi omkhulu wasesukuma wathi kuJesu, “Kawuyikuphendula na? Kuyini kanti lokhu okufakazwa ngamadoda la ngawe na?” <verse eid="MAT 26:62"/><verse number="63" style="v" sid="MAT 26:63"/>Kodwa uJesu wala elokhu ethule.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 26:63">Umphristi omkhulu wathi kuye, “Ngiyakulaya, ngifunga ngoNkulunkulu ophilayo ngithi: Sitshele ingabe unguKhristu, iNdodana kaNkulunkulu.”<verse eid="MAT 26:63"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="64" style="v" sid="MAT 26:64"/>UJesu waphendula wathi, <char style="wj">“Yebo, kunjengoba usitsho. Kodwa ngithi kini lonke: Ngesikhathi esizayo lizayibona iNdodana yoMuntu ihlezi kwesokunene sikaMninimandla isehla ngamayezi ezulwini.”</char><verse eid="MAT 26:64"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="65" style="v" sid="MAT 26:65"/>Khonapho umphristi omkhulu wadabula izigqoko zakhe wathi, “Uyahlambaza! Sisafunelani abanye ofakazi na? Khangelani, manje selikuzwile ukuhlambaza. <verse eid="MAT 26:65"/><verse number="66" style="v" sid="MAT 26:66"/>Lithini ngakho?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 26:66">Baphendula bathi, “Ufanele ukufa.”<verse eid="MAT 26:66"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="67" style="v" sid="MAT 26:67"/>Basebemkhafulela emehlweni njalo bamdutshuza ngenqindi. Abanye bamakala <verse eid="MAT 26:67"/><verse number="68" style="v" sid="MAT 26:68"/>bathi, “Phrofitha kithi, wena Khristu. Ngubani okutshayileyo?”<verse eid="MAT 26:68"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UPhethro Ulandula UJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="69" style="v" sid="MAT 26:69"/>UPhethro wayehlezi phandle egumeni, kwasekusiza kuye intombazana eyincekukazi yathi kuye, “Lawe njalo wawuloJesu waseGalile.”<verse eid="MAT 26:69"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="70" style="v" sid="MAT 26:70"/>Kodwa walandula phambi kwabo bonke. Wathi, “Angikwazi lokho okhuluma ngakho.”<verse eid="MAT 26:70"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="71" style="v" sid="MAT 26:71"/>Wasesuka ephuma entubeni lapho abonwa khona ngenye intombazana eyathi ebantwini khonapho, “Umfokazi lo wayeloJesu waseNazaretha.”<verse eid="MAT 26:71"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="72" style="v" sid="MAT 26:72"/>Walandula njalo efunga esithi, “Kangiyazi indoda leyo!”<verse eid="MAT 26:72"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="73" style="v" sid="MAT 26:73"/>Ngemva kwesikhatshana labo ababemi khonapho baya kuPhethro bathi, “Ngempela ungomunye wabo ngoba indlela okhuluma ngayo iyakuceba.”<verse eid="MAT 26:73"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="74" style="v" sid="MAT 26:74"/>Wasekhihliza iziqalekiso phezu kwakhe wafunga kubo wathi, “Angimazi mina lowomuntu!”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 26:74">Masinyane iqhude lakhala. <verse eid="MAT 26:74"/><verse number="75" style="v" sid="MAT 26:75"/>UPhethro waselikhumbula ilizwi elakhulunywa nguJesu esithi: <char style="wj">“Iqhude lingakakhali uzangilandula kathathu.”</char> Waphumela ngaphandle wakhala kabuhlungu.<verse eid="MAT 26:75"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 26"/>
  <chapter number="27" style="c" sid="MAT 27"/>
  <para style="s1">UJudasi Uyazibophela</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 27:1"/>Ekuseni ngovivi bonke abaphristi abakhulu labadala babantu benza isinqumo sokumbulala uJesu. <verse eid="MAT 27:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 27:2"/>Bambopha, bamqhuba, bamnikela kuPhilathu umbusi.<verse eid="MAT 27:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 27:3"/>Kwathi uJudasi, owayemnikele, esebona ukuthi uJesu wayesegwetshiwe, wadabuka ngokuzisola, wabuyisela inhlamvu zesiliva ezingamatshumi amathathu kubaphristi abakhulu labadala. <verse eid="MAT 27:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 27:4"/>Wathi, “Ngenze isono, ngoba nginikele igazi elingelacala.”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 27:4">Baphendula bathi, “silani lalokho thina? Lokho kungumlandu wakho.”<verse eid="MAT 27:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 27:5"/>Ngakho uJudasi wayiphosela ethempelini leyomali wahamba. Wasuka lapho wayazibophela.<verse eid="MAT 27:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 27:6"/>Abaphristi abakhulu bazidobha inhlamvu zemali lezo bathi, “Kungaphandle komthetho ukufaka imali le esitsheni somnikelo ngoba yimali yegazi.” <verse eid="MAT 27:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 27:7"/>Ngakho basebemisa ukuyisebenzisa ukuthenga isiqinti sombumbi sibe yindawo yamangcwaba abantu bezizweni. <verse eid="MAT 27:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 27:8"/>Yikho yabizwa ngokuthi yiNsimu yeGazi kuze kube namuhla. <verse eid="MAT 27:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 27:9"/>Kwasekugcwaliseka okwakhulunywa nguJeremiya umphrofethi ukuthi: “Bathatha inhlamvu zesiliva ezingamatshumi amathathu, intengo eyamiswa ngaye ngabantu bako-Israyeli, <verse eid="MAT 27:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 27:10"/>bazisebenzisa ukuthenga insimu yombumbi, njengokulaywa kwami yiNkosi.”<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">27.10 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">UZakhariya 11.12-13; UJeremiya 19.1-13; 32.6-9</char></note><verse eid="MAT 27:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UJesu Ephambi KukaPhilathu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 27:11"/>Ngalesosikhathi uJesu wamiswa phambi kombusi, umbusi wasebuza wathi, “Uyinkosi yamaJuda na?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 27:11">
    <char style="wj">“Njengoba usitsho,”</char> kuphendula uJesu.<verse eid="MAT 27:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 27:12"/>Wayesithi nxa ethonisiswa ngabaphristi abakhulu labadala angaze aphendula. <verse eid="MAT 27:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 27:13"/>UPhilathu wasembuza wathi, “Awubuzwa yini ubufakazi abakwethesa bona?” <verse eid="MAT 27:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 27:14"/>Kodwa uJesu wathula, kazaphendula lamlandu munye, okwamangalisa umbusi kakhulu.<verse eid="MAT 27:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 27:15"/>Kwakungumkhuba wakhe umbusi ukuthi ngomkhosi akhulule isibotshwa esikhethwe lixuku labantu. <verse eid="MAT 27:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 27:16"/>Ngalesosikhathi kwakulesibotshwa esasigange kubi, sithiwa nguJesu isibongo saso singuBharabhasi. <verse eid="MAT 27:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 27:17"/>Kuthe abantu sebebuthene uPhilathu wababuza wathi, “Lifuna ngilikhululele wuphi na, uBharabhasi loba uJesu othiwa nguKhristu?” <verse eid="MAT 27:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 27:18"/>Ngoba wayesazi ukuthi kwakungenxa yomhawu okwenza banikela uJesu kuye.<verse eid="MAT 27:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 27:19"/>Kwathi uPhilathu esahlezi esihlalweni sakhe sokwahlulela, umkakhe wamthumela ilizwi wathi: “Ungayingeni indaba yomuntu lowo ongelacala, ngoba lamuhla ngihluphekile kakhulu ngaye emaphutsheni.”<verse eid="MAT 27:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 27:20"/>Kodwa abaphristi abakhulu labadala bakhuthaza abantu ukuthi bacele uBharabhasi, bathi uJesu kabulawe.<verse eid="MAT 27:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="MAT 27:21"/>Wabuza umbusi wathi, “Lifuna ngilikhululele wuphi phakathi kwalaba ababili na?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 27:21">Baphendula bathi, “UBharabhasi.”<verse eid="MAT 27:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="MAT 27:22"/>UPhilathu wabuza wathi, “Pho ngenzeni ngoJesu othiwa nguKhristu?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 27:22">Bonke bamphendula bathi, “Mbethele!”<verse eid="MAT 27:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="MAT 27:23"/>UPhilathu wabuza wathi, “Yindaba? Woneni?”</para>
  <para style="p" vid="MAT 27:23">Kodwa bamemeza ngamandla bathi, “Mbethele!”<verse eid="MAT 27:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="MAT 27:24"/>Kwathi uPhilathu esebona ukuthi akusela enye indlela, kwasekuzavuka isiyaluyalu, wathatha amanzi wageza izandla zakhe phambi kwexuku wathi, “Angilacala ngegazi lalumuntu. Ngumlandu wenu!”<verse eid="MAT 27:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="MAT 27:25"/>Bonke abantu bamphendula bathi, “Yekela igazi lakhe libe phezu kwethu laphezu kwabantwabethu!”<verse eid="MAT 27:25"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="MAT 27:26"/>Wasebakhululela uBharabhasi. Wathi uJesu katshaywe, wasemnikeza ukuba abethelwe.<verse eid="MAT 27:26"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amabutho Aklolodela UJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="MAT 27:27"/>Amabutho ombusi asemthatha uJesu amngenisa ePhritoriyamu, inkundla yombusi, wabuthanelwa liviyo lonke lamabutho. <verse eid="MAT 27:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="MAT 27:28"/>Bamkhulula izigqoko zakhe bamgqokisa ijazi elibomvu, <verse eid="MAT 27:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="MAT 27:29"/>basebeseluka umqhele wameva bamethesa wona. Bamphathisa intonga kwesokunene sakhe baguqa phambi kwakhe bamklolodela. Bathi, “Bayethe, Nkosi yamaJuda!” <verse eid="MAT 27:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="MAT 27:30"/>Bamkhafulela, bamthathela lowomqwayi bamtshaya bemphindaphinda ekhanda. <verse eid="MAT 27:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="MAT 27:31"/>Sebemklolodele, bamhlubula ijazi bamgqokisa ezakhe. Basebemqhuba besiya mbethela.<verse eid="MAT 27:31"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukubethelwa Kwakhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="MAT 27:32"/>Bathi sebephumela ngaphandle bahlangana lendoda yaseKhureni, ethiwa nguSimoni, bayibamba ngamandla ukuthi ithwale isiphambano. <verse eid="MAT 27:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="MAT 27:33"/>Bafika endaweni ethiwa kuseGoligotha (okutsho ukuthi “Indawo yoKhakhayi”). <verse eid="MAT 27:33"/><verse number="34" style="v" sid="MAT 27:34"/>Khonapho uJesu bamupha iwayini ukuba anathe, lixutshaniswe lenyongo; kodwa wonela ukulinambitha wasesala ukulinatha. <verse eid="MAT 27:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="MAT 27:35"/>Kwathi sebembethele behlukaniselana izigqoko zakhe ngokwenza inkatho. <verse eid="MAT 27:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="MAT 27:36"/>Bahlala phansi bamlinda khonapho. <verse eid="MAT 27:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="MAT 27:37"/>Phezu kwekhanda lakhe babeka umbhalo wecala lakhe owawusithi,</para>
  <para style="pc" vid="MAT 27:37">Lo nguJesu, iNkosi yamaJuda.<verse eid="MAT 27:37"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="MAT 27:38"/>Izigebenga ezimbili zabethelwa kanye laye, esinye ngakwesokunene sakhe, esinye ngakwesokhohlo. <verse eid="MAT 27:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="MAT 27:39"/>Labo ababesedlula lapho babemhlambaza, benikina amakhanda besithi, <verse eid="MAT 27:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="MAT 27:40"/>“Wena ozadiliza ithempeli ulakhe ngezinsuku ezintathu, zisindise! Yehla esiphambanweni nxa uyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu!” <verse eid="MAT 27:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="MAT 27:41"/>Ngokunjalo abaphristi abakhulu, labafundisi bomthetho kanye labadala bamklolodela. <verse eid="MAT 27:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="MAT 27:42"/>Bathi, “Wasindisa abanye, kodwa uyehluleka ukuzisindisa yena! UyiNkosi yako-Israyeli! Kehle manje esiphambanweni ukuze simkholwe. <verse eid="MAT 27:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="MAT 27:43"/>Uthembele kuNkulunkulu. UNkulunkulu kamsindise phela manje nxa emfuna, ngoba wathi, <char style="wj">‘NgiyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu.’</char> ” <verse eid="MAT 27:43"/><verse number="44" style="v" sid="MAT 27:44"/>Ngaleyondlela izigebenga ezazibethelwe kanye laye lazo zamthethisa ngenhlamba.<verse eid="MAT 27:44"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukufa KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="MAT 27:45"/>Kusukela emini kwaze kwaba lihola lesithathu emini ubumnyama bembesa lonke ilizwe. <verse eid="MAT 27:45"/><verse number="46" style="v" sid="MAT 27:46"/>Ngehola lesithathu emini uJesu wamemeza ngelizwi elikhulu wathi, <char style="tl"><char style="wj">“Eloyi, Eloyi, lamasabakithani?”</char></char><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">27.46 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">AmaHubo 22.1</char></note> (okutsho ukuthi, <char style="wj">“Nkulunkulu wami, Nkulunkulu wami, kungani usungidelile na?”</char>).<verse eid="MAT 27:46"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="MAT 27:47"/>Kwathi abanye kwababemi lapho bekuzwa lokho bathi, “Ubiza u-Elija.”<verse eid="MAT 27:47"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="MAT 27:48"/>Masinyane omunye wabo wagijima wathatha isipontshi. Wasicwilisa phakathi kwewayini elimunyu, wasixhuma oluthini wasidlulisela kuJesu ukuthi anathe. <verse eid="MAT 27:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="MAT 27:49"/>Abanengi bathi, “Myekele. Ake sibone ingabe u-Elija uzakuza azomsindisa.”<verse eid="MAT 27:49"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="MAT 27:50"/>UJesu esephindile ukumemeza ngelizwi elikhulu, umoya wakhe waphuma.<verse eid="MAT 27:50"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="51" style="v" sid="MAT 27:51"/>Ngalesosikhathi ikhetheni lethempeli laqhekezeka kabili kusukela phezulu kusiya phansi. Umhlaba wazamazama lamatshe aqhekezeka. <verse eid="MAT 27:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="MAT 27:52"/>Amathuna avuleka, izidumbu zabantu abanengi abangcwele abafayo zavuswa kwabafileyo. <verse eid="MAT 27:52"/><verse number="53" style="v" sid="MAT 27:53"/>Baphuma emathuneni, kwathi ngemva kokuvuka kukaJesu kwabafileyo baya edolobheni elingcwele bavela ebantwini abanengi.<verse eid="MAT 27:53"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="54" style="v" sid="MAT 27:54"/>Kwathi ukuba induna yekhulu kanye lalabo ababelinde uJesu bebona ukuzamazama komhlaba kanye lakho konke okwakwenzakele, besaba kakhulu, bababaza bathi, “Ngempela ubeyiNdodana kaNkulunkulu!”<verse eid="MAT 27:54"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="55" style="v" sid="MAT 27:55"/>Kwakulabesifazane abanengi, bebukele bebucwala. Babelandele uJesu besuka eGalile ukuthi banakekele izinswelo zakhe. <verse eid="MAT 27:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="MAT 27:56"/>Phakathi kwabo kwakuloMariya Magadalini, loMariya unina kaJakhobe loJosefa kanye lonina wamadodana kaZebhediya.<verse eid="MAT 27:56"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukungcwatshwa KukaJesu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="57" style="v" sid="MAT 27:57"/>Kwathi ilanga selithambeme, kwafika indoda enothileyo yase-Arimathiya, eyayibizwa ngokuthi nguJosefa, yena owayesengumfundi kaJesu. <verse eid="MAT 27:57"/><verse number="58" style="v" sid="MAT 27:58"/>Waya kuPhilathu wayacela isidumbu sikaJesu, uPhilathu walaya ukuba asiphiwe. <verse eid="MAT 27:58"/><verse number="59" style="v" sid="MAT 27:59"/>UJosefa wasithatha isidumbu wasigoqela ngelembu elihlanzekileyo lelineni, <verse eid="MAT 27:59"/><verse number="60" style="v" sid="MAT 27:60"/>wayasibeka ethuneni lakhe elitsha ayeligubhe edwaleni. Wagiqela ilitshe elikhulu emlonyeni wethuna wasehamba. <verse eid="MAT 27:60"/><verse number="61" style="v" sid="MAT 27:61"/>UMariya Magadalini lomunye uMariya babehlezi khonapho malungana lethuna.<verse eid="MAT 27:61"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Abalindi Ethuneni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="62" style="v" sid="MAT 27:62"/>Ngosuku olulandelayo, oluza ngemva kosuku lokuLungisela, abaphristi abakhulu labaFarisi baya kuPhilathu. <verse eid="MAT 27:62"/><verse number="63" style="v" sid="MAT 27:63"/>Bathi, “Nkosi, siyakhumbula ukuthi esaphila umkhohlisi loyana wathi yena, <char style="wj">‘Ngemva kwensuku ezintathu ngizavuka kwabafileyo.’</char> <verse eid="MAT 27:63"/><verse number="64" style="v" sid="MAT 27:64"/>Ngakho yenza ukuthi ithuna lilindwe kuze kube lusuku lwesithathu. Engxenye abafundi bakhe bangeza bantshontshe isidumbu sakhe, batshele abantu ukuthi usevukile kwabafileyo. Inkohliso le ingabambi kakhulu kuleyakuqala.”<verse eid="MAT 27:64"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="65" style="v" sid="MAT 27:65"/>UPhilathu waphendula wathi, “Thathani abalindi. Hambani liyevikela ithuna njengokubona kwenu.” <verse eid="MAT 27:65"/><verse number="66" style="v" sid="MAT 27:66"/>Basebehamba ukuyalinda lokuqinisa ithuna ngokubeka uphawu phezu kwelitshe njalo bamisa abalindi.<verse eid="MAT 27:66"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 27"/>
  <chapter number="28" style="c" sid="MAT 28"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuvuka Ekufeni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="MAT 28:1"/>Ngemva kweSabatha, ekuseni ngovivi losuku lokuqala lweviki, uMariya Magadalini lomunye uMariya baya ethuneni besiyakhangela.<verse eid="MAT 28:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="MAT 28:2"/>Kwaba lokuzamazama komhlaba okukhulu ngoba ingilosi yeNkosi yehla ivela ezulwini, yaya ethuneni yaligiqela ilitshe eceleni yahlala phezu kwalo. <verse eid="MAT 28:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="MAT 28:3"/>Ukubonakala kwayo kwakunjengombane, lezigqoko zayo zimhlophe nke njengongqwaqwane. <verse eid="MAT 28:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="MAT 28:4"/>Abalindi besaba baze bathuthumela baba njengabafileyo.<verse eid="MAT 28:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="MAT 28:5"/>Ingilosi yathi kwabesifazane, “Lingesabi, ngoba ngiyazi ukuthi lidinga uJesu obebethelwe. <verse eid="MAT 28:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="MAT 28:6"/>Kakho lapha; usevukile kwabafileyo njengoba watsho. Wozani libone indawo abelele kuyo. <verse eid="MAT 28:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="MAT 28:7"/>Hambani masinyane liyetshela abafundi bakhe lithi: ‘Usevukile kwabafileyo, uselandulele ukuya eGalile. Kulapho elizambona khona.’ Mina sengilitshelile manje.”<verse eid="MAT 28:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="MAT 28:8"/>Ngakho abesifazane basuka ngokuphangisa ethuneni, besesaba kodwa begcwele intokozo, bagijima ukuyatshela abafundi bakhe. <verse eid="MAT 28:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="MAT 28:9"/>Khonokho uJesu wahlangana labo. Wathi, <char style="wj">“Salibonani.”</char> Beza kuye, bamnamathela ngezandla ezinyaweni zakhe bamkhonza. <verse eid="MAT 28:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="MAT 28:10"/>UJesu wasesithi kubo, <char style="wj">“Lingesabi. Hambani liyetshela abafowethu ukuthi baye eGalile; kulapho abazangibona khona.”</char><verse eid="MAT 28:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umbiko Wabalindi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="MAT 28:11"/>Kwathi abesifazane sebehambile besendleleni, abanye babalindi bangena edolobheni bayabika kubaphristi abakhulu ngakho konke okwakwenzakele. <verse eid="MAT 28:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="MAT 28:12"/>Kwathi abaphristi abakhulu sebehlangene labadala babopha icebo, bafumbathisa abalindi imali ezwayo, <verse eid="MAT 28:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="MAT 28:13"/>babatshela bathi, “Libokuthi, ‘Abafundi bakhe beze ebusuku bamntshontsha thina silele.’ <verse eid="MAT 28:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="MAT 28:14"/>Nxa lelilizwi lifika kumbusi, sizamsuthisa ukuze lani lingangeni enkathazweni.” <verse eid="MAT 28:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="MAT 28:15"/>Ngakho amabutho ayithatha imali enza njengokulaywa kwawo. Yikho indaba le seyandiswa yakhula phakathi kwamaJuda kuze kube lamuhla.<verse eid="MAT 28:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umlayo Omkhulu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="MAT 28:16"/>Abafundi abalitshumi lanye basuka baya eGalile, baqonda entabeni uJesu ayethe baye kuyo. <verse eid="MAT 28:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="MAT 28:17"/>Bathi ukumbona bamkhonza; kodwa abanye bathandabuza. <verse eid="MAT 28:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="MAT 28:18"/>UJesu weza kubo wathi, <char style="wj">“Wonke amandla ezulwini lasemhlabeni aphiwe mina.</char> <verse eid="MAT 28:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="MAT 28:19"/><char style="wj">Ngakho hambani lenze abafundi ezizweni zonke, libabhaphathize ebizweni likaBaba, leleNdodana lelikaMoya oNgcwele,</char> <verse eid="MAT 28:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="MAT 28:20"/><char style="wj">njalo libafundise ukulalela konke engililaye ngakho. Ngempela ngilani kokuphela, kuze kube sekupheleni kwesikhathi.”</char><verse eid="MAT 28:20"/></para>
  <chapter eid="MAT 28"/>
</usx>
